\id ACT - Sembeleke Samberigi PNG Acts 01 22/3/91 Macnaughtan 
\h APOSOLO 
\toc1 Aposolo haliwekimaęž‰ pimiki ekimanue 
\toc2 Aposolo 
\toc3 Aposolo 
\mt1 Aposolo haliwekimaęž‰ pimiki ekimanue  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Diopilusio. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ titinaęž‰ buka wape puaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e kini pea mea pokeeke natenaęž‰ kini pea pua kutupa pa ipiki oli hepeni nane peeke natenaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ piekeeki make walaęž‰tiki piekeeki make paeyao wape puaęž‰me.  
\v 2 Kutupa Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ walolo haenaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ talopu mea haenaęž‰ leeke aposolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ pi lo paeyaotaęž‰ oli ya nane aęž‰meiyeketaęž‰ wape pu naowaęž‰me.  
\v 3 Yesumaęž‰ ipiki homa hoki nane mo aposolo haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki otaęž‰ wotu handenaęž‰yeke peneme yao hali tieke yaapo natenaęž‰ hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone tiaeyekeeki walaataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki iki paęž‰taęž‰ walo hayekeme.  
\v 4 Mo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± pa hayeke dinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Diutuseleme na minaęž‰paęž‰laake pa hapaęž‰peke. Ya Apaęž‰maęž‰ kulueke laa laęž‰ ulaęž‰ ale handeteke hapaęž‰peke. Hande IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ loaęž‰ alenaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 5 Kutupa Dionimaęž‰taęž‰ pa ikalimaęž‰ bapitaisi peao hayaęž‰pate hosikisiki hao hao peaataęž‰ Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ bapitaisi peaalieke loaęž‰ pitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ opimime leekeme.   
\s1 Yesu oli ya nane mea paęž‰laęž‰eki  
\p
\v 6 Yesu make mo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± mandake paęž‰taęž‰ mombaęž‰la haemeke dinaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Ame do natenaęž‰taęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ Isulai paa kilu tombuao haluekemaęž‰ alepe lemekeme.  
\v 7 Yesumaęž‰ mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Do natenaęž‰ doeki piliekee o Do ekinaęž‰ dupiliekee laa opuemenaęž‰ ikaęž‰eki diaęž‰me. Mo Apaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ honumake pulu paęž‰laęž‰ekie leekeme.  
\v 8 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate ikitaęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰eki milimikie leekeme. Mo Holi Sipitidi epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ yaka wekitisi haliweki Diutuseleme paęž‰taęž‰ make Sametia paęž‰taęž‰ make Diudia paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ make hama hama pea kenke honiki honiki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰manu make la halimikie leekeme.  
\v 9 Kotoeki lo paeyaotaęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ handaęž‰ poto poto la haenaęž‰ kone opaęž‰liao peekeme. Kutupa ya hapi homekemaęž‰ aęž‰pa ipiki aęž‰mbaeyekeme.  
\v 10 Yesu peeke handa mo haliwekimaęž‰ oli pulaęž‰me laa wopu handaęž‰hake witolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ koto kone hali yaapo hake pupa peke dau yamaęž‰ mea aęž‰pa halu pitolo alotaęž‰  
\v 11 Kaęž‰lili haliwekio. Do paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ ya paęž‰taęž‰ ombu ekipeke handaęž‰liao halemepe lepekeme. Do iki minaęž‰paęž‰lao ya nane pulaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ paa ipulu make do ya nane puleke handa handeleme tupaęž‰ kone paa ipiliaęž‰eki make koto tupaęž‰ kone ipiliekee lepekeme.   
\s1 Diudasinaęž‰ anke teke mieke hali  
\p
\v 12 Kutupa Diutuseleme nepoko paęž‰taęž‰ kilomida homeke tupaęž‰ pote maęž‰ndaęž‰ biki Olipeti paęž‰taęž‰ hao Diutuseleme nane laęž‰kaęž‰la pemekeme.  
\v 13 Mo teke da tieke paęž‰taęž‰ puaataęž‰ ikaęž‰ pelia hao haemeke manda da pandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ opaęž‰liaemekeme. Pida Dioni yaapo Diaęž‰mesi Aęž‰ndutu yaapo Pilipi Tomasi yaapo Badolomiu Maęž‰tiu yaapo Aęž‰lopiaęž‰sinaęž‰ eiyeke Diaęž‰mesi pitaęž‰ Saimono Seloti yaapo kutupa Diaęž‰mesinaęž‰ eiyeke Diudasi makee.  
\v 14 Koto haliweki paeyao mo wandaęž‰weki tonkaęž‰naęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ amaęž‰ Meti make ipikaęž‰ hameketiti make mandake paęž‰taęž‰ mombaęž‰la pitaęž‰ yeni pu pitimikime.   
\p
\v 15 Yeni pu pitaataęž‰ pa hosiki hao hao peaataęž‰ mo Ketisonaęž‰ pi minaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ pi hotuluekemaęž‰ mombelemekeme. Iki paeyaotaęž‰ 120 wandaęž‰hali tupaęž‰ mombaęž‰la pitinaęž‰ Pidamaęž‰ pi loluekemaęž‰ tiaeyekeme.  
\v 16 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka anaęž‰ kame titio. Hande Baibolo bukanaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ pitaęž‰ otaęž‰ yaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Hande Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ Deipidinaęž‰ hone u tiaaso haenaęž‰taęž‰ Yesu daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ mininaęž‰ haliweki hatuku polo piaęž‰ hali Diudasimaęž‰ pulu piekeeki dupilieke laa Deipidimaęž‰ wape piekeme.  
\v 17 Yesumaęž‰ Diudasi make niki ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ e pokomonoyeke talopu mea haenaęž‰ leeke handaataęž‰ niki ameĚ±leĚ± pomu hayaęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 18 Hande Diudasimaęž‰taęž‰ hokeeki puluekemaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ yapaęž‰ pea mieke manimaęž‰taęž‰ kenkesiki maęž‰ndaęž‰ hambaęž‰ miekeme. Koto kenke paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone lopaęž‰niaotaęž‰ otaęž‰ homeekeme. Ipikaęž‰ weleke tekelipe lia weleke yokaęž‰ petepete pea wiekeme.  
\v 19 Kutupa mo Diutuseleme da paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ koto piekeeki opuaataęž‰ koto kenke sikinaęž‰ biki ikaęž‰ da pi la alotaęž‰ Akeledama lo haemekeme. Koto laęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ We Kenkee laa lo haemekeme.   
\p
\v 20 Pidamaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo Emeli buka paęž‰taęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupa  
\q1 Ipikaęž‰ dataęž‰ hankoko pa hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ epelieke. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ na pua haenaęž‰e laa wape paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\p Kutupa wape paęž‰laęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ make dupa  
\q1 Ipikaęž‰ pokeeke etaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ meaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me laa wape paęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 21-22 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ niki ameĚ±leĚ± taęž‰maęž‰ni pea haluekemaęž‰ mo Tekehali Yesu paa mea tiaeyaęž‰eki handeaęž‰ hali kone anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me. Koto halitaęž‰ niki ameĚ±leĚ± hataęž‰ hoto paeyao Tekehali Yesu ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ pomu haomaęž‰ halie. Hande Dionimaęž‰ bapitaisi hau waleaęž‰ dinaęž‰ kini pu mea aęž‰pa Yesu niki ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ hamono kone ipiki hatuku mea hepeni nane aęž‰meiyeke handomaęž‰ pitaęž‰ pomu haomaęž‰ hali koto hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 23 Koto leeke handaa mo Ketiso wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hali yaaponaęž‰ biki lemekeme. Hali homeketaęž‰ Diosepee. Ipikaęž‰ biki maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ Basabasie. Koto hali kone pa tepo peao leeke bikitaęž‰ Diasedasi. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ Madaiyasie.  
\v 24-25 Kotoeki peaataęž‰ yeni dupa pimikime. Tekehalio. Wandaęž‰hali paeyaonaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ haumanu paeyao nakanaęž‰maęž‰ handeleme. Kutu pele ekinaęž‰ Tekehalio. Do hali yaapo paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Diudasimaęž‰taęž‰ aposolo hali hataęž‰ pokeaęž‰ e minaęž‰paęž‰lao ipikaęž‰ halo piaęž‰ alenaęž‰ peeke handaataęž‰ koto etaęž‰ hali epimaęž‰ minaęž‰pe. Niki paęž‰taęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ walae.  
\v 26 Koto yeni peaataęž‰ mo hali yaaponaęž‰ biki toopisiki yaaponaęž‰ wape peaataęž‰ titinaęž‰ wape pea lopaeyeke halinaęž‰ biki Madaiyasi yeketaęž‰ koto hali mimikime. Kutupa mo halitaęž‰ hande kiki yaaponaęž‰ ankenaęž‰ homeke pu aposolo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± taęž‰maęž‰ni pea haemekeme.   
\c 2  
\s1 Hande Holi Sipitidi epeekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Mo hande Pendikosi nate epeeke dinaęž‰taęž‰ mo pi mimiki wandaęž‰hali paeyao homeke alenaęž‰ mombaęž‰la haemekeme.  
\v 2 Kuta kone oli ya nanemaęž‰ po tilipu tieke ipulaęž‰ tupaęž‰ uĚ± tieke laa aęž‰paataęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali mombaęž‰la pitimiki da paęž‰taęž‰ pua otaęž‰ tumbaeyekeme.  
\v 3 Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo ti ulekemaęž‰ handeke ekimanu handemekeme. Kutupa mo ti ulekemaęž‰ handekeeki manumaęž‰taęž‰ telipeaaso hataęž‰ iki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ wataeyekeme.  
\v 4 Kutupa mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ iki paeyao tumba pitinaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ pi taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ lenaęž‰ leekeme.   
\p
\v 5 Yeni puluekemaęž‰ hone wimiki Diu haliwekitaęž‰ mo kenke paeyao nane hao pua mo Diutuseleme da paęž‰taęž‰ pua haemekeme.  
\v 6 Mo hande u tieke leekeeki opuaataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wopu pua handemekeme. Hande kenke paeyao nane hao epemeke Diu haliwekimaęž‰ do pi mimiki haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ da pi taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ kone laa lemekeeki opitolo hataęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰  
\v 7 wotu penkilipaęž‰tia pominolo hataęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone alotaęž‰ Do pi aleme haliweki paeyaotaęž‰ Kaęž‰lili haliwekie.  
\v 8 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ da pimanu aleme ekitaęž‰ ekipa paęž‰laęž‰pe laa alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\v 9 Nikitaęž‰ Padia nane make Midia nane make Ilame nane make Mesopoteimia nane make Diudia nane make Kaęž‰padosia nane make Pondasi nane make Eisia nane make  
\v 10 Pitikia nane make Paęž‰mbilia nane make Idiepi nane make mo Saitini teke paęž‰taęž‰ Libia nane make mandane haliweki Lomaęž‰ da hao epolomaęž‰me laataęž‰ nikitaęž‰ Diu haliweki make mo Diu haliwekinaęž‰ hau puluekemaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la halomaęž‰ Diendaili haliwekimaęž‰ make mandane ekitaęž‰  
\v 11 mo Kotiti Aęž‰teibia yaapo nane hao epolomaęž‰ haliweki halomaęž‰patetaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ hau tieke paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu mo haliwekimaęž‰ aleme ekitaęž‰ niki paeyaomaęž‰ nikaęž‰ da pi taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki pimanu kone opitolomaęž‰me lemekeme.  
\v 12 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone elekeeleke witolo hataęž‰ penkilipaęž‰tia pomua ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone lotaęž‰ peaęž‰tiki pitolo alotaęž‰ Do hau tieketaęž‰ ekipa paęž‰laęž‰pe laa lemekepate  
\v 13 mandane haliwekimaęž‰ mo pi mimiki haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ kitaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ hoke ikali naa keaaso pitelememe laa lemekeme.   
\s1 Pidamaęž‰ pi waleekeeki  
\p
\v 14 Kutupa Pidamaęž‰ mo hande 11 haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± tiao hataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi anekemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo ya tapake Diu haliweki make do Diutuseleme teke da paęž‰taęž‰ hao haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make iki paeyao IĚ±maęž‰ loluaęž‰ pitaęž‰ wotu opuaęž‰paęž‰pekee laataęž‰  
\v 15 Mandane haliweki ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ do haliwekitaęž‰ hoke ikali naa keaaso pitelememe alemepate diaęž‰me. Ametaęž‰ pa 9 okoloko nate minolo haenaęž‰ kone halomaęž‰me.  
\v 16 Diaęž‰me. Do hautaęž‰ ambaęž‰ mo potopede hali Diolemaęž‰ leekeeki dupa   
\q1
\v 17 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Natemanu paeluekemaęž‰ haenaęž‰taęž‰ dupulueke laa  
\q1 Wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ yaka Holi Sipitidi hale hale pulueke.  
\q1 Kutupa ikaęž‰ weki manumaęž‰ make wandiki manumaęž‰ make yaka pi laęž‰ mea halaęž‰tiki pilimikie.  
\q1 Ikaęž‰ weki haliwekimaęž‰ mandane hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu handenaęž‰ lolueke.  
\q1 Kutupa ikaęž‰ koke haliwekimaęž‰ make upamanu pilimikie.   
\q1
\v 18 Aowe. Koto nate manunaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ yaka Holi Sipitidi hale hale puaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰  
\q1 yaka e pokao haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ kone yaka pi laęž‰ mea halaęž‰tiki pilimikie.   
\q1
\v 19 Oli ya nane make oni kenke nane make mo na hando haleme wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu pulueke.  
\q1 Kutupa we make ti uleke make lumu tieke make handilimikie.   
\q1
\v 20 Oli natetaęž‰ na teke timbaęž‰ lelieke. Oli sumbaęž‰ make we pupa pelieke.  
\q1 Kutupa koto hoki nanetaęž‰ mo hande Tekehalinaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± pitaęž‰laęž‰ Nate Tieke ipilieke.   
\q1
\v 21 Koto di ipulaęž‰ nanetaęž‰ hali epimaęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ biki alo hataęž‰ wi leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰  
\q1 kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰ daęž‰taenaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ petelelieke laa leekeme.   
\p
\v 22 Isulai haliwekio. IĚ±maęž‰ do alo pi opuaęž‰paęž‰peke. Hande Naęž‰saęž‰tete hali Yesutaęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰pa hataęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ wele peaaso haenaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ na hando halomaęž‰ ekimanu make wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu make ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pitolo haenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ tapaalo halie laa peneme yatiki piaęž‰me. Kutupa do haumanu paeyao ikaęž‰ hone wilimime leekeme.  
\v 23 Ambaęž‰ kone Kodaęž‰maęž‰ hone wiaataęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ milimikie laa pi laęž‰ wiekeme. Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo hoke hau pu haleme haliwekimaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ hande aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki tinaęž‰ ikokomaęž‰ tamendiaenaęž‰ lemeke ekimaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ kone Yesu limikime.  
\v 24 Kutu pimipate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande toopi kaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ Yesu paa mea tiaeyekeme. Mo hande lapaęž‰ pimiki toopimaęž‰taęž‰ Yesu miniki pitaęž‰peke anaęž‰ na pitolo hataęž‰ mo hande homaasaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ Yesu tonkaeyeke ekitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapawaeyekeme.  
\v 25 Deipidimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ doeki laęž‰leke handa loaęž‰me.  
\q1 Tekehali hoto paeyao IĚ± yaapo halaęž‰eki handolome. Maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± laęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰maęž‰ peaapaęž‰naęž‰yeke yaka popeke kiki nane halaęž‰me.   
\q1
\v 26 Koto ekinaęž‰ yaka pukimaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ ya kakemaęž‰ make taęž‰naęž‰piki pimanu lo halome.  
\q1 Kutupa make IĚ±taęž‰ pa kenke hali halopate kone mo epekeeki muluekemaęž‰ handeteke halueke.   
\q1
\v 27 Pa ekipeke nakanaęž‰maęž‰ yaka temokotaęž‰ mo homemeke wandaęž‰hali haleme alenaęž‰ na haenaęž‰ lelipikie.  
\q1 Kutupa nakaęž‰ yakopiki halitaęž‰ oni kenke paęž‰taęž‰ na tandepenaęž‰ lelipikiyeke loaęž‰me.   
\q1
\v 28 Mo hande daęž‰taęž‰ lolo paęž‰laęž‰ potaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰ waleme. Kutupa nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± yaapo hale ekinaęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ tumbaalaęž‰me laa laęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 29 Kametitio. Iki paęž‰taęž‰ mo nikaęž‰ apaęž‰ Deipidinaęž‰ do otaęž‰ pimanu alome. Ipikitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ kone homeeke handa mea hoimikipate pa ame make hande hoimiki alenaęž‰ hando halomaęž‰me.  
\v 30 Deipidimaęž‰taęž‰ potopede hali hataęž‰taęž‰ hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pi laęž‰ wiekeeki piekeme. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pi laęž‰ witolo alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ hoki nane halo paęž‰laęž‰ hali homeketaęž‰ neke kini hali hale tupaęž‰ mea haenaęž‰ lolueke laa laęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 31 Kutupa Deipidimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ pulu piekeeki hone witolo hataęž‰ hande Ketiso paa tiaalo piekeeki paęž‰taęž‰ dupa leekeme.  
\q1 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo homemeke wandaęž‰hali haleme alenaęž‰ yaka temoko na haenaęž‰ lelipikie.  
\q1 Kutupa nakaęž‰ yakopiki halitaęž‰ oni kenke paęž‰taęž‰ na tandepo lo paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me laęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 32 Do hande Yesutaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ paa mea tiaalaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ niki paeyaomaęž‰ handomaęž‰eki iki paęž‰taęž‰ la kitolomaęž‰me.  
\v 33 Ipikaęž‰ Apaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰ wieke tupaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ mea tiao ipikaęž‰ popeke kiki nane mea pitaotaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ Holi Sipitidi haleekeme. Kutupa nikanaęž‰maęž‰ ame do handolomaęž‰ ekimanu make do opitolomaęž‰ ekimanu tonkaęž‰naęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ ipulaęž‰me.  
\v 34 Deipidimaęž‰taęž‰ oli ya nane na aęž‰meiyekepate pa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\q1 Mo Tekehalimaęž‰ yaka Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰   
\q1
\v 35 IĚ±maęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ nakaęž‰ anke tapaęž‰pao pituelenaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ ame do yaka popeke nane kikinaęž‰ pitie laa laęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 36 Koto ekinaęž‰ Isulai wandaęž‰hali paeyao do hande ikanaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki tinaęž‰ tamendiao limiki hali Yesutaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ Tekehali make Ketiso make mea haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone otaęž‰ wopu wiaęž‰paęž‰peke laa leekeme.   
\p
\v 37 Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ koto pi opuaataęž‰ ikaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ aweeke handaa Pida paęž‰taęž‰ make mandane aposolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ make alotaęž‰ Kametitio. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ eki peomonope laa lemekeme.  
\v 38 Koto lemeke handaa Pidamaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke hau peleme ekimanu pa paeyaenaęž‰yeke hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰ mina wiaataęž‰ Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ bapitaisi hau peaęž‰paęž‰peke. Kutu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kilie aletaęž‰ mo Holi Sipitidi kilieke.  
\v 39 Pa ekipeke mo hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ pi laęž‰ wieke ekitaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ make ikaęž‰ weki wandiki paęž‰taęž‰ make mo papate haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make pa mo Tekehalimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ kone epenaęž‰ wi alaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ make ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi laęž‰ wiekeme laa leekeme.   
\p
\v 40 Pidamaęž‰ koto tupaęž‰ pi walaataęž‰ pa mandane pimanu make mea aęž‰meiyao alotaęž‰ Do hoke wandaęž‰hali hoeyaaluekemaęž‰ ipilie panisimaęž‰ iki tonkaęž‰naęž‰ hoeyaapaęž‰naęž‰ otaęž‰ paapaęž‰peke.  
\v 41 Koto leeke handa wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ Pidamaęž‰ waleeke pi opuaataęž‰ bapitaisi hau pimikime. Paeyaotaęž‰ 3 daoseni wandaęž‰hali tupaęž‰ koto natenaęž‰ mo hande pi minolo hataęž‰ mo Ketiso wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± apaęž‰tao hao haemekeme.  
\v 42 Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ hande aposolo haliwekimaęž‰ waleme pimanu opuaęž‰tiki peaataęž‰ Ketiso wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± mombaęž‰laęž‰tiki peaataęž‰ yeni pea ne naęž‰tiki pimikime.   
\s1 Ketiso wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ haemeke hau  
\p
\v 43 Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ wele peaaso haenaęž‰ mo aposolo haliwekimaęž‰ na hando haemeke ekimanu wotu pimiki handaa wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homemekeme.  
\v 44 Mo hande pi mimiki wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ wotu taęž‰maęž‰ni pea hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ wia haemeke alemanu paeyao telipea pimikime.  
\v 45 Ikaęž‰ kenkemanu o damanu make ikaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ make maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hambenaęž‰ laataęž‰ mani meataęž‰ mo iki ameĚ±leĚ± mani diaęž‰yeke wandaęž‰halimanu paęž‰taęž‰ telipaemekeme.  
\v 46 Nate paeyao mo tembolo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ homeke alenaęž‰ mombaęž‰laęž‰tiki peaataęž‰ ikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰manu make mandake paęž‰taęž‰ pitaęž‰ ne naęž‰tiki pimikime. Homu pea hataęž‰  
\v 47 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi laaso hataęž‰ kutu pimikime. Kutupa wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ make iki paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰tiki pimikime. Koto ekinaęž‰ nate paeyao Tekehalimaęž‰ mo daęž‰taenaęž‰yeke pi mimiki wandaęž‰hali iki ameĚ±leĚ± haenaęž‰yeke mea taęž‰maęž‰ni peao haenaęž‰ laęž‰tiki piekeme.   
\c 3  
\s1 Mo hande anke hoke hali mea epeaeyekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Kutupa Pida Dioni yaapotaęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ yeni pu haepeke nate lekenaęž‰ 3 okoloko nate oni pambolo pulu haenaęž‰ oli tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ yeni puluekemaęž‰ pepekeme.  
\v 2 Kutupa hali homeke mendieke paęž‰taęž‰ kone potaęž‰ otaęž‰ pomuaęž‰peke na yeke hali nate paeyao mea tia puaęž‰tiki pea mo tembolo da potaęž‰ kake bikitaęž‰ Seliapopiki Potaęž‰ Kake koto paęž‰taęž‰ mo tembolo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ yopuaęž‰tiki pimiki wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ mani maęž‰ndaęž‰ kipee laa honke laęž‰tiki pinaęž‰ yeke pua tu wiaęž‰tiki pimikime.   
\p
\v 3 Mo hande potaęž‰ puaęž‰peke na yeke halimaęž‰taęž‰ Pida Dioni yaapo mo tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambuluekemaęž‰ haenaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mani maęž‰ndaęž‰ kipee laa honke leekeme.  
\v 4 Koto leeke Pida Dioni yaapomaęž‰ mo hande hali handaęž‰moneaaso hataęž‰ Pidamaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Diki handaęž‰e leekeme.  
\v 5 Mo hande potaęž‰ pomuaęž‰peke na yeke halimaęž‰ hone witolotaęž‰ do hali yaapomaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ kilieke hone witolo hataęž‰ mo hali yaapo otaęž‰ wopu handaęž‰hake wiekepate  
\v 6 Pidamaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ kolo o silipamanu make maęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate IĚ±maęž‰ wia halo aletaęž‰ kionoe. Mo Naęž‰saęž‰tete hali Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ loaęž‰maęž‰ potaęž‰ pue leekeme.  
\v 7 Kutupa Pidamaęž‰ popeke nane kiki mina mea aęž‰meiyaeyekeme. Kutupa koto kone mo halinaęž‰ anke maĚ±lekemanu honkopu honkopu hao hayekeme.  
\v 8 Kutupa mo hande hali tialu bao anke hao peekeme.  
\p Kutupa mo hali yaapo ameĚ±leĚ± mo tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ puaataęž‰ mo hande potaęž‰ puaęž‰peke na yeke halitaęž‰ puaęž‰tiki ponkaęž‰daęž‰daęž‰ puaęž‰tiki pitolo hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki make mea aęž‰meiyatiki peekeme.  
\v 9 Kutupa da paęž‰taęž‰ pitimiki wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo hande hali yopulu hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki mea aęž‰meiyatiki yapeekeeki handemekeme.  
\v 10 Kutupa mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hone wimikime. Do halitaęž‰ mo hande tembolonaęž‰ Seliapopiki Potaęž‰ Kake paęž‰taęž‰ pitaęž‰ mani honke lo halaęž‰ halie hone wimikime. Kutupa puki keapa anemone pitolo haenaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do halitaęž‰ ekipa paęž‰laęž‰pe lemekeme.   
\s1 Pidamaęž‰ tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ pi waleekeeki  
\p
\v 11 Mo hande halimaęž‰ Pida Dioni yaaponaęž‰ kiki pa wia haenaęž‰ iki tepotaęž‰ mo tembolonaęž‰ kalale maęž‰ndaęž‰ biki Solomononaęž‰ Kaputaęž‰ haemekeme. Kutupa mo wandaęž‰hali paeyao leke opo handaęž‰hake witolo hataęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ anke hao pua mombelemekeme.  
\v 12 Pidamaęž‰ doeki handa mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Isulai haliwekio. Do ekinaęž‰ ekipeke leke opo handaęž‰hake wia yopilimipe o diki make ekipeke handaęž‰hake witemepe. Dikanaęž‰maęž‰ dikaęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ o nikaęž‰ yakopiki haumaęž‰ do hali mea potaęž‰ penaęž‰ lolopaęž‰pe leekeme.  
\v 13 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ Aisaęž‰ke Dieikope ikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ apaęž‰ titinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kone mo wele pitaęž‰laęž‰eki ipikaęž‰ e pokaeyeke hali Yesunaęž‰ biki mea aęž‰meiyaaso hataęž‰ haleekeme. Kutu paęž‰laęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Pailedi paęž‰taęž‰ luekemaęž‰ hatuku pua Pailedimaęž‰taęž‰ paa penaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ taapolo haenaęž‰ kone ikanaęž‰maęž‰ luekemaęž‰ taapeme hali ipikinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 14 Kutu paęž‰laęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Epeke Yakopiki Hali kiao pa Pailedi paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Ikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo hande hali litaęž‰laęž‰ hali kone pa penaęž‰ lae lememe leekeme.  
\v 15 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo daęž‰taasaęž‰ hali limipate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mea tiaeyekeme. Kutupa nikanaęž‰maęž‰ wekitisi do halualu pitolomaęž‰ handaęž‰e leekeme.  
\v 16 Mo hande ipikaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ mo potaęž‰ pomuaęž‰peke na yeke hali honkopu haenaęž‰ lopaęž‰me. Ame do handeleme ekitaęž‰ mo hande ipikaęž‰ hone tulaasaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰me. Ame do handeleme ekitaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaasaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ ipiki epeaalaęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 17 Ya kametitio. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make ikaęž‰ you haliwekimaęž‰ tonkaęž‰naęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ pimiki ekitaęž‰ teke na handaęž‰ wiki hataęž‰ pimi ekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ hone witolome.  
\v 18 Ambaęž‰ kiaake Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ tanda mulu paęž‰laęž‰eki mo potopede haliweki paeyaomaęž‰ la hale hale pinaęž‰ leekeme. Kutupa hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰ wiekeeki kone otaęž‰ yao ikanaęž‰maęž‰ do pimime.  
\v 19 Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke hau peleme ekimanu Kodaęž‰maęž‰ honi mea baenaęž‰yeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰ mina wiaataęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰ mina puaęž‰paęž‰peke.  
\v 20 Dupimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ temoko manunaęž‰ honkopu ha tiaasaęž‰eki Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kiaataęž‰ kutupa Yesutaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ mea ikaęž‰ Ketiso hali haenaęž‰ leeke hali iki paęž‰taęž‰ tapaalieke.  
\v 21 Yesutaęž‰ hepeni nane pua hao halaęž‰pate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao panake ekimanu wopulu paęž‰laęž‰ nate handeteke halaęž‰me. Ambaęž‰ kiaake Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yakopiki potopede haliwekimaęž‰ la hale hale pieke tupaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 22 Mosesimaęž‰ dupa leekeme. Ikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ hande Tekehalimaęž‰ IĚ± tapaeyaęž‰ tupaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ make potopede hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ tapaalieke. Koto halitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ tapake hali kone tapaalieke. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ eki pimanu iki paęž‰taęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ opuaęž‰paęž‰peke.  
\v 23 Hali epimaęž‰ mo hande potopede halimaęž‰ lelie pi na opiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ koto halitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± taęž‰maęž‰ni pea na hake Kodaęž‰maęž‰ hoeyaalieke leekeme.   
\p
\v 24 Kutupa make mo potopede haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ Samuele make ipikaęž‰ hoki nane haemeke potopede haliweki make pi laęž‰ mea halaęž‰paęž‰peke yeeke haliweki paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ ame do pitolomaęž‰ haumanu kone ambaęž‰ la hale hale pimikime.  
\v 25 Mo potopede haliwekimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰ wieke pimanu la hale hale pimiki ekitaęž‰ ikaęž‰eki kone ulaęž‰me. Kutupa make Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ apaęž‰mei ameda ameĚ±leĚ± pi laęž‰ wieke ekitaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ make laęž‰ ulaęž‰me. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ leeke tupaęž‰ dupae. Nakaęž‰ hoki nane mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilimi wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ kenke wandaęž‰hali paeyao IĚ±maęž‰ epeaalueke laa leekeme.  
\v 26 Koto ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ hali mea haenaęž‰ laataęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰la tapaeyekeme. Koto tapake hautaęž‰ iki epeaaluekemaęž‰ piekeme. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke haumanu minaęž‰paęž‰lao ikaęž‰ puki ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰laasaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ iki epeaaluekemaęž‰ piekeme laa leekeme.   
\c 4  
\s1 Pida Dioni yaapo kaĚ±leĚ±sete haliwekinaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ haepekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Pida Dioni yaapomaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi alo haenaęž‰ yeni peao haemeke haliweki make mo tembolo da handeteke hayeke you hali make Saęž‰dusi haliweki make mo hali tepo paęž‰taęž‰ epemekeme.  
\v 2 Pida Dioni yaapomaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ hande homa paa tiaalo polomaęž‰eki wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ walepeke handa mo haliwekimaęž‰ mineke pankolo hataęž‰  
\v 3 iki tepo taęž‰nkaęž‰paęž‰ mina timbaęž‰ ambaęž‰ leeke handa da kaęž‰laęž‰paaso pi yokaalu puluekemaęž‰ dipula pitaemekeme.  
\v 4 Kutu piekepate mo pi opimiki wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ pi mimikime. Kutupa mo haliwekitaęž‰ 5000manu yekeme.   
\p
\v 5 Da maęž‰ndaęž‰ kelepeeke ikaęž‰ you haliwekitaęž‰ kutupa tondiki haliweki make wape pea walaęž‰tiki pu haemeke haliweki make Diutuseleme paęž‰taęž‰ mandaęž‰hande mandaęž‰hande pu alu alu pimikime.  
\v 6 Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ yeni peao haemeke you haliwekinaęž‰ you hali Aęž‰nasi kutupa Kaiyaęž‰pasi Dioni make Aęž‰lekesaęž‰nda kutupa yeni peao haemeke you haliwekinaęž‰ you halinaęž‰ tapake haliweki make mombelemekeme.  
\v 7 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ mo aposolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Eki wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ o eki bikinaęž‰ doeki pitelepepe lemekeme.   
\p
\v 8 Kutupa Pidataęž‰ Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ tumba hake halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ you haliweki pitaęž‰ tondiki haliweki yaapoo.  
\v 9 Do dikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto anke hoke hali mea epeaalopaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ loaęž‰me. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ diki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Do halitaęž‰ ekipa mea epeao pipipe alemepe.  
\v 10 Iki paeyao mo Isulai wandaęž‰hali make doeki opuaęž‰pe. Naęž‰saęž‰tete hali Yesu Ketisotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ limipate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ paa mea tiaeyeke hali ipikaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ do hali epeke tupaęž‰ tiao honkopu hao do halaęž‰ handaęž‰e leekeme.  
\v 11 Pa ekipeke Yesu paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo Baibolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\q1 Koto toopitaęž‰ iki mo da aęž‰eteleme haliwekimaęž‰ kipaęž‰laęž‰me lemepate pa ametaęž‰ koto toopi kone mo keneme toopi pa ulaęž‰me laa laęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 12 Kutupa niki mea detemono paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰laęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ na halaęž‰me. Oli ya oto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali mea daęž‰taasaęž‰ halinaęž‰ biki maęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰leke loaęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 13 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ Pida Dioni yaapomaęž‰ paalaęž‰ na homepekeeki handolo hataęž‰ koto hali yaapomaęž‰ sukulunaęž‰ make na pepeke otaęž‰ pa da haepeke hali yaapoe laataęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ leke opaęž‰ alu alu pea kutupa hone witolotaęž‰ Yesu ameĚ±leĚ± pomu hataęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ hone wimikime.  
\v 14 Kutupa mo hande mea tiao hayeke halitaęž‰ koto hali yaapo ameĚ±leĚ± hayeke eki handolo hataęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ laapeke na yeekeme.  
\v 15 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo hali tepo paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do kaĚ±leĚ±sete da minaęž‰paęž‰lao pupe laataęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone alotaęž‰  
\v 16 Do hali yaapo paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ eki pumanaęž‰pe lemekeme. Oni Diutuseleme paęž‰taęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo otaęž‰ na hando halomaęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ tieke pipikieki ambaęž‰ opua wilimime. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ yapi alo alepeme pi lapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰pate  
\v 17 pa do hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ saęž‰mbaęž‰laęž‰pa wiaapaęž‰naęž‰ do hali yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ Mo hande bikinaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ paa na walaęž‰paęž‰peke laa pi takaęž‰lakemaęž‰ lomanaęž‰e lemekeme.   
\p
\v 18 Koto ekinaęž‰ Pida Dioni yaapo wi la alotaęž‰ Do wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ biki laa alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ o pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ na walaęž‰paęž‰pekee lemekeme.  
\v 19 Koto leeke Pidamaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ hataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ aleme pi opua pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰pe o Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi opua pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰pe. Ikaęž‰ hone wia pi hotiaęž‰paęž‰peke lepekeme.  
\v 20 Dikanaęž‰maęž‰ handopaęž‰eki make opupaęž‰eki make pa walaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 21 Kutupa wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ kutu piekeeki hando hao Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi laemeke handa hali yaapo panisi peaapeke na yeke pi takaęž‰lakemaęž‰ paa laataęž‰ da penaęž‰ tapaemekeme.  
\v 22 Mo hande mea tiaeyeke halitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ anke hoeya u pitinaęž‰ yapeeke bapitaęž‰ 40 tupaęž‰ ambaęž‰ paeyekeme.   
\s1 Ketiso wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ puki hanaęž‰ nokepenaęž‰yeke yeni pimikieki  
\p
\v 23 Pida Dioni yaapotaęž‰ lombaęž‰ tapaeyeke pitaęž‰taęž‰ kuta kone ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la puakaęž‰naęž‰ mo hande yeni peao haemeke teke haliwekimaęž‰ make mo tondiki haliwekimaęž‰ make lemekeeki mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ la halepekeme.  
\v 24 Koto lepeke pi opuaataęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ homeke hone wia Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pitolo alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Neketaęž‰ ya kenke dawala tepo make kutupa koto paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ alemanu paeyao make nakanaęž‰maęž‰ wepia winaęž‰ lele halie laataęž‰  
\v 25 Nikaęž‰ apaęž‰mei hali Deipiditaęž‰ nakaęž‰ e pokaeyeke hali haenaęž‰maęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ pu tiaaso haenaęž‰ kone ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\q1 Diendaili wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ekipeke mineke sokaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ homemekepe.  
\q1 Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ekipeke pa hameke kone aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombemekepe.   
\q1
\v 26 Do kenkenaęž‰ kini haliwekimaęž‰ tikitiki yao hataęž‰ mo you haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± mombaęž‰laataęž‰  
\q1 mo Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ make mea lopaaluekemaęž‰ tiao haemekeme leekeme.   
\p
\v 27 Otaęž‰ leekeme laataęž‰ Do daoni tieke paęž‰taęž‰ Hetodi pitaęž‰ Pontiasi Pailedi yaapomaęž‰ make mo Diendaili haliweki pitaęž‰ Isulai wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± make paeyaomaęž‰ mombaęž‰laataęž‰ nakaęž‰ yakopiki E Pokaeyaęž‰ Halitaęž‰ hande Ketiso haenaęž‰ lele hali Yesu mea lopaaluekemaęž‰ tiao haememe.  
\v 28 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mombaęž‰la hataęž‰ kotoeki puluekemaęž‰ pimikipate nakanaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ hone wia nakaęž‰ wele paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ ambaęž‰ kone dupilimikie laa pinaęž‰ leleme.  
\v 29 Kutupa Tekehalio. Ametaęž‰ niki paalaęž‰maęž‰ homomono alemeeki nakanaęž‰maęž‰ opuaataęž‰ niki nakaęž‰ e pokaasomaęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ nakaęž‰ pitaęž‰ puki takaęž‰lao hataęž‰ lamono lapeke laataęž‰  
\v 30 Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ yenimanu tande laluekemaęž‰ nakaęž‰ kiki tindipao hataęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu make na hando halomaęž‰ ekimanu make nakaęž‰ yakopiki E Pokaasaęž‰ Hali Yesu ipikaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ pinaęž‰ lapeke laa lemekeme.   
\p
\v 31 Yeni pu paeyeketaęž‰ ikaęž‰ mo hande mombelemeke da kone laęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰maęž‰ piekeme. Koto paęž‰taęž‰ pitimiki wandaęž‰hali paeyaotaęž‰ Holi Sipitidi tumba pitumaęž‰ pitumaęž‰ piekeme. Kutupa Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ puki takaęž‰lao hataęž‰ lemekeme.   
\s1 Alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao mandakenaęž‰eki  
\p
\v 32 Kutupa mo hande pi mimiki wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ hone homeke hau homeke wia haemekeme. Kutupa hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wieke alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ yakaeki homekee lapeke na yekeme. Homekemaęž‰ wieke alaęž‰taęž‰ peaęž‰naęž‰eki yekeme.  
\v 33 Kutupa wele pitaęž‰laęž‰eki tiekemaęž‰taęž‰ mo aposolo haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ tiaeyaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ wekitisi halu alu pea kutupa Kodaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ pitiekeme.  
\v 34-35 Kutu piekepate iki paeyaotaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao anaęž‰naęž‰ wimikime. Mo hande tapake wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ da make ikaęž‰ kenke make hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hambenaęž‰ laataęž‰ koto mani ki laęž‰ meaataęž‰ mo aposolo haliwekinaęž‰ anke teke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa wiaęž‰tiki pimikime. Kutupa mo manitaęž‰ aposolo haliwekimaęž‰ meaataęž‰ Ketiso wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ telipatiki pimikime.   
\p
\v 36 Kutupu haemekepate hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ Diosepe hayekeme. Koto halitaęž‰ Lipae tapake hali hayekepate ipiki mendiki hautaęž‰ Saipotasi nane mendieke halie. Aposolo haliwekimaęž‰ mo halinaęž‰ biki maęž‰ndaęž‰ Banabasi lemekeme. Mo biki lemeke ekinaęž‰ pi napeketaęž‰ dupae. Honkopu haenaęž‰ Sutiaasaęž‰ Halie la kone lemekeme.  
\v 37 Koto hali ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kenkesiki maęž‰ndaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hambenaęž‰ laataęž‰ koto mieke mani mea aęž‰paataęž‰ aposolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ haleekeme.   
\c 5  
\s1 Aęž‰naęž‰naisi Sapaita yaapo  
\p
\v 1 Kutu piekepate Aęž‰naęž‰naisi ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ Sapaita yaapo ipilikaęž‰ kenketaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hambenaęž‰ lepekeme.  
\v 2 Kutupa mo hande mipiki manitaęž‰ mandaneeki ipilikaęž‰ hone wia mea pankaęž‰ wiaataęž‰ mandaneeki ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande aposolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ mea epeekeme.  
\v 3 Kutu piekepate Pidamaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aęž‰naęž‰naisio. Ekipeke Holi Sipitidi paęž‰taęž‰ yayapiki pi alepe leekeme. Sadani nakaęž‰ you paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa pitaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ kenkenaęž‰ mele manitaęž‰ pa ekipeke mandaneeki pankaęž‰ winaęž‰ laa pipe leekeme.  
\v 4 Ambaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ wia hae dinaęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰eki na yekepe leekeme. Kutupa mo hambenaęž‰ le dinaęž‰ make mo manitaęž‰ nakaęž‰ honkopunaęž‰ kone na pelepe leekeme. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ hali paęž‰taęž‰ yayapiki hau na pelepate Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ kone peleme. Do hautaęž‰ ekipa handaęž‰ wia pelepe leekeme.  
\v 5 Do leeke ekimanu opuaataęž‰ Aęž‰naęž‰naisi kenkenaęž‰ hondaęž‰pa lopa homeekeme. Kutupa koto hao yapeeke haliwekimaęž‰ doeki opimiki haliwekimaęž‰ make paalaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ leke opo handaęž‰hake wimikime.  
\v 6 Kutupa paęž‰paęž‰naęž‰ wekitonu aęž‰pa ipikaęž‰ toko mea daumaęž‰ tonkao hoilu pemekeme.   
\p
\v 7 Hosiki pitu pitu pea mo awa tepomanu paeyeke ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ mo hande pieke ekimanu hone make na wiki hondaęž‰ pambolo epeekeme.  
\v 8 Pidamaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo ipilikaęž‰ kenke hambenaęž‰ lepe mani manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ dupiki wopu mipipe leeke mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aowe. Koto tupaęž‰ mupaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 9 Pidamaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipiliki yaapomaęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ mo Tekehalinaęž‰ Holi Sipitidi paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hone mea wialuekemaęž‰ ekipeke pipipe leekeme. Handaęž‰e. Nakaęž‰ haliki mea hoilu paęž‰laęž‰ haliwekitaęž‰ neke mea hoilu puluekemaęž‰ ambaęž‰ do potaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ do aęž‰pa haleme handaęž‰e leekeme.  
\v 10 Kutupa koto kone mo wandaęž‰ Pidanaęž‰ anke teke paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰pa lopaęž‰niao homeekeme. Kutupa mo hande wekihali tonu aęž‰pa handemekepate homeeke handa ipikaęž‰ toko mea tia pua haliki hoiyeke ale paęž‰taęž‰ pua hoimikime.  
\v 11 Kutupa koto siosi wandaęž‰hali paeyaotaęž‰ pa mo opimiki wandaęž‰hali make paalaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ kone leke opaęž‰ minaęž‰ bepi pu alu alu pimikime.   
\s1 Na hando haemeke haumanu  
\p
\v 12 Mo aposolo haliwekimaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ na hando haemeke ekimanu wotu pimikime. Kutupa paeyaomaęž‰ mo tembolonaęž‰ kalale maęž‰ndaęž‰ biki Solomononaęž‰ Kapu paęž‰taęž‰ mombelaęž‰tiki pimikime.  
\v 13 Kutupa ikinaęž‰ mo pa haemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ pi laemekepate paalaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± haluekemaęž‰ hone na wimikime.  
\v 14 Kutu pimikipate ambaęž‰ na pu haemeke tupaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ lo wandaęž‰weki make haliweki make Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰maęž‰ni puluendi pimikime.  
\v 15 Mo aposolo haliwekimaęž‰ koto haumanu pu haemeke ekinaęž‰ da wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ yeni hapa papu wimiki wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ tu mea pua potaęž‰naęž‰ yapaęž‰taęž‰ yamaomaęž‰ yamaomaęž‰ peaataęž‰ mandaneeki bedinaęž‰ umaęž‰ umaęž‰ pea paeyao potaęž‰naęž‰ wimikime. Koto hau pimiki ekitaęž‰ Pida potaęž‰naęž‰ yopulu hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ suasuamaęž‰ kone mo wimiki mandane wandaęž‰hali ankulatiki yapenaęž‰ pimikime.  
\v 16 Mo Diutuseleme da teke paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke daonimanu paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰hali paeya tapaomaęž‰ ikaęž‰ yeni haemeke wandaęž‰hali make hoke temoko pitieke wandaęž‰hali make hatuku mea epemekeme. Kutu pieketaęž‰ paeyao ikaęž‰ yeni tandeleekeme.   
\s1 Aposolo haliwekimaęž‰ tanda paęž‰laęž‰eki mimikieki  
\p
\v 17 Kutu pieke handaataęž‰ mo yeni peao haemeke you haliwekinaęž‰ you halimaęž‰ ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ haemeke haliweki tonkaęž‰naęž‰ mo Saęž‰dusi tapake mandane haliweki kone ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo aposolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hone witolo hataęž‰ sokaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ homemekeme. Hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ pulumeke hone wimikime.  
\v 18 Kutupa mo aposolo haliweki daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ mininaęž‰ laataęž‰ dipula mea lopaemekeme.  
\v 19 Kutu pimikipate koto timbataęž‰ Tekehali ipikaęž‰ enisolo maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ mo dipula da potaęž‰ lombaęž‰ mea hande aposolo haliweki hamaęž‰ nane hatuku pua iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\v 20 Mo tembolo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pamba pua hataęž‰ do panake daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ pi wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ opinaęž‰ walaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.  
\v 21 Mo hande aposolo haliwekimaęž‰ koto leeke pi opuaataęž‰ da panake kaęž‰laęž‰polo haenaęž‰ mo tembolo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pamba pua pi walemekeme.  
\p Mo yeni peao haemeke you haliwekinaęž‰ you halimaęž‰ ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ haemeke haliweki tonkaęž‰naęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Diu kaĚ±leĚ±sete haliweki paeyaomaęž‰ pi tieke hotuluekemaęž‰ mombelenaęž‰ lemekeme. Kutupa mo dipula da nane make pi tapaaso alotaęž‰ Koto hande haliwekitaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku mea ipupe laa lemekeme.  
\v 22 Mo tembolo da handeteke haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ dipula da paęž‰taęž‰ opolo pua handemekepate pa mo aposolo haliweki na pitimikieki handaataęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la pua mo kaĚ±leĚ±sete haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ la halolo alotaęž‰  
\v 23 Nikitaęž‰ mo dipula da paęž‰taęž‰ opolo pomaęž‰ pitaęž‰taęž‰ potaęž‰ setepe pu pamba potaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ handeteke haenaęž‰ leeke haliweki haemaęž‰eki handomaęž‰me. Kutu pumaęž‰pate potaęž‰ lomba tukiki nane handolo pomaęž‰pate hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ na pitiaęž‰eki handomaęž‰me laa lemekeme.  
\v 24 Mo tembolo da handeteke hayeke you halimaęž‰ make mo yeni peao haemeke you haliwekimaęž‰ make koto lemeke pi opuaataęž‰ koto hau paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ekipa paęž‰laęž‰pe laa hone elekeeleke wimikime.  
\v 25 Kutu pimikipate hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ hondaęž‰ pamba aęž‰pa iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Opuaęž‰pe. Hande ikanaęž‰maęž‰ dipula mea lopaeme haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo tembolo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi walolo pitelememe laa leekeme.  
\v 26 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo hande tembolo da handeteke hayeke you halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± puaataęž‰ mo aposolo haliweki hatuku mulu pua epemekeme. Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ toopimaęž‰ iki liaamaęž‰naęž‰yeke mo haliweki yopu hatuku mea epemekeme.   
\p
\v 27 Mo aposolo haliweki hatuku mea aęž‰pa mo kaĚ±leĚ±sete haliwekinaęž‰ leke minekenaęž‰ haenaęž‰ leekeme. Kutupa mo yeni peao haemeke you haliwekinaęž‰ you halimaęž‰ iki lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰  
\v 28 Mo hande halinaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ na walaęž‰paęž‰peke laa iki paęž‰taęž‰ na lapaęž‰peke laa taęž‰e leke pi lomaęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pimieki hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke. Do Diutuseleme da paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi yamaęž‰ tumbulu bao ulaęž‰me. Kutupa make mo hande hali homeaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ niki tulaasememe laa leekeme.   
\p
\v 29 Pidamaęž‰ mo aposolo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ haliwekinaęž‰ pi ambaęž‰la na opiki Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi opuaęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 30 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki tinaęž‰ ikoko lia homaemepate nikaęž‰ apaęž‰ amedanaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu lapaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ kone paa mea tiaeyekeme.  
\v 31 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu paa mea tiaotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ Titinaęž‰ Pulaęž‰ Hali make Daęž‰taasaęž‰ Hali make ipikaęž‰ popeke kiki nane haenaęž‰ laataęž‰ Isulai wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la mina wiaataęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke hau peleme ekimanu pa tumbaenaęž‰yeke piekeme.  
\v 32 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ do hande piteleme haumanu handaataęž‰ la halolomaęž‰ haliweki halomaęž‰me. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ homeke diaęž‰me. Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ make nikanaęž‰maęž‰ make la halolomaęž‰me. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi opu halaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ Holi Sipitidi halo halaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 33 Koto lemekeeki kaĚ±leĚ±sete haliwekimaęž‰ opuaataęž‰ mineke wotu pankolo hataęž‰ mo aposolo haliweki lia homaalumeke hone wimikipate  
\v 34 kaĚ±leĚ±sete hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ Paęž‰tisi hali ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Kamaliele pitiekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande Lo Pimanu walaęž‰laęž‰ hali hataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ Ipikitaęž‰ epeke halie laa ipikaęž‰ pi lao haemekeme. Koto hali ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo kaĚ±leĚ±sete haliweki mombaęž‰la pitinaęž‰ ipiki tiao hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo aposolo haliweki hamaęž‰ nane hatuku pupe laa  
\v 35 mo kaĚ±leĚ±sete haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ dupa leekeme. Isulai haliwekio. Koto haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ puluekemaęž‰taęž‰ titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la hone wopu wiaęž‰paęž‰peke.  
\v 36 Ambaęž‰taęž‰ Teudasi tiaotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ hali tiekee hone wiekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ 400 haliweki ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± taĚ±lemekeme. Kutupa haemekepate mo hande hali lieke handaataęž‰ ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± taĚ±laĚ± haemeke haliwekitaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pea tankulupu alu alu pea pulu hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ tumiki haemekeeki alu piekeme.  
\v 37 Kotoeki pieke hoki nanetaęž‰ mo Kaęž‰lili nane hao epeeke hali Diudasitaęž‰ kapomanimaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ biki minolo haenaęž‰ Diudasi ipiki tiaeyekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ make haliweki wopu yolaęž‰ mea hatuku peekepate pa koto hali make lieke handa ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± taĚ±lemeke haliweki make taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pea tankulupu alu alu pimikime.  
\v 38 Koto ekinaęž‰ ame make do pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ do alome. Do haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ na peaęž‰paęž‰peke. Pa haenaęž‰ paape. Do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. Do haliweki ikaęž‰ piteleme hau manutaęž‰ kenke halimaęž‰ hone wia ikaęž‰ e waleaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ pa alemaęž‰ handilieke.  
\v 39 Kutu pulu piaęž‰pate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ pinaęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo haliweki bepolaapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ litaęž‰laęž‰eki handilimikie leekeme.  
\p Kamalielemaęž‰ manaęž‰ leeke pitaęž‰ mo kaĚ±leĚ±sete haliwekimaęž‰ opimikime.  
\v 40 Mo aposolo haliweki epenaęž‰ wi laęž‰ mepi peaataęž‰ yombua bao alotaęž‰ Pa hoto maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ na lapaęž‰peke laa taęž‰e taęž‰e lo laataęž‰ pao da tapaemekeme.  
\v 41 Mo aposolo haliwekitaęž‰ kaĚ±leĚ±sete haliweki minaęž‰paęž‰lao pulu hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ikitaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ tanda paęž‰laęž‰eki anaęž‰naęž‰ meaęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me laa iki paęž‰taęž‰ hone wieke ekinaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ wopu homolo hataęž‰ pemekeme.  
\v 42 Kutupa tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ make wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰manu make mo haliwekimaęž‰ hande Yesutaęž‰ otaęž‰ Ketiso halaęž‰me laa mo Pi Seliapo nate paeyao walaęž‰tiki pu haemekeme.   
\c 6  
\s1 Mo tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ wataake hataęž‰ haliweki  
\p
\v 1 Koto natenaęž‰taęž‰ mo Yesunaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki daeyaeyekeme. Mo Kitiki pi lo haemeke Diu wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo teke da paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke Diu wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kosaęž‰piki wandaęž‰sunu ne anaęž‰naęž‰ na telipitolo hataęž‰ honditi pitelememe laa pi lemekeme.  
\v 2 Mo 12 haliwekimaęž‰ mo Ketiso haliweki paeyao wi la alotaęž‰ Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi walolomaęž‰eki minaęž‰paęž‰lao ne telipaomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me lemekeme.  
\v 3 Koto ekinaęž‰ kame titio. Hali paeyao watake hataęž‰ hali Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ tumbulaęž‰ hali hone wopu u halaęž‰ hali kutupa koto hali manumaęž‰ do ne telipatiki pinaęž‰ mimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ mea haenaęž‰ lolumeke lemekeme.  
\v 4 Kutupa nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi paa walolo ombu halumeke lemekeme.   
\p
\v 5 Koto lemeke ekinaęž‰ mo Ketiso hali paeyao taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ wopu homa mimiki haliwekitaęž‰ Sidipeni Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi wopu miniki hataęž‰ make Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ tumba hayeke halie. Kutupa Pilipi Polokotasi Nikano Timono Pamenasi Nikolasi make Aęž‰ndioko hali kone Diu haliwekinaęž‰ hau mieke halie.  
\v 6 Do haliwekitaęž‰ hatuku pua mo aposolo haliwekinaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ aęž‰pa yeni pitolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ kiki mo haliwekinaęž‰ younaęž‰ wimikime.   
\p
\v 7 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi paa mea aęž‰meiyao kutupa Diutuseleme da nane mo disaipolo wandaęž‰hali make aneke hapu daeyao kutupa mandane yeni peao haemeke haliweki wopu make mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi opua Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao haemekeme.   
\s1 Sidipeni daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ minimikieki  
\p
\v 8 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ make wele paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ make Sidipenitaęž‰ tumbiekeme. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ wele paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu make na hando haemeke ekimanu make pu tia pomiekeme.  
\v 9 Kutu piekepate mo kaęž‰ndaęž‰ pikieki minaęž‰paęž‰lao pi hotu haemeke da paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke haliweki mandaneeki make kutupa Saitini haliweki make Aęž‰lekesaęž‰ndia haliweki make kutupa mandane Silisia haliweki make Eisia haliweki make mandake paęž‰taęž‰ mombaęž‰la hataęž‰ Sidipeni ameĚ±leĚ± pi yokaęž‰ alu pimikime.  
\v 10 Kutu pimikipate Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ wele peaaso haenaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone epekeeki wia hataęž‰ pi laęž‰tiki pieke ekitaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ bepolaapeke na yekeme.  
\v 11 Kutupa mo haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone lomba mandane haliweki mea Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ dupa lapaęž‰peke. Do halimaęž‰taęž‰ Mosesi paęž‰taęž‰ make Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ make hoke pi leaęž‰ halie laa aęž‰pa lapaęž‰peke lemekeme.  
\v 12 Kutupa mo haliwekimaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali make tondiki haliweki make wape pea walaęž‰tiki pu haemeke haliweki make sutiaemeke handaataęž‰ Sidipeni pua minataęž‰ kaĚ±leĚ±sete haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ yolaęž‰ mea pemekeme.  
\v 13 Kutupa hande laęž‰ wimiki tupaęž‰ mo yayapiki wekitisi haliwekimaęž‰ tiao alotaęž‰ Do halitaęž‰ do yakopiki tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ make hande Lo Pimanu paęž‰taęž‰ make hoke pi lo halaęž‰ halie lemekeme.  
\v 14 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ dupa leeke opumaęž‰me. Mo Naęž‰saęž‰tete hali Yesumaęž‰ do da teke hoeyao Mosesimaęž‰ waleeke ekimanu make topo pea panakeeki walieke leaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ peaęž‰maęž‰ opumaęž‰me lemekeme.  
\v 15 Kutupa mo kaĚ±leĚ±sete haliweki paeyaomaęž‰ ipiki handa hake wimikipate ipikaęž‰ leke popeleketaęž‰ enisolonaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ handemekeme.   
\c 7  
\s1 Sidipenimaęž‰ pi leekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Mo yeni peao haemeke you haliwekinaęž‰ you halimaęž‰ Sidipeni paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Koto aleme pitaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alemepe laa leekeme.   
\p
\v 2 Sidipenimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ya kame apaęž‰manuo. IĚ±maęž‰ alo pi opuaęž‰pe. Nikaęž‰ tapake kini paęž‰laęž‰ hali Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Hatani nane aĚ±iĚ± na halo peeke pitaęž‰ mo Mesopoteimia nane pa haenaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande manda hataęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± peao halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰taęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ peneme yao aęž‰pa hayekeme.  
\v 3 Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ tapake nakaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali make nakaęž‰ kenke make minaęž‰paęž‰laotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ walo polo kenke paęž‰taęž‰ puaęž‰peke leekeme.  
\v 4 Koto leeke pi opuaataęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ mo Koledia wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ kenke minaęž‰paęž‰laotaęž‰ hande Hatani nane halo peekeme. Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ateke homao haenaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ ame do iki haleme kenke paęž‰taęž‰ da yoka epenaęž‰ leekeme.   
\p
\v 5 Koto pitaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kenke winaęž‰yeke kenke hosiki alesiki kone maęž‰ndaęž‰ na haleekepate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ pi laęž‰ witolo Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ hoki nane hatiki polo peleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make otaęž‰ kulueke laa leekeme. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ do pi laęž‰ wieke natenaęž‰taęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ weki maęž‰ndaęž‰ make na mendiki hayeke dinaęž‰ leekeme.  
\v 6 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pi dupa leekeme. Nakaęž‰ hoki nane halo peleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ kenke maęž‰ndaęž‰ nane halo pelimikie. Koto kenke nane pua hataęž‰taęž‰ pa hameke e pokaaso tanda muaęž‰tiki pulu hataęž‰taęž‰ bapi 400 bapimanu hao halimikie.   
\p
\v 7 Kutu pulu pelemepatetaęž‰ mo e pa hameke pokaape lolo peleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ panisi peaalueke laa kutupa wetepenaęž‰ nakaęž‰ tapake wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ koto kenke nane minaęž‰paęž‰lao do hale paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao yeni pilimikie laa leekeme.  
\v 8 Koto hoki nanetaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pi laęž‰ wiekeeki tombo witolo hataęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ sekemesaisi hau waleekeme. Kutupa haenaęž‰taęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Aisaęž‰ke mendia haenaęž‰ pulaęž‰ homeke paeyeketaęž‰ Aisaęž‰ke paęž‰taęž‰ sekemesaisi hau peayekeme. Kutupa Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰taęž‰ Dieikope paęž‰taęž‰ sekemesaisi hau piekeme. Kutupa Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande tapake tapake kini pieke 12 haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ sekemesaisi hau peayekeme.   
\p
\v 9 Mo hande tapake tapake kini pieke haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ Diosepe paęž‰taęž‰ honditi pitolo hataęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ Idiepi nane hataęž‰ pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ hali halo penaęž‰yeke mani muluekemaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hambenaęž‰ lemekeme. Kutu pimikipate Kodaęž‰ ipiki yaapo hataęž‰taęž‰  
\v 10 ipikaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu paeyao minolo haenaęž‰ kone Kodaęž‰maęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ handeteke hayekeme. Diosepetaęž‰ mo Idiepi you hali Petou paęž‰taęž‰ pua hayeke dinaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ kipa baake hone wiki hali make hone lenkenaęž‰ pea wiki hali make haenaęž‰ leekeme. Kutu pieke ekimaęž‰ Petoumaęž‰ Diosepetaęž‰ Idiepi nane kapomani you hali pitinaęž‰ laataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ da kenkemanu paeyao make handeteke haenaęž‰ leekeme.  
\v 11 Koto hoki nanetaęž‰ mo Idiepi Keinani kenke yaapo paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ teaęž‰ ki tieke epeeke handaataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homa yapemekeme. Nikaęž‰ apaęž‰mei amedamaęž‰taęž‰ nemanu maęž‰ndaęž‰ na handaęž‰ wimikime.  
\v 12 Koto ekinaęž‰ Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ Idiepi nane nemanu ulaęž‰me lemekeeki opuaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ eiyeketiti hande nikaęž‰ apaęž‰mei ameda kone titi panake paęž‰taęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ tapaeyekeme.   
\p
\v 13 Pa hoto yaapo peao paa tapaeyeke pitaęž‰taęž‰ Diosepemaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hameketiti paęž‰taęž‰ ipiki peneme yao la haleekeme. Kutu pieketaęž‰ Petoumaęž‰ Diosepe ipikaęž‰ tapake wandaęž‰halie lemeke ekitaęž‰ opua hone wiekeme.  
\v 14 Koto ekinaęž‰ Diosepemaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ateke Dieikope paęž‰taęž‰ pi laęž‰ moneaaso alotaęž‰ Neke make neke ameĚ±leĚ± tapake wandaęž‰hali paeyao make Idiepi nane ipupe laa leekeme. Mo wandaęž‰hali paeyaotaęž‰ 75 wandaęž‰hali haemekeme.  
\v 15 Kutupa Dieikope Idiepi nane pua haotaęž‰ ipiki make nikaęž‰ apaęž‰mei ameda make koto paęž‰taęž‰ hao homemekeme.  
\v 16 Ikaęž‰ toko manutaęž‰ Sekeme kenke paęž‰taęž‰ mea pua hoimikime. Koto hali lapaęž‰ pu haemeke kenketaęž‰ ambaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ Heimonaęž‰ tapake paęž‰taęž‰ manimaęž‰ hambeeke kenkee.   
\p
\v 17 Hande Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ pi laęž‰ wiekeeki otaęž‰ yao peaalo pieke nate mo Idiepi nane nikaęž‰ tapake wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ tapake tieke kone haemekeme.  
\v 18 Koto pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ you hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ tiao Idiepi wandaęž‰hali handeteke hayekepate Diosepe hayekeeki ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ na handeekeme.  
\v 19 Nikaęž‰ tapake wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ makeatiki pea puki tandamaęž‰ homaatiki piekeme. Panake hambaęž‰ mea mendimiki wekisunu da paęž‰taęž‰ na mondu wia pitinaęž‰ leke pa hamaęž‰ nane homenaęž‰yeke mondu batiki pinaęž‰ leekeme.  
\v 20 Koto pitaęž‰taęž‰ Mosesitaęž‰ epeke weki seliaposikitaęž‰ inkikimaęž‰ mendiekepate pa da tukiki nane mea mondu wia pitinaęž‰ sumbaęž‰ tepo yapeekeme.  
\v 21 Kutupa wetepenaęž‰ hamaęž‰ nane mea pua nunaęž‰ palaęž‰mbaęž‰ hao wieke alenaęž‰ Petounaęž‰ wanekemaęž‰ mea puna daeyaotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weki kone haenaęž‰ leekeme.  
\v 22 Mosesimaęž‰taęž‰ mo Idiepi haliwekimaęž‰ epeke honemanu wia pu haemekeeki paeyao sukulu peataęž‰ pi pi lo haemeke ekimanu make peaęž‰peke ekimanu make ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ handaęž‰ wia pitolo hataęž‰ hali tieke hayekeme.   
\p
\v 23 Mosesitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ bapi 40 paeyeketaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Isulai tapake wandaęž‰hali handolo peekeme.  
\v 24 Idiepi hali homekemaęž‰ Isulai hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ liekeeki Mosesimaęž‰ handaataęž‰ mo hali tambaęž‰ minolo hataęž‰ mo Idiepi hali otaęž‰ liekeme.  
\v 25 Mosesi ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± maęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ iki mea tapaano paęž‰laęž‰me laataęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ koto hone witelememe hone wiekepate mo Isulai wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ koto hone na wimikime.  
\v 26 Da maęž‰ndaęž‰ kelepeeketaęž‰ Isulai hali yaapo aęž‰ndaęž‰ pitolo haepekeeki Mosesimaęž‰ handaataęž‰ pua saęž‰saęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Hali yaapo opuaęž‰pe laa Ipilikitaęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰e. Ekipeke ipilikaęž‰ kone aęž‰ndaęž‰ pitelepepe laa leekeme.  
\v 27 Koto leekepate mo hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ yumbieke halimaęž‰ Mosesi pendulu baaso alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ nikaęž‰ you hali hataęž‰ pi yokaalu peaalo paęž‰laęž‰ halitaęž‰ epimaęž‰ neke mea haenaęž‰ leaęž‰pe.  
\v 28 Hande nakanaęž‰maęž‰ ambaneke mo Idiepi hali litolo pi tupaęž‰ IĚ± make luekemaęž‰ alepe laa leekeme.  
\v 29 Mosesimaęž‰ koto leeke pi opuaataęž‰ Idiepi nane minaęž‰paęž‰lao pindipa pua mo Midiani nane halo peekeme. Koto paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰taęž‰ weki yaapo mondu wiekeme.   
\p
\v 30 Bapi 40 yapeeketaęž‰ Mosesitaęž‰ mo Sainai pote teke paęž‰taęž‰ hapu hayeke alenaęž‰ haenaęž‰taęž‰ ti to hayeke alenaęž‰ mo ti uleke paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ enisolo maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ Mosesi paęž‰taęž‰ peneme yao waleekeme.  
\v 31 Mosesimaęž‰ leke opo handake witolo hataęž‰ mo ti teke paęž‰taęž‰ wotu handuluekemaęž‰ peekepate Tekehalimaęž‰ leeke pi make opiekeme dupa.  
\v 32 IĚ±taęž‰ nakaęž‰ apaęž‰mei amedanaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ halome laataęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ Aisaęž‰ke Dieikope amedanaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ halome la leekeme. Mosesimaęž‰ pututumaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ na handaęž‰liaeyekeme.  
\v 33 Mo hande Tekehalimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neke hale kenketaęž‰ yakopiki kenkee. Nakaęž‰ anke dake holo wie.  
\v 34 Ya Idiepi nane haleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ tanda tieke mu haleme ekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ handolome. Ikaęž‰ eĚ± alo hataęž‰ kememe kememe pu halemeeki manutaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ opuaataęž‰ iki tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ holaęž‰paęž‰niaalo aęž‰pa puaęž‰me. Neke do paęž‰taęž‰ leke epoe la alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ mo Idiepi nane tapaalueke laa leekeme.   
\p
\v 35 Hande Isulai wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ Mosesi kiaemekeme. Neketaęž‰ nikaęž‰ you hali hataęž‰ pi yokaalu peaalo paęž‰laęž‰ hali halenaęž‰ neketaęž‰ epimaęž‰ mea haenaęž‰ leaęž‰pe laa lotaęž‰ pimikime. Koto hali konetaęž‰ you hali hataęž‰ tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ hali haenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mea tapaeyekeme. Mo enisolomaęž‰ handeteke haenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ tapaeyekeme. Hande ti to hayeke ale paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ Mosesi paęž‰taęž‰ peneme yao waleeke ekimaęž‰ tapaaso piekeme.  
\v 36 Mosesimaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali Idiepi nane minaęž‰paęž‰lao hatuku puaataęž‰ mo Idiepi nane make mo Wepiki Dawala Ikali paęž‰taęž‰ make mo hapu hayeke ale paęž‰taęž‰manu make ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ bapi 40manu mo wandaęž‰hali hatuku pominolo hataęž‰ na hando haemeke hau tieke tieke piaęž‰tiki piekeme.  
\v 37 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Isulai wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ dupa leekeme. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± tapaeyaęž‰ tupaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ potopede hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ make tapaalieke. Koto sometaęž‰ ikaęž‰ tapake hali kone tapaalieke laa leekeme.  
\v 38 Ipiki make mo Isulai wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± mo hapu hayeke alenaęž‰ mombaęž‰la haemekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ apaęž‰mei ameda ameĚ±leĚ± koto paęž‰taęž‰ hayeke halie. Mo Sainai Pote paęž‰taęž‰ hande ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pi leeke enisolo yaapo hayeke halie. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ pi niki paęž‰taęž‰ la kinaęž‰yeke Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ la haleekeme.   
\p
\v 39 Kutu piekepate nikaęž‰ apaęž‰mei amedamaęž‰ Mosesimaęž‰ leeke pi opuaęž‰peke ekitaęž‰ kiaemekeme. Idiepi nane paa laęž‰kaęž‰la polumeke hone witolo hataęž‰ Mosesi pa nane pendilaemekeme.  
\v 40 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Etoni paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ niki hatuku polo peleme kodaęž‰manu wepiae. Mo hande Idiepi nane hamono niki hatuku epeaęž‰ hali Mosesitaęž‰ hane paęž‰laęž‰pe niki na handolomaęž‰me lemekeme.  
\v 41 Koto lemeke pitaęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ kao sikimaęž‰ handeke ale wepia wiaataęž‰ koto ale paęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ lia halaataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ kone ikaęž‰ kikimaęž‰ wepieke ale taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ ne pambaemekeme.  
\v 42 Kutu pimikipate Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ iki hoki laęž‰kaęž‰laataęž‰ oli ya nane halaęž‰ hombulankaęž‰manu paęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao pa yeni pinaęž‰ leekeme. Hande buka paęž‰taęž‰ potopede haliwekimaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰eki dupa  
\q1 Isulai wandaęž‰halio. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo hapu halaęž‰ alenaęž‰ bapi 40manu hataęž‰taęž‰ kaomanu make sipisipi make lia halo haemeeki manutaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ na kimime.   
\q1
\v 43 Kutupa ikaęž‰ palai dataęž‰ mo Moleke kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ palai da kone mea tia puaataęž‰ ikaęž‰ wepia winaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ hombulankaęž‰maęž‰ handeke ale manutaęž‰ mo Lepani kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰eki kone mea tia pememe.  
\q1 Koto ale manutaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ kone ikaęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao yeni puluekemaęž‰ wepia winaęž‰ lemeke alemanue.  
\q1 Koto peleme ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ikitaęž‰ mo Baęž‰biloni nane ankulao poemenaęž‰ mea tapaalueke laa leekeme.   
\p
\v 44 Nikaęž‰ apaęž‰mei amedamaęž‰taęž‰ mo hapu hayeke alenaęž‰ haemeke pitaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ hayeke palai dataęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ hayekeme. Koto dataęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Mosesi paęž‰taęž‰ pi la halolo hataęž‰ pikisa make waleeke tupaęž‰ Mosesimaęž‰ aęž‰eyaenaęž‰ leekeme.  
\v 45 Kutupa hao hao pea wetepenaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ apaęž‰mei amedamaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande palai dataęž‰ ikaęž‰ apaęž‰ ameda paęž‰taęž‰ meataęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone mea tia puaęž‰tiki pimikime. Diosua make mandakenaęž‰ puaataęž‰ hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ tolu lieke tapake wandaęž‰halimanu ikaęž‰ kenke paęž‰taęž‰la minolo hataęž‰ mea tia pemekeme. Kutupa koto kenke paęž‰taęž‰ mo palai da aęž‰eya pa ha pelia haenaęž‰ kone Deipidi make opolo aęž‰pa hayekeme.  
\v 46 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo Deipidinaęž‰ hayeke haumanu handaataęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homeekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ Deipidimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰mei hali Dieikopenaęž‰ tapake ikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ da aęž‰eyaluekemaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ aęž‰eyaano lae laa honke leekeme.  
\v 47 Koto leekepate Solomonomaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ da aęž‰eyaeyekeme.   
\p
\v 48 Kutu piekepate otaęž‰ oli manda halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰taęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ kikimaęž‰ aęž‰eyaaseme da paęž‰taęž‰manu na hao halaęž‰me. Koto mo hande potopede halimaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰   
\q1
\v 49 IĚ±taęž‰ hepeni nane hataęž‰ kilu tombuao hao halome laataęž‰  
\q1 kenketaęž‰ yaka anke tapaęž‰pao hao halo alee laa Tekehalimaęž‰ alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\q1 Yaka dataęž‰ ekipiki da aęž‰eyaluekemaęž‰ alemepe.  
\q1 IĚ± hoto pitulu polo dataęž‰ hando paęž‰taęž‰ yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe.   
\q1
\v 50 Koto alemanu paeyaotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ya kone na wopua winaęž‰ lolope laa leekeme.   
\p
\v 51 Iki make hoi pea hao haleme haliwekio. Ikaęž‰ puki manutaęž‰ pi na opitaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ handelememe. Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi ale opuaęž‰peke ekitaęž‰ katake pokeeke hali leke hao halememe. Hande ikaęž‰ apaęž‰mei amedamaęž‰ mo Holi Sipitidi kiayeke tupaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make kiatiki pitelememe.  
\v 52 Ikaęž‰ apaęž‰mei amedamaęž‰taęž‰ potopede hali homeke paęž‰taęž‰ kone tanda na halemekepe. Hande Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ tikitiki yao halaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ Hali epolo piekeeki la haleeke haliwekitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ tapaeyeke haliweki kone ikaęž‰ apaęž‰mei amedamaęž‰ limikime. Ame make ikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto Hali aęž‰ndaęž‰ lomba limime.  
\v 53 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Lo Pi manutaęž‰ enisolo manumaęž‰ lopaęž‰niao kiekepate ikitaęž‰ kieke meleme haliweki halemepate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto pi manutaęž‰ na opiki pa halememe laa leekeme.   
\s1 Sidipeni toopimaęž‰ limikieki  
\p
\v 54 Koto leekeeki opua mo haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ sokaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ wotu homolo hataęž‰ kake nokaęž‰pa haemekepate  
\v 55 Sidipeni Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ tumba hake halimaęž‰ oli ya paęž‰taęž‰ handaęž‰liao Kodaęž‰naęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± pitaęž‰laęž‰eki make Yesutaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ popeke nane kikinaęž‰ tiao hayaęž‰eki make handolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\v 56 Handaęž‰pe. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ oli ya akolopaęž‰ lumbaęž‰lu bao kutupa Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke Kodaęž‰naęž‰ popeke nane kikinaęž‰ oli halaęž‰eki handolome leekeme.  
\v 57 Koto leekepate mo haliwekimaęž‰ taęž‰e taęž‰e lo laa ikaęž‰ katake aęž‰mba kutupa mandake dinaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ±ya pua mo hali yolaęž‰ mea pua  
\v 58 da minaęž‰paęž‰lao pua toopimaęž‰ limikime. Kutupa mo wekitisi haliwekinaęž‰ dau manutaęž‰ wekihali maęž‰ndaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Solo koto halinaęž‰ anke teke paęž‰taęž‰ holo pambaataęž‰  
\v 59 kutupa toopimaęž‰ litolo haenaęž‰ Sidipenimaęž‰ yeni pitolo alotaęž‰ Tekehali Yesuo. Yaka temoko nakanaęž‰maęž‰ handaęž‰ mie leekeme.  
\v 60 Kutupa pa tumiki yotuao pitaęž‰ anekemaęž‰ eĚ± alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Do haliwekimaęž‰ hoke hau piteleme ekitaęž‰ pa na winaęž‰ leke nakanaęž‰maęž‰ paeyaapeke leekeme. Kotoeki lo paeyaotaęž‰ homeekeme.   
\c 8  
\s1 Solomaęž‰ siosi wandaęž‰hali tanda haleekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Sidipeni limiki ekitaęž‰ Solomaęž‰ linaęž‰e hone wiekeme. Koto limiki pitaęž‰ kone mo Diutuseleme nane haemeke siosi wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ tanda wotu mulu pimikieki kini pea mimikime. Kutu pieke handa Ketiso wandaęž‰hali paeyaotaęž‰ mo Diudia Sametia koto potopinisi yaapo paęž‰taęž‰manu haloendi pimikipate mo aposolo haliwekitaęž‰ Diutuseleme nane pa ha pelia haemekeme.  
\v 2 Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao yeni pu haemeke mandane haliwekimaęž‰ Sidipeni toko mea pua hoitolo hataęž‰ eĚ± tieke lemekeme.   
\p
\v 3 Kutu pimikipate Solomaęž‰ siosi wandaęž‰hali hoeyaaluekemaęž‰ taapeekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ da maęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pominolo hataęž‰ siosi wandaęž‰hali kiki yolaęž‰ mea hamaęž‰ nane mea batiki pea dipula mea lopatiki piekeme.   
\s1 Mo hande Pi Seliapo Sametia nane waleekeeki  
\p
\v 4 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo hande pindipa taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pea pemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo hande Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Pi Seliapo latia tia pomimikime.  
\v 5 Pilipimaęž‰ mo Sametia daoni nane pua Ketisonaęž‰ pi mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ waleekeme.  
\v 6 Kutupa mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ leeke pi opuaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wele pieke ekimanu hando pitolo hataęž‰taęž‰ peaęž‰maęž‰ homeke hone witolo hataęž‰ Pilipimaęž‰ leeke pi opimikime.  
\v 7 Wandaęž‰hali wopunaęž‰ weleke paęž‰taęž‰ pitimiki hoke temokomanu eĚ± wi laęž‰ paleke paleke pea opolu bepi pea yapemekeeki make kiki anke homa pa wieke wandaęž‰hali wopu make ankenaęž‰ puaęž‰peke na yeke wandaęž‰hali wopu make tiaemekeeki handolotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi opimikime.  
\v 8 Kutupa koto daoni paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ tieke homo haemekeme.   
\p
\v 9 Kutu piekepate hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Saimonotaęž‰ oni da ambaęž‰ yopua hataęž‰ tiĚ±oĚ± haumanu mokaęž‰laęž‰ hande hande pitolo hataęž‰ mo Sametia wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ leke mea opaaso hataęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kutu pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ Tieke halueke hone wiekeme.  
\v 10 Mo wandaęž‰hali tieke tiekemaęž‰ make hosiki wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ make mo leeke ekimanu opitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do halinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰eki kone yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me lemekeme.  
\v 11 Mo haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo tiĚ±oĚ± halimaęž‰ nate paeyao piaęž‰tiki pieke ekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ leke opo handake wiaęž‰tiki pitolo hataęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ pi opuaęž‰tiki pimikime.  
\v 12 Kutu piekepate wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Pilipimaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ epeke Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ pi seliapo Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ biki tonkaęž‰naęž‰ pua waleekeeki paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaemeke handaataęž‰ kotaęž‰ haliweki make wandaęž‰weki make paeyao bapitaisi pimikime.  
\v 13 Kutupa Saimono make Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi minolo haenaęž‰ ipiki bapitaisi peaeyekeme. Kutupa Saimonotaęž‰ Pilipi yaapo hataęž‰ mo wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu make na hando haemeke ekimanu make hando haotaęž‰ leke opaęž‰ minaęž‰ bepi piekeme.   
\p
\v 14 Kutupa mo Diutuseleme da haemeke aposolo haliwekimaęž‰ Sametia wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi mineleme pi opu haotaęž‰ Pida Dioni yaapo pupaęž‰ laa tapaemekeme.  
\v 15 Kutupa mo hande Pida Dioni yaapo Sametia da opolo puataęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Holi Sipitidi minaęž‰yeke yeni pua pipikime.  
\v 16 Pa ekipeke mo Holi Sipitiditaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ weleke paęž‰taęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na aęž‰pa pitiekeme. Mo ikaęž‰ bapitaisi pimiki hau make Tekehali Yesunaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ homeke bapitaisi pimikime.  
\v 17 Pida Dioni yaapomaęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ kiki mo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ younaęž‰ wia hataęž‰ yeni pipiki handa Holi Sipitiditaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ weleke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa pitiekeme.   
\p
\v 18 Kutupa Saimonomaęž‰ mo aposolo hali yaapomaęž‰ kiki wieke ekinaęž‰ hande Holi Sipitidi epeekeeki handolo hataęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ manimanu mutia aęž‰pa wia hataęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\v 19 IĚ±maęž‰ make yaka kiki hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ younaęž‰ uaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ Holi Sipitidi minaęž‰ loaęž‰me do wele pitaęž‰laęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ kipe leekeme.   
\p
\v 20 Koto leekepate Pidamaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ pa kitaęž‰laęž‰ ale nakaęž‰ honemaęž‰ hambuluekemaęž‰ hone witele ekinaęž‰ neke tonkaęž‰naęž‰ nakaęž‰ mani tonkaęž‰naęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hoeyaenaęž‰e.  
\v 21 Du pitele ekinaęž‰ neketaęž‰ niki ameĚ±leĚ± na hake. Pa ekipeke nakaęž‰ pukitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ tikitiki na paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 22 Do hoke hau pi ekinaęž‰ hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la wiaataęž‰ yeni peaęž‰peke. Tekehalimaęž‰ nakaęž‰ hoke hone witele ekimanu paa mea tombualiepe mataęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 23 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ neketaęž‰ teto pitaęž‰laęž‰ alemaęž‰ handeleke handolome. Kutupa nakaęž‰ hoke hau pitele ekimaęž‰ neke tonkao ulaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 24 Saimonomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ koto ale pimanu IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰paapaęž‰naęž‰ Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ yeni peae leekeme.   
\p
\v 25 Kutupa Pida Dioni yaapomaęž‰ mo Tekehalinaęž‰ pi walolo hataęž‰ la halaęž‰tiki peaataęž‰ mo Diutuseleme da nane paa laęž‰kaęž‰la pulu hataęž‰ mandane Sametia da paęž‰taęž‰manu mo Pi Seliapo walaęž‰tia tia pepekeme.   
\s1 Pilipi mo Idiopia kapomani hali yaapo  
\p
\v 26 Tekehalinaęž‰ enisolomaęž‰ Pilipi paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tiao. Oni Diutuseleme kini pea Kasa nane pulaęž‰ potaęž‰ teli mea pue leekeme. Koto potaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ hapu hayeke ale tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ peeke potaęž‰e.  
\v 27 Kutupa Pilipi tiaotaęž‰ peekeme. Pulu haenaęž‰taęž‰ mo potaęž‰naęž‰ Idiopia yuniki hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ mo Idiopia Kuini wandaęž‰naęž‰ mani paeyao handeteke hae leeke hali tieke mandaęž‰hande piekeme.  
\v 28 Mo halitaęž‰ Diutuseleme da nane Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pulu yopua ipikaęž‰ da laęž‰kaęž‰la yopulu piekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ mo hosimaęž‰ yolaęž‰laęž‰ bokisi pita potaęž‰naęž‰ pulu hataęž‰ potopede hali Aisayamaęž‰ wape piekeeki yataęž‰po pitiekeme.  
\v 29 Kutupa mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ Pilipi paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo hosimaęž‰ yola yopulaęž‰ ale teke paęž‰taęž‰ leke pua pitaęž‰peke leekeme.  
\v 30 Koto ekinaęž‰ Pilipi aĚ±iĚ±ya pua mo hali paęž‰taęž‰ peekepate mo halimaęž‰ mo Aisayamaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ buka yataęž‰polo pitiekeeki opua alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ koto yataęž‰pele ekitaęž‰ hone witelepe leekeme.   
\p
\v 31 Mo halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na waleke haenaęž‰ ekipa hone wiono alepe leekeme. Kutupa mo halimaęž‰ Pilipi paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do IĚ± pilu paęž‰taęž‰ lopulao pitupanaęž‰ epoe leekeme.  
\v 32 Mo hande halimaęž‰ mo Baibolo bukanaęž‰ yataęž‰polo pitieke ekitaęž‰ doeki yeekeme.  
\q1 Ipikitaęž‰ sipisipi pitaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ kia kia pi na leekeme.  
\q1 Kutupa mo sipisipimaęž‰ mo itiki tunkulu halaęž‰ halinaęž‰ leke popeleke nane aęž‰pa haenaęž‰ kake aęž‰mbaaso hataęž‰ pi na laęž‰lie tupaęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kake na aĚ±aĚ± leekeme.   
\q1
\v 33 Ipikaęž‰ hande tieke hayekeeki mea lopao pitaęž‰taęž‰ pi yokaalu epeke tupaęž‰ na pimikime.  
\q1 Kutupa ipikaęž‰ kini pu mieke tapake epimaęž‰ lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰pe.  
\q1 Ipikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hoeyaasaęž‰me  
\m laęž‰laęž‰eki yataęž‰polo pitiekeme.   
\p
\v 34 Kutupa mo hande kapomani halimaęž‰ Pilipi paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do potopede halimaęž‰taęž‰ pilisi epi paęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰pe leekeme. Ipikaęž‰ kone alaęž‰pe o maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰pe leekeme.  
\v 35 Koto leeke Pilipimaęž‰ pi alo hataęž‰taęž‰ mo Baibolo buka aĚ±iĚ± koto kone yataęž‰peaęž‰ ekimanu paęž‰taęž‰ kini pea mo some paęž‰taęž‰ Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ epeke Pi Seliapo la haleekeme.  
\v 36 Ametaęž‰ mo potaęž‰ hokulunaęž‰ pu hao ikali paęž‰taęž‰ opolo pua kutupa mo yuniki halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Handaęž‰e. Ikali doe leekeme. Epimaęž‰ ya bapitaisi pulu poloeki saęž‰saęž‰ piliepe leekeme.  
\v 37 [Kutupa Pilipimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ puki paeyaomaęž‰ hone wikinaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakaęž‰e leekeme. Kutupa mo halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ Yesu Ketisotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeke halaęž‰me hone witolome leekeme.]   
\p
\v 38 Kutupa mo hande hosimaęž‰ yola yopulaęž‰ ale dataiwa hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Koto pate hae laa Pilipi mo hali yaapo telipinaęž‰ ikali paęž‰taęž‰ pua kutupa Pilipimaęž‰ hande hali bapitaisi peaeyekeme.  
\v 39 Kutu piekepate ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo ikali minaęž‰paęž‰lao yopulu haenaęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ Sipitidimaęž‰ Pilipitaęž‰ pa aęž‰pa aĚ±iĚ± tambaęž‰ mea peekeme. Kutupa mo bapitaisi pieke halimaęž‰ Pilipi otaęž‰ paa na handeekepate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰paleke ipikaęž‰ da peekeme  
\v 40 Kutu piekepate Pilipitaęž‰ Aęž‰sidoti da paęž‰taęž‰ hao pulu hataęž‰ mandane damanu paęž‰taęž‰ mo Pi Seliapo walomaęž‰ walomaęž‰ putialo hataęž‰ Sesatia nane peekeme.   
\c 9  
\s1 Solonaęž‰ hone laęž‰kaęž‰la miniekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Solomaęž‰ wese wese alo hataęž‰ mo Tekehalinaęž‰ disaipolo wandaęž‰hali tolu lutia pomiekeme.  
\v 2 Kutu putia mo yeni peao haemeke you haliwekinaęž‰ you hali paęž‰taęž‰ pua alotaęž‰ Mo Damasikasi nane pi hotu haleme damanu paęž‰taęž‰ do hande panake hau piteleme wandaęž‰hali dipula mea Diutuseleme nane mea ipuluekemaęž‰ loaęž‰maęž‰ pase kie laa pua honke leekeme.  
\v 3 Solotaęž‰ Damasikasi nane polueke laa potaęž‰naęž‰ pulu haenaęž‰ oli ya nanemaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± tieke aęž‰pa mo some dupao aęž‰pa to hopaęž‰liaeyekeme.  
\v 4 Kutupa mo some kenkenaęž‰ hondaęž‰pa topopi lopolo hataęž‰ hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make opiekepate alotaęž‰ Soloo. Soloo. Ekipeke IĚ± yaapo aęž‰ndaęž‰ litelepe leekeme.  
\v 5 Kutupa Solomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Neketaęž‰ epiyaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe leekeme. Mo hande pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰makemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Yesue. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± yaapo aęž‰ndaęž‰ liteleke handa loaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 6 Tiao oni da nane nakaęž‰ pulu peleeki loluekemaęž‰ pue leekeme.   
\p
\v 7 Kutupa mo Solo ameĚ±leĚ± epemeke haliweki otaęž‰ nunu nunu pisiki make otaęž‰ na leke hataęž‰ mo leeke pi homeke opiekepate maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ na handemekeme.  
\v 8 Solo oni kenke minaęž‰paęž‰lao tiao ipikaęž‰ leketaęž‰ ki leekepate otaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na handeeke handa hali mandane hatiki mandane hatiki pea hatuku oni Damasikasi da paęž‰taęž‰ pemekeme.  
\v 9 Kutupa Solotaęž‰ ikali ne make na neke alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ make na handeke hoto tepo oni Damasikasi da paęž‰taęž‰ wiekeme.   
\p
\v 10 Kutupa oni Damasikasi Ketiso hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Aęž‰naęž‰naisi hayekeme. Tekehalimaęž‰ upamaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aęž‰naęž‰naisio. Kutupa Aęž‰naęž‰naisimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. IĚ±taęž‰ do pilume leekeme.  
\v 11 Kutupa Tekehalimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tiao. Oni potaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Tikitikipiki potaęž‰ yolaęž‰ mea pua Diudasinaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ pua Tasaęž‰si hali Solotaęž‰ hando paęž‰taęž‰ pilaęž‰pe laa lotaęž‰ piaęž‰pekee. Ipikitaęž‰ yeni koto pitolo pilaęž‰ handaęž‰e leekeme.  
\v 12 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ biki Aęž‰naęž‰naisi aęž‰pa ipikaęž‰ kiki yaka younaęž‰ aęž‰pa wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ ya leke ki leliekee laa ambaęž‰ handeaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 13 Aęž‰naęž‰naisimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Do halitaęž‰ nakaęž‰ Diutuseleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ tanda tanda halaęž‰laęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰pa laęž‰tiki pu haleke opu halome leekeme.  
\v 14 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo yeni peao haleme teke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ pase mea wia hataęž‰ do nakaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ pi milie Damasikasi wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ tanda tanda halolo pitaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 15 Koto leekepate Tekehalimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Pue. Do halitaęž‰ yaka ambaęž‰ molo halimaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme. Yaka bikitaęž‰ Diendaili wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ make kini haliwekimaęž‰ make Isulai wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ make opinaęž‰ puaęž‰maęž‰ pue leekeme.  
\v 16 IĚ±maęž‰ yaka haunaęž‰ tanda paęž‰laęž‰eki minaęž‰ la waluekemaęž‰ pue leekeme.   
\p
\v 17 Koto ekinaęž‰ Aęž‰naęž‰naisi pua da paęž‰taęž‰ opolo peekeme. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ kiki Solonaęž‰ younaęž‰ pua witolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Solo ya kameo. Tekehali Yesu mo potaęž‰naęž‰ ipulu halenaęž‰ epeeke hande Yesumaęž‰ nakaęž‰ leke paa kilao Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ tumba halenaęž‰ yeke IĚ± tapaeyaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 18 Kutupa koto kone mo taęž‰peli oĚ±maęž‰ handeke ale manumaęž‰ leke tombuao hao londaęž‰laęž‰pa lopeke nono piekeme. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ leke paa ki leekeme. Kutupa koto kone tiao pua bapitaisi piekeme.  
\v 19 Kutupa ne tambaęž‰ mea nolo yapeeke dinaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ honkopu paa hao epeekeme.  
\s1 Solomaęž‰ Damasikasi hataęž‰ pi waleekeeki  
\p Solotaęž‰ Damasikasi da hao halaęž‰ Ketiso haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± hosiki hayekeme.  
\v 20 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto kone Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ pi mo pi hotu haemeke da paęž‰taęž‰ walolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyekee leekeme.  
\v 21 Mo opimiki haliwekitaęž‰ leke wopu opaęž‰ alu alu pimikime. Kutupa alotaęž‰ Do hali diaęž‰yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe. Mo hande Diutuseleme da paęž‰taęž‰ hande some Yesunaęž‰ biki laa yeni pimi wandaęž‰hali tanda tanda haleaęž‰ hali diaęž‰yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe. Aowe. Ipikitaęž‰ do epaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo kutupiki wandaęž‰hali mea tonkao hatuku mo yeni peao haleme teke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ mea poluekemaęž‰ aęž‰pa paęž‰laęž‰me lemekeme.  
\v 22 Kutu piekepate Solomaęž‰taęž‰ pi waluekemaęž‰ wele wopu piekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ otaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Ketisoe laa otaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ peneme yao waleeke mandane pi manutaęž‰ mo Damasikasi da haleme Diu haliwekimaęž‰ pi homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hombo pealuekemaęž‰ anaęž‰ na pimikime.   
\p
\v 23 Hosiki hao hao pea wetepenaęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ Solo luekemaęž‰ tome tome pambemekepate mo hande lemeke ekitaęž‰ Solomaęž‰ ambaęž‰ opiekeme.  
\v 24 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ mo potaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ timba andusaęž‰ andusaęž‰ make paĚ±aĚ±naęž‰ make haemekeme.  
\v 25 Kutu pimikipate disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ mo peiyekeeki mea ankulao Solotaęž‰ basekedenaęž‰ pitinaęž‰ laataęž‰ mea lopaęž‰niaemekeme.   
\s1 Solo Diutuseleme hayekeeki  
\p
\v 26 Mo Diutuseleme da nane opolo aęž‰pa mo disaipolo wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± apaęž‰tao haluekemaęž‰ piekepate mo Ketiso haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ Ipikitaęž‰ disaipolo hali diaęž‰me hone witolo hataęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homemekeme.  
\v 27 Kutupa Banabasimaęž‰ Solotaęž‰ mo aposolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku pua mo Tekehalimaęž‰ potaęž‰naęž‰ Solo paęž‰taęž‰ peneme yaeyaęž‰eki make pi leekeeki make la haleekeme. Kutupa oli Damasikasi da hataęž‰ Solomaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ biki aęž‰mbao na leke pi waleekeeki make mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ la haleekeme.  
\v 28 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± hataęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambaęž‰tiki opolu batiki piekeme.  
\v 29 Solotaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homeke mo Tekehalinaęž‰ biki laa pi walaęž‰tiki piekeme. Kutupa pi pi laęž‰tiki pitolo hataęž‰ mo Kitiki pi lo haemeke Diu wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± make pi la alu alu puaęž‰tiki pomiekepate mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ Solo lu pie hone wimikime.  
\v 30 Mo hameke titimaęž‰ kotoeki opu haotaęž‰ Solotaęž‰ Sesatia nane hatuku pua Tasaęž‰si nane penaęž‰ tapaemekeme.   
\p
\v 31 Kutu pieketaęž‰ mo Diudia nane make Kaęž‰lili nane make Sametia nane make koto kenke paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke siosi wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ pelia haemekeme. Koto siosi wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ tambaęž‰ minolo haenaęž‰ honkopu hao hataęž‰ daeyatiki pimikime. Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao hataęž‰ pimikime.   
\s1 Pidataęž‰ Lida Diopa da yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ hayekeeki  
\p
\v 32 Pidataęž‰ kenke paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ pomu lopaataęž‰ hoto maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ mo Lida da nane haemeke Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali handolo peekeme.  
\v 33 Koto da paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ hali homeke Iniasi handeekeme. Koto halitaęž‰ kiki anke homa pa wieke hali pitaęž‰ bapi ketepo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ da pandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ u pitaęž‰tiki pu hayekeme.  
\v 34 Pidamaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Iniasio. Yesu Ketisomaęž‰ neke epeaasaęž‰me. Nakaęž‰ yapaęž‰taęž‰ oko pea mina tiae laa leekeme. Koto leeke pitaęž‰ kone Iniasitaęž‰ tiaeyekeme.  
\v 35 Mo Lida Sietoni da yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ mo hali handaataęž‰ Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la hone tulaemekeme.   
\p
\v 36 Mo Diopa da paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ disaipolo wandaęž‰ homeke Taęž‰bida hayekeme. Koto bikitaęž‰ pa mo Kitiki pi laataęž‰ Dokasi laa laęž‰laęž‰me. Koto wandaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ hoto paeyao epeke hau pu hataęž‰ mo alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰yeke mesiolo hali wandaęž‰hali tambaęž‰ mu hayekeme.  
\v 37 Kutu pu hayekepate nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ koto wandaęž‰taęž‰ yeni tondope mea otaęž‰ homeekeme. Ipikaęž‰ toko tandaęž‰paataęž‰ oli manda da pandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ winaęž‰ lemekeme.  
\v 38 Koto Diopa dataęž‰ mo Lida da teke paęž‰taęž‰ hayeke handaa mo Diopa da haemeke disaipolo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ Pidataęž‰ Lida da paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa halaęž‰me pi opuaataęž‰ hali yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ pi tapaaso alotaęž‰ Niki paęž‰taęž‰ pilisi aĚ±iĚ± epo lapaęž‰peke lenaęž‰ tapaemekeme.   
\p
\v 39 Koto ekinaęž‰ Pida tiaotaęž‰ mo hali yaapo ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ pemekeme. Da opolo peeketaęž‰ oli manda da pandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ ipiki hatuku aęž‰meimikime. Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo kosaęž‰piki wandaęž‰sunu paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ mombololo hataęž‰ eĚ± aęž‰pa lemekeme. Hande Dokasimaęž‰ na homeke pa hayeke pitaęž‰naęž‰ tumbulieke sedisunu make kosaęž‰ akaęž‰manu make Pida paęž‰taęž‰ walemekeme.  
\v 40 Pidamaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰sunu paeyao hamaęž‰ nane pupe laataęž‰ tumiki yotuao yeni peaataęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ toko handaęž‰moneaaso alotaęž‰ Taęž‰bida. Tiae laa leekeme. Mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ leke kila Pida handaataęž‰ tiao pitiekeme.  
\v 41 Pidamaęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao ipikaęž‰ kiki yolaęž‰ mea tiaeyekeme. Kutu pieketaęž‰ Pidamaęž‰ mo Ketiso wandaęž‰hali make mo kosaęž‰piki wandaęž‰sunu make ipupe laataęž‰ hande wandaęž‰taęž‰ do tiao halaęž‰ handaęž‰pe laa leekeme.  
\v 42 Koto hande pieke ekitaęž‰ mo Diopa da paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰tia tia pimikime. Kutupa wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaemekeme.  
\v 43 Pidataęž‰ Diopa da paęž‰taęž‰ hoto elekeeleke hatiki peaataęž‰ mo maęž‰naęž‰ yonkelekemaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ wepu hayeke hali Saimononaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ pelia haepekeme.   
\c 10  
\s1 Pida Koniliesi yaapo  
\p
\v 1 Mo Sesatia da nane ami opisa hali homeke hayekeme. Ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Koniliesie. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo ami haliweki 100 handeteke hayekeme. Koto somemaęž‰ handeteke hayeke ami tapakenaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Ideli tapakee.  
\v 2 Hande halitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone wotu u hao ipikaęž‰ weteke weki wandikimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ wotu homaęž‰tiki pu haemekeme. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ kiki tindipao mani diaęž‰yeke wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ halo haotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni piaęž‰tiki pu hayekeme.  
\v 3 Nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ nate toke nane haenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ enisolo homeke epeekeeki upamaęž‰ otaęž‰ peneme yao handeke nono piekeme. Mo enisolomaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Koniliesio leekeme.  
\v 4 Koniliesimaęž‰ mo enisolo paęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰ tieke homa handake witolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Aleke kaęž‰taęž‰pe leekeme. Kutupa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ yeni pu haleeki make nakaęž‰ mani halo haleeki make oli hepeni da nane pua Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ pi laasaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 5 Kutupa ame do mo Diopa da paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ biki Saimono biki maęž‰ndaęž‰ Pida epenaęž‰ handaęž‰ mulu penaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ tapae leekeme.  
\v 6 Koto sometaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰kaęž‰li pua pilaęž‰me. Mo da teke hali Saimonotaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ yonkeleke hako alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ wepu halaęž‰ halie. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ dataęž‰ dawala ikali teaęž‰naęž‰ halaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 7 Kutupa mo hande ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pi leeke enisolo peeke nane ipikaęž‰ e pokao hayeke hali yaapo make ipiki teke paęž‰taęž‰ hayeke ami hali homeke make wi leekeme. Mo ipiki teke paęž‰taęž‰ hayeke ami halitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homo hayekeme.  
\v 8 Kutupa mo hande leeke pitaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ la halaakaęž‰naęž‰ Diopa da nane tapaeyekeme.   
\p
\v 9 Kutupa da kelepeeketaęž‰ mo potaęž‰naęž‰ pu opu hao pa Diopa da teke paęž‰taęž‰ ipulu haenaęž‰ kone Pidataęž‰ nate you tikekenaęž‰ haenaęž‰ mo da holunaęž‰ aęž‰meiya yeni pua piekeme.  
\v 10 Kotoeki pitolo haenaęž‰ teaęž‰ tieke wopu pieke handa ya nee hone witolo haenaęž‰ oni haliwekimaęž‰ ne amu peaaso haenaęž‰ Pidataęž‰ uĚ± yokaęž‰ lupa peekeme.  
\v 11 Peliolo hataęž‰ upamaęž‰ handeekepate oli ya akolopaęž‰olu bao dapolo tiekemaęž‰ handeke ale honiki nane tonkopu minaęž‰ alu alu pea mea lopaęž‰niaeyekeme.  
\v 12 Koto ale paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ yeti alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ make basunu paeyao kenkenaęž‰ ulaęž‰ keto alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ sunu make mu pamba aęž‰pa mea lopaęž‰niaeyekeme.  
\v 13 Kutupa pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰makemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Pidao. Tiao. Koto alemanu lia nae leekeme.  
\v 14 Koto leekepate Pidamaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Otaęž‰ diaęž‰me leekeme. IĚ±taęž‰ hoke ale manutaęž‰ na no halome leekeme.  
\v 15 Hande pi hoto yaapo peao paa alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ wamo pea ulaęž‰ aletaęž‰ hoepeao ulaęž‰ alee pi na lapeke leekeme.  
\v 16 Kotoeki hoto tepo peao peataęž‰ mo hande aletaęž‰ oli ya nane pa mea aęž‰meiyekeme.   
\p
\v 17 Pidataęž‰ mo hande upataęž‰ eki pulu pienaęž‰ piaęž‰pe laa hone witolo haenaęž‰ Koniliesimaęž‰ tapaeyeke haliweki Saimononaęž‰ dataęž‰ hando paęž‰taęž‰pe lolo pieke haliweki potaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa hando haemekeme.  
\v 18 Kutupa wi leekeme. Saimono Pidataęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰pe la lotaęž‰ piekeme.  
\v 19 Koto ekinaęž‰ Pidamaęž‰ mo hande upa piekeeki hone witolo pitinaęž‰ mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Handaęž‰e. Hali tepomaęž‰ neke oni aęž‰pa lotaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ handaęž‰e leekeme.  
\v 20 Tiao. Oni haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ na wiki pa pulu ombu hapekee leekeme. Koto haliwekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ tapao puaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 21 Kutupa Pida holaęž‰paęž‰niao alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto weiteleme halie leekeme. Ekipeke epemepe leekeme.  
\v 22 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Koniliesitaęž‰ ami opisa epeke halimaęž‰ tapaeyaęž‰me laa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ halie laataęž‰ Diu wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ epeke pi lo halaęž‰ halie. Kutupa Kodaęž‰naęž‰ yako piki enisolo homekemaęž‰ leeke handa nakaęž‰ pimanu tonkaęž‰naęž‰ opuluekemaęž‰ neke handaęž‰ mulu pupe leeke handa ipulumaęž‰me lemekeme.  
