\v 26 Kutu piekepate Pidamaęž‰ mo hali minaęž‰liao alotaęž‰ Tiae. IĚ± make kenke halie leekeme.  
\v 27 Kutupa Pidamaęž‰ mo hali yaapo pi alo hataęž‰ da tukiki nane puaataęž‰ mo hande mombelemeke wandaęž‰hali handa alotaęž‰  
\v 28 Diu halimaęž‰ kenke maęž‰ndaęž‰ hali yaapo taęž‰maęž‰ni peaęž‰peke na yeke ipikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ puaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me ekitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone handelemepate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ hoke hali o hoe peao halaęž‰ halie pi na lapeke laa IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ waleaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 29 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ IĚ± handaęž‰ mulu epeeke handa IĚ±taęž‰ hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ na wiki epoaęž‰me. Kotaęž‰ ekipeke IĚ± handaęž‰ mulu epenaęž‰ la pipe leekeme.   
\p
\v 30 Kutupa Koniliesimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hoto tonkopu ambaęž‰ yopua nate dupitolo haenaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ do da paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ welealo nane yeni pitolo hano hakepiki dau pambaake hali kuta kone aęž‰pa IĚ± teke paęž‰taęž‰ hayaęž‰me leekeme.  
