\s1 Pidanaęž‰ pi leekeeki  
\p
\v 34 Kutupa Pidamaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ametaęž‰ otaęž‰ handolome. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ hone taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ na wiki homeke hone witaęž‰laęž‰eki handolome leekeme.  
\v 35 Kenke paeyaonaęž‰ halaęž‰ hali epimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ epeke hau pu hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ koto hali milieke leekeme.  
\v 36 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ do ekitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ ta handeleme handaęž‰e. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo Isulai wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi tapaeyekeeki loaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo aęž‰ndaęž‰ peliaasaęž‰ Pi Seliapotaęž‰ Yesu Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ walenaęž‰ leekeme. Yesutaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali make alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ make paeyaonaęž‰ Tekehalie.  
\v 37 Kutupa mo hande Diudia nane paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ ame do numaneke pimiki ekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ na lolueke. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ opimikaęž‰taęž‰me. Dionimaęž‰ bapitaisi hau peaeyeke nane wetepenaęž‰ mo Kaęž‰lili nane kini pu miekeme.  
\v 38 Hande Naęž‰saęž‰tete da halitaęž‰ Yesue. Ipikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ wele peaaso hataęž‰ mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ make sutaęž‰pe wiaeyekeeki opimikaęž‰taęž‰me. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ameĚ±leĚ± hataęž‰ epeke hau peaęž‰tiki pu hao Sadanimaęž‰ hoeyaeyeke wandaęž‰hali mea tiatiki pu hao pomu hayekeme.  
\v 39 Kutupa mo Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ kenke nane make mo Diutuseleme da paęž‰taęž‰ make ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ piaęž‰ ekimanu paeyaotaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ wekitisi halomaęž‰me. Kutupa koto hoki nanetaęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki meataęž‰ tinaęž‰ tamendiao homenaęž‰ lememe.  
\v 40 Kutu pimipate hoto teponaęž‰ winaęž‰ laataęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ paa mea tiaotaęž‰ peneme yao waleaęž‰me.  
\v 41 Wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ handenaęž‰ na leke pa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰la talopu mieke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ homeke handenaęž‰ leaęž‰me. Nikitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ la halolomaęž‰ haliweki halomaęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ homa paa tiao aęž‰paataęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± ne nomaęž‰me.  
\v 42 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ manaęž‰ alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ dupae. Wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi walemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali make pa haleme wandaęž‰hali make ikaęž‰ pi yokaalu peaalo polo hali mea hano leaęž‰me lapaęž‰peke leaęž‰me.  
\v 43 Mo hande potopede haliweki paeyaomaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ lemeke ekitaęž‰ dupae. Hali epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi miniki hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ mo hoke hau piekeeki pa tombuaasaęž‰eki milieke lemekeme leekeme.   
