\p
\v 22 Mo Diutuseleme siosi tapakemaęž‰ handeeki pi opuaataęž‰ kutupa oli Aęž‰ndioko da paęž‰taęž‰ Banabasi tapaemekeme.  
\v 23 Banabasitaęž‰ oli da opolo puaataęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ epeaeyekeeki handaataęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ wopu homeekeme. Kutupa paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ pi daĚ±oĚ±la hataęž‰ wopu miniki hao hapaęž‰peke laa pi waleekeme.  
\v 24 Banabasitaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ epeke hali hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi wopu miniki hayeketaęž‰ Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ ipiki tumbaeyekeme. Kutupa wandaęž‰hali wopu Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ apaęž‰tao taęž‰maęž‰ni pea haemekeme.  
\v 25 Koto ekinaęž‰ Banabasimaęž‰ mo Tasaęž‰si da nane Solo weilu peekeme.  
\v 26 Kutupa handaęž‰ wiataęž‰ mo Aęž‰ndioko da paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku epeekeme. Bapi homeke koto paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ mo siosi tapake ameĚ±leĚ± pi hotu haotaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wopu pi walo haepekeme. Koto da paęž‰taęž‰ pi mimiki wandaęž‰hali ikitaęž‰ mo Ketiso wandaęž‰halie laa mo koto bikitaęž‰ koto da paęž‰taęž‰ kini pu mimikime.   
\p
\v 27 Koto dinaęž‰taęž‰ mandane potopede haliwekitaęž‰ Diutuseleme da hao oni Aęž‰ndioko da opolo epemekeme.  
\v 28 Kutupa homeke halitaęž‰ Akipasimaęž‰ mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ la halolo haenaęž‰ tiao alotaęž‰ Teaęž‰ ki tieke kenke paeyao nane ipilieke laa waleekeme. Kutupa mo Kolodiusimaęž‰ Sisa hayeke natenaęž‰ kutu piekeme.  
\v 29 Kutupa mo disaipolo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hone wia alotaęž‰ Nikaęž‰ Diudia nane haleme kametiti tambaęž‰ mumanaęž‰ paeyaomaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ halomanaęž‰e lemekeme.  
\v 30 Koto ekinaęž‰ kotoeki peataęž‰ oli siosi tondiki haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ Banabasi Solo yaapomaęž‰ mea puaenaęž‰ laa tapaemekeme.   
\c 12  
\s1 Tanda wopu minelemeeki  
\p
\v 1 Koto pitaęž‰taęž‰ hande kini hali Hetodimaęž‰ mandane siosi tapake haliweki daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ miniekeme.  
\v 2 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Dioninaęž‰ hameke Diaęž‰mesitaęž‰ kepete hokulumaęž‰ liekeme.  
\v 3 Kutupa Diu wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homemeke handa Pida make daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ miniekeme. Mo hande Na Pombei Yaake Palaowa Nemeke pitaęž‰ piekeme.  
\v 4 Kutupa daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ minataęž‰ dipula mea lopao ami haliweki mandane tonkopu mandane tonkopu mandane tonkopu mandane tonkopu haliwekitaęž‰ kade hatiki pinaęž‰ leekeme. Ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Lombei Pupa Yapeeke pitaęž‰ paeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ mea aęž‰pa walueke hone wiekeme.  
\v 5 Koto ekinaęž‰ Pidataęž‰ dipula da paęž‰taęž‰ pa pitinaęž‰ leekepate mo siosi tapake wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ Pida yeni wopu peaęž‰tiki pimikime.   
\s1 Pida dipula pao tapaeyekeeki  
\p
\v 6 Hetodimaęž‰ Pida mea aęž‰pa waluekemaęž‰ haenaęž‰ timba kone Pidataęž‰ mo ami hali yaapo ameĚ±leĚ± seni pu yaapomaęž‰ endialu pea tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ peliekeme. Kutupa potaęž‰ hamaęž‰ nane hataęž‰ kade haliwekimaęž‰ mo dipula da handeteke hatiki ombu pimikime.  
\v 7 Kuta kone Tekehalinaęž‰ enisolo homeke epeeketaęž‰ mo da pandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± tieke piekeme. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Pida aęž‰pa lu tiaaso alotaęž‰ AĚ±iĚ± tiae leekeme. Kutupa hande seni pumanu ipikaęž‰ kiki paęž‰taęž‰ kone tunkulupa lopaęž‰ lopaęž‰ piekeme.  
\v 8 Kutupa mo enisolomaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ hako yama anke dake pambae leekeme. Kutu piekeme. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Pida paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ dau mea dopua IĚ± teli mea epoe leekeme.  
\v 9 Kutupa teli mea hama peekeme. Pidamaęž‰ mo enisolomaęž‰ pieke ekitaęž‰ hone na wiki upamaęž‰ piki nono piekeme.  
\v 10 Kutupa titinaęž‰ kade hayeke alenaęž‰ lombei pupa pua koto hoki paęž‰taęž‰eki make lombei pupa puaataęž‰ mo hande daoni nane peeke ayenimaęž‰ wepieke potaęž‰ kake tieke paęž‰taęž‰ opolo pepekeme. Kutupa mo hande potaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone lombeekeme. Kutupa ipilikitaęž‰ tunkulupa puaataęž‰ potaęž‰ homeke yolaęž‰ mea pepekepate mo enisolotaęž‰ koto kone Pida minaęž‰paęž‰lao peekeme.   
\p
\v 11 Koto pitaęž‰taęž‰ Pidamaęž‰ hone wiekeme. Ametaęž‰ otaęž‰ hone wia handolome leekeme. Tekehalimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ enisolo tapao mo Hetodimaęž‰ IĚ± miaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo Diu wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pulu pelemeeki make IĚ± tambaęž‰ miaęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 12 Koto hone wiataęž‰ Dionitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ biki maęž‰ndaęž‰ Maka ipikaęž‰ inkiki Metinaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ peekeme. Koto da paęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ mombaęž‰la pitaęž‰ yeni pu pitimikime.  
\v 13 Kutupa mo potaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ pua hoto laa kilikili laeyekeme. Kutupa wandiki maęž‰ndaęž‰ Loudamaęž‰ lombolo peekepate  
\v 14 Pidanaęž‰ pi make meataęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ wopu homolo hataęž‰ potaęž‰ na lombeke da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ anke hao pua Pidataęž‰ potaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa halaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 15 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ keaaso alee lemekepate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Otaęž‰ loaęž‰me leekeme. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipikaęž‰ enisolo hataęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me lemekepate  
\v 16 Pidamaęž‰ kilikili laaso haenaęž‰ pua potaęž‰ lomba Pida handolo hataęž‰ penkilipaęž‰tia pomua wotu handake wimikime.   
\p
\v 17 Kutu pimikipate Pidamaęž‰ kikimaęž‰ kone pi na lapee leekeme. Kutupa Tekehalimaęž‰ mo dipula da paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku epeeke pi la haleekeme. Kutupa Pidamaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Diaęž‰mesi paęž‰taęž‰ make Ketiso kametiti paęž‰taęž‰ make do pi la halaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme. Kutupa minaęž‰paęž‰lao pua da maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ peekeme.   
\p
\v 18 Da kelepeeketaęž‰ mo hande ami haliwekimaęž‰ Pida na pitieke handa hone ti yokemekeme.  
\v 19 Kutupa Hetodimaęž‰ Pida weiyekepate na handaęž‰ wiekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo kade haemeke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ Ekipa paęž‰laęž‰pe laa lotaęž‰ lotaęž‰ peataęž‰ mo haliweki homenaęž‰ linaęž‰ leekeme. Doeki paeyeketaęž‰ Hetodi Diudia minaęž‰paęž‰lao nate mandaneeki Sesatia nane hayekeme.   
\s1 Hetodi homeekeeki  
\p
\v 20 Hetodimaęž‰ Taiya Saidoni da yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ mineke tieke wopu pankeekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo da yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke mandane haliwekimaęž‰ apaęž‰tao Hetodi handolo pemekeme. Titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la mo kini halinaęž‰ da handeteke hayeke hali Baęž‰lasitusitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ liaenaęž‰yeke ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± pi lolo pemekeme. Mo halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi opiekeme. Kotoeki peaęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ polumanaęž‰e laa Hetodi paęž‰taęž‰ honke lolo pemekeme. Ikaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ netaęž‰ Hetodimaęž‰ handeteke hayeke kenke paęž‰taęž‰ mu haemeke ekinaęž‰yeke lemekeme.   
\p
\v 21 Hetodimaęž‰ laęž‰ wieke nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ kini halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yamo hayaęž‰ akaęž‰manu yamaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yama pitu hayeke seanaęž‰ pitaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi leekeme.  
\v 22 Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ opuaataęž‰ anekemaęž‰ wi la alu alu pitolo alotaęž‰ Dotaęž‰ otaęž‰ halimaęž‰ na alaęž‰me laa kodaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ alaęž‰pate yaęž‰laęž‰me lemekeme.  
\v 23 Hetodimaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi na laenaęž‰ leke pa ipikaęž‰ pi kone laenaęž‰ leeke handaataęž‰ kuta kone Tekehalinaęž‰ enisolomaęž‰ Hetodi yeni tondaęž‰paęž‰ minaęž‰ leekeme. Kutupa pipi manumaęž‰ weleke tunkulaęž‰ mepi naataęž‰ homeekeme.   
\p
\v 24 Kutu pitolo haenaęž‰ kone Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi mandane mandane wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ daeyatia peekeme.   
\p
\v 25 Banabasi Solo yaapomaęž‰ mo Diutuseleme da paęž‰taęž‰ peaęž‰peke ekimanu pu paeyaotaęž‰ pa laęž‰kaęž‰la Dioni Maka make hatuku mandakenaęž‰ pemekeme.   
\c 13  
\s1 Banabasi Solo yaapo meataęž‰ tapaemekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Mo Aęž‰ndioko siosi tapake paęž‰taęž‰ mandane potopede haliweki make pi walo haemeke haliweki make haemekeme. Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi lao hayeke Banabasi make Simioni biki maęž‰ndaęž‰ Naidia make Saitini hali Lusiasi make hande you hali Hetodinaęž‰ yankeke hali homeke Maneini make Solo make haemekeme.  
\v 2 Kutupa Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ ne na neke pandaęž‰puniaaso haenaęž‰ mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Banabasi Solo yaapo yaka walo polo e pokaenaęž‰yeketaęž‰ pa nane haenaęž‰ lape leekeme.  
\v 3 Kutupa pa ne na neke yeni peaataęž‰ mo hali yaaponaęž‰ younaęž‰ kiki wiataęž‰ hande leeke e pokaenaęž‰ penaęž‰ tapaemekeme.   
\s1 Saipotasi haepekeeki  
\p
\v 4 Koto ekinaęž‰ hande hali yaapotaęž‰ mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ tapaaso haenaęž‰ oni Selusia nane pepekeme. Koto paęž‰taęž‰ opolo pua Saipotasi nane palai kawaso tiekenaęž‰ pita pepekeme.  
\v 5 Kutupa Salamisa da nane opolo puaataęž‰ Diu haliwekinaęž‰ pi hotu haemeke damanu paęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi ale waloendi pu haepekeme. Dioni Makamaęž‰ make ipiliki petoloendi pu hayekeme.   
\p
\v 6 Mo hoki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ waloendi pu haotaęž‰ mo Peiposi da nane puaataęž‰ tiĚ±oĚ± hali homeke bikitaęž‰ Ba Yesu handepekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ Diu hali hataęž‰ pa yayapiki potopede hayekeme.  
\v 7 Koto halitaęž‰ mo hokinaęž‰ kapomani you hali Sesiasi Polasi yaapo ameĚ±leĚ± hao hayeke halie. Mo Sesiasi Polasi ipikitaęž‰ hone wopu lenkenaęž‰ pea u hayeke halie. Mo kapomani you halimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi opuluekemaęž‰ Banabasi Solo yaapo ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ epenaęž‰ wi leekeme.  
\v 8 Hali yaapo pepekepate mo tiĚ±oĚ± hali Elimasimaęž‰ mo Kitiki pi laa koto tiĚ±oĚ± halinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Elimasie ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Banabasi Solo yaapo saęž‰saęž‰ puluekemaęž‰ taapeekeme. Mo kapomaninaęž‰ you halimaęž‰ Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaasaęž‰eki pao laęž‰kaęž‰la mina haenaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ taapeekeme.  
\v 9 Kutu pieke handa Solo ipikaęž‰ biki maęž‰ndaęž‰ Polo ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ ipiki tumba pitinaęž‰ mo tiĚ±oĚ± hali handaake wia alotaęž‰  
\v 10 Neketaęž‰ Sadaninaęž‰ halie. Epeke alemanu paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ lu halemee. Mo hoke hoke yayapiki haumanu pitaęž‰laęž‰eki neke paęž‰taęž‰ tumba pilaęž‰me laataęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ otaęž‰ pimanu kone nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ yayapiki pimanu laa laęž‰kaęž‰laluekemaęž‰ taapo haleme.  
\v 11 Koto ekinaęž‰ ametaęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰ neke liekee. Kutupa neketaęž‰ leke holupiki hali hao hataęž‰taęž‰ nate paĚ±aĚ± aĚ±iĚ± na handilipikie laa leekeme.  
\p Polomaęž‰ koto alo haenaęž‰ kone timbaęž‰laęž‰ pambeke koamaęž‰ handeke alemaęž‰ Elimasinaęž‰ leke telipinaęž‰ holu peaeyekeme. Maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kiki yolaęž‰ mea mina penaęž‰yeke kikimaęž‰ hali weiyaęž‰tiki pomiekeme.  
\v 12 Mo kapomaninaęž‰ you halimaęž‰taęž‰ kutu piekeeki hando haotaęž‰ hone tulaeyekeme. Tekehalinaęž‰ pi waleekeeki opitolo hataęž‰ penkilipaęž‰tia pomiekeme.   
\s1 Pisidia nane hayeke da Aęž‰ndioko da paęž‰taęž‰ pepekeeki  
\p
\v 13 Polo ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ pemeke haliwekitaęž‰ palai kawaso tiekenaęž‰ pitataęž‰ mo Peiposi da minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo Paęž‰mbilia nane hayeke da Peka paęž‰taęž‰ opolo pemekeme. Koto paęž‰taęž‰ opolo pemekepate Dioni Makataęž‰ iki minaęž‰paęž‰lao Diutuseleme nane pa laęž‰kaęž‰la peekeme.  
\v 14 Peka da minaęž‰paęž‰lao puaataęž‰ mo Pisidia da nane hayeke da Aęž‰ndioko da paęž‰taęž‰ opolo puaataęž‰ mo Hoto Pilaęž‰ Natenaęž‰ mo haliwekitaęž‰ mo Diu haliwekinaęž‰ pi hotu haemeke da paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pamba pua pitimikime.  
\v 15 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ mo Mosesimaęž‰ wape pea ulaęž‰ Lo Pimanu make mo potopede haliwekimaęž‰ wape pea ulaęž‰ pimanu make yataęž‰pa haenaęž‰taęž‰ mo pi hotu haemeke da you haliwekimaęž‰ Polo ameda paęž‰taęž‰ pi laęž‰moneaaso alotaęž‰ Kame titio. Wandaęž‰hali honkopu hao halo paęž‰laęž‰ pi lapaęž‰peke yeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ loaęž‰minaęž‰e hone witolomaęž‰me lemekeme.  
\v 16 Koto lemeke Polomaęž‰ tiao hataęž‰ kiki mea aęž‰meiyao pi dupa waleekeme.  
\p Ya tapake Isulai wandaęž‰hali iki make Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao yeni pu haleme Diendaili wandaęž‰hali paeyao iki make IĚ±maęž‰ alo pi opuaęž‰pe laataęž‰  
\v 17 Koto Isulai tapake wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ apaęž‰mei ameda mea haenaęž‰ laataęž‰ mo Idiepi kenke nane da maęž‰ndaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali hataęž‰ kone tapake tieke wandaęž‰hali haminaęž‰ leekeme. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wele wotu pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ koto wandaęž‰hali Idiepi nane minaęž‰paęž‰lao hatuku puaataęž‰  
\v 18 mo hapu hayeke alenaęž‰ bapi 40 mo wandaęž‰hali koto paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ ikitaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homo hatiki pimikipate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ handeteke hatiki pu hayekeme.  
\v 19 Mo Keinani kenke paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke tapake watake hataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ hoeyaotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ koto kenke teke wandaęž‰hali haenaęž‰ leekeme.  
\v 20 Kutu pu paeyaasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ bapi manutaęž‰ pa 450manu yapeekeme.  
\p Kutupa wetepe nanetaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pi yokaalu peao haemeke teke haliweki haenaęž‰ lomaęž‰ lomaęž‰ puaęž‰tiki aęž‰pa mo potopede hali Samuele ipiki aęž‰pa hayekeme.  
\v 21 Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Nikaęž‰ kini hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ haenaęž‰e laa honke lemeke handa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ Solo mea haenaęž‰ leekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ Benisamini tapake hali Kisinaęž‰ eiyeke hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ kini hali haenaęž‰ yapeeke bapi manutaęž‰ 40e.  
\v 22 Kutu piekepate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Solo yoka pa nane haenaęž‰ laa Deipidi meataęž‰ kini hali haenaęž‰ leekeme. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Deipidi hayekeeki handaataęž‰ pi dupa leekeme. IĚ±maęž‰ handolo alotaęž‰ dupae. Diesinaęž‰ eiyeke Deipiditaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ halaęž‰eki handolo hataęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰me laataęž‰ koto halimaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki paeyao ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pilieke la leekeme.  
\v 23 Hande Deipidinaęž‰ tapake hali Yesutaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰ wieke tupaęž‰ Isulai wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Daęž‰taalaęž‰ Hali haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 24 Yesumaęž‰ e aĚ±iĚ± na kini pu mea pokeeke haenaęž‰taęž‰ Dionimaęž‰ Isulai wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ pi waleekeme. Ikaęž‰ hoke hau pimiki ekimanu minaęž‰paęž‰laotaęž‰ bapitaisi pinaęž‰yeke pi waleekeme.  
\v 25 Kutupa Dionimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e poko paeyaaluekemaęž‰ hataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ IĚ± halo ekitaęž‰ epi hone witelemepe. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ yu wia haleme halitaęž‰ IĚ± diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate handaęž‰pe. Yaka hoki nane ipulaęž‰me. Koto ipulaęž‰ halinaęž‰ anke daketaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ holawaapeketaęž‰ anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me laa leekeme.   
\p
\v 26 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ tapake haliweki ya kametitio. Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao yeni pu haleme Diendaili wandaęž‰hali paeyao iki make Kodaęž‰maęž‰ do hande niki daęž‰taapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ pi niki paęž‰taęž‰ epenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 27 Mo Diutuseleme da paęž‰taęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ make ikaęž‰ you haliwekimaęž‰ make Yesutaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali Daęž‰taasaęž‰ Hali halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hone na wimikime. Mo Hoto Pilaęž‰ Natemanu paeyaonaęž‰ mo hande potopede haliwekimaęž‰ wape pea ulaęž‰ ekimanu yataęž‰po halemeeki make hone wopu na wilimime. Kutu pimikipate ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ lia homaemeke ekimaęž‰ mo hande potopede haliwekimaęž‰ wape pea ulaęž‰eki kone yaemekeme.  
\v 28 Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu lia homaaluekemaęž‰taęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰eki teke maęž‰ndaęž‰ na handaęž‰ wiki kone Pailedi paęž‰taęž‰ pua honke alo alotaęž‰ Yesu homae laa honke lemekeme.   
\p
\v 29 Kutupa hande Baibolo bukanaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ pulu piekeeki wape pea ulaęž‰eki kone ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pu paeyaemekeme. Mandane haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ Yesu toko mo aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki tinaęž‰ endiaemekeme alenaęž‰ pua hondaęž‰ mea pua lapaęž‰ pimikime.  
\v 30 Kutu pimikipate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo lapaęž‰ wieke alenaęž‰ Yesu pa mea tiaeyekeme.  
\v 31 Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ Kaęž‰lili nane hao Diutuseleme da paęž‰taęž‰ pemeke wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ ipiki handenaęž‰ hoto elekeeleke peneme yao ipikaęž‰ leke mineke walaęž‰tiki piekeme. Ametaęž‰ koto wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ Yesu handemeeki Isulai wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ la halele wandaęž‰hali halememe.  
\v 32-33 Kutupa dikanaęž‰maęž‰ make koto hande Pi Seliapo iki paęž‰taęž‰ la kuluekemaęž‰ aęž‰pa halopaęž‰me. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ make nikaęž‰ apaęž‰mei ameda paęž‰taęž‰ pi laęž‰ wiekeeki ametaęž‰ ikaęž‰ wekiwandiki titi niki paęž‰taęž‰ peaowalaęž‰me. Yesu daęž‰taalaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰eki peaowalaęž‰me. Hande hoto yaapo peao wape pieke Emeli paęž‰taęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ dupae.  
\q1 Neketaęž‰ yaka Wekie. Ame do natenaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ nakaęž‰ Apaęž‰ halome  
\m laa wape paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 34 Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu lapaęž‰ wieke alenaęž‰ mea tiao pa hoto maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ paa na homolo pieke ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ pi dupa leekeme.  
\q1 Hande Deipidi paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ pi laęž‰ ulueki kone IĚ±maęž‰ epeke yakopiki haumaęž‰ neke otaęž‰ epeaalueke  
\m laa wape paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 35 Kutupa make mo Baibolo bukanaęž‰ pa maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pi alo hataęž‰ dupa wape paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\q1 Nakaęž‰ Yakopiki Halinaęž‰ loke na tandepenaęž‰ lelipikie  
\m laa wape paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 36 Deipidi ipikaęž‰ hayeke pitaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu piaęž‰tiki pu hao wetepenaęž‰ homeekeme. Ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰mei ameda lapaęž‰ pimiki alenaęž‰ ipiki make koto paęž‰taęž‰ lapaęž‰ pimikipate ipikaęž‰ loke make tandepeekeme.  
\v 37 Kutu piekepate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ lapaęž‰ wieke alenaęž‰ paa mea tiaeyeke halitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ loke na tandepeekeme.  
\v 38-39 Ya kametitio. Iki paeyaomaęž‰ doeki otaęž‰ hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke. Yesu ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ kone ikaęž‰ hoke hau pimiki ekimanu pa hameke paeyaapeke pi iki paęž‰taęž‰ walolomaęž‰me. Wandaęž‰hali epi amedamaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoke hau piekeeki manutaęž‰ Mosesimaęž‰ wape pea ulaęž‰ Lo Pi manumaęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapaapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰pate Yesumaęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapawalieke.  
\v 40 Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ wotu handeteke hapaęž‰peke. Mo hande potopede haliwekimaęž‰ leeke ekimanu iki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰paamaęž‰naęž‰ loaęž‰me. Dupa   
\q1
\v 41 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ pimanu paęž‰taęž‰ pi la la pu haleme wandaęž‰halio. Handaęž‰pe.  
\q1 Kutupa handolo hataęž‰ penkilipaęž‰tia pomua otaęž‰ homaęž‰paęž‰pekee.  
\q1 Iki haleme dinaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ pokolo polo etaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone na wilimikie.  
\q1 Maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ la kinaęž‰ kone opua hone na tulaalimikie laa wape paęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 42 Solo Banabasi yaapotaęž‰ hamaęž‰ nane pulu haenaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hande lepe pi mo Hoto Pilaęž‰ Nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ make pa lopenaęž‰e laa honke lemekeme.  
\v 43 Kutupa mo pi hotu haemeke da paęž‰taęž‰ pi hotia paeyeketaęž‰ Diu haliweki wopu make Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone wopu u haemeke Diendaili haliweki wopu make Polo Banabasi yaapo teli mea pemekeme. Kutupa ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ pi laataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pa aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki honkopu hao wotu miniki hao haenaęž‰ pi walepekeme.   
\p
\v 44 Kutupa mo hande Hoto Pilaęž‰ Nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ mo daoni nane wandaęž‰hali paeyao Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi opuluekemaęž‰ mombelemekeme.  
\v 45 Kutu pimikipate mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paeyao handaataęž‰ honditi pitolo hataęž‰ Polomaęž‰ leeke pitaęž‰ Ya pi alaęž‰me laa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pi la la pimikime.  
\v 46 Kutupa Solo pitaęž‰ Banabasi yaapomaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homeke hataęž‰ pi alo alotaęž‰ Iki paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰la Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi ale walaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pateo. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ kiaaso hataęž‰ Nikitaęž‰ deto halaęž‰eki meaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me alemeke handaataęž‰ kotaęž‰ handaęž‰pe. Mo Diendaili wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ walo pulupaęž‰me lepekeme.  
\v 47 Pa ekipeke Kodaęž‰maęž‰ dupape laa niki paęž‰taęž‰ leeke ekitaęž‰ dupae.  
\q1 Ikitaęž‰ mo Diendaili wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± pitaęž‰laęž‰eki haminaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.  
\q1 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo kenke honiki nane paęž‰taęž‰manu daęž‰taasaęž‰eki mea pominaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 48 Kutupa mo Diendaili wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ koto pi opuaataęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi laemekeme. Kutupa deto halaęž‰eki mulu pimiki wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ pi mimikime.   
\p
\v 49 Kutupa Tekehalinaęž‰ pi aletaęž‰ da paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ kende tia wiekeme.  
\v 50 Kutu piekepate hande Diu haliwekimaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone wopu u haemeke wandaęž‰ tieke tieke mandaneeki manumaęž‰ make mo daoninaęž‰ you haliwekimaęž‰ make Polo Banabasi yaapo ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ linaęž‰yeke sutiaemekeme. Kutupa koto da nane minaęž‰paęž‰lao penaęž‰yeke tolu limikime.  
\v 51 Kutu pimikipate mo hali yaapomaęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ ankenaęž‰ taleeke dokolotaęž‰ koto Aęž‰ndioko wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ tandelaataęž‰ Aikoniomo da nane pepekeme.  
\v 52 Kutupa mo disaipolo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ tumba pitaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰ tiaaso haenaęž‰ haemekeme.   
\c 14  
\s1 Aikoniomo da paęž‰taęž‰ haepekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Kutupa mo Aikoniomo da paęž‰taęž‰ mo Diu haliwekinaęž‰ pi hotu haemeke da paęž‰taęž‰ telipinaęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambepekeme. Kutupa pi epeke tupaęž‰ walepeke handa Diu wandaęž‰hali wopu make Kitiki wandaęž‰hali wopu make Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi mimikime.  
\v 2 Kutu pimiki handa pi na miki Diu haliwekimaęž‰ mo Diendaili haliweki sutiaaso hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone dunki peao Ketiso wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hone winaęž‰yeke lemekeme.  
\v 3 Kutupa Polo Banabasi yaapomaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ hao hataęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homeke Tekehali Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi walaęž‰tiki pipikime. Kutupa Tekehalimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pa aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ pi wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ peneme yaaluekemaęž‰ mo hali yaapomaęž‰ wele peaaso hataęž‰ na hando haemeke ekimanu pinaęž‰ leekeme.  
\v 4 Kutu piekepate mo daoni wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ mandane aposolo hali yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ talaęž‰tiki mandane wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ Diu wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± talaęž‰tiki pimikime.  
\v 5 Kutupa mandane Diu haliweki pitaęž‰ Diendaili haliweki yaapomaęž‰ ikaęž‰ you haliwekimaęž‰ Aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me alo haenaęž‰ mo Solo Banabasi yaapo hoeyao toopimaęž‰ luekemaęž‰ tome tome pambemekepate  
\v 6 mo hali yaapomaęž‰ opuaataęž‰ mo Laikonia nane haepeke Lisita Debi da yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ make mo topu damanu paęž‰taęž‰ make pindipa puaataęž‰  
\v 7 mo hande Pi Seliapo walaęž‰tiki pipikime.   
\s1 Lisita Debi da yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ haepekeeki  
\p
\v 8 Kutupa mo Lisita da paęž‰taęž‰ ankenaęž‰ puaęž‰peke na yeeke hali pitiekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ hoto maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ ankenaęž‰ na peekeme. Mendieke natenaęž‰ kone otaęž‰ hoeyaęž‰ paleke mendiekeme.  
\v 9 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Polomaęž‰ pi alo haenaęž‰ pi opiekeme. Kutupa Polomaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ wotu handaataęž‰ Do halitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ epeaenaęž‰yeke hone tulaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me hone witolo hataęž‰  
\v 10 pi anekemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tiao nakaęž‰ anke tindipao hae leekeme. Kutupa mo hande halitaęž‰ koto kone tindipulu bao tiao peekeme.  
\v 11 Wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ Polomaęž‰ piekeeki handaataęž‰ Laikonia da pi la wi alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰manu otaęž‰ hali leke niki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa piaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me lemekeme.  
\v 12 Banabasinaęž‰ biki maęž‰ndaęž‰ Siusi lemekeme. Kutupa Polo ipikitaęž‰ titinaęž‰ pi waleeke hali yeeke handaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Hemesi lemekeme.  
\v 13 Kutupa mo poĚ±loĚ±ko nane temoko da maęž‰ndaęž‰ hayekeme. Koto danaęž‰ kodaęž‰ Siusi paęž‰taęž‰ yeni peao hayeke halimaęž‰ hali kaomanu make palapalamaęž‰ au laemeke ekimanu make potaęž‰ kake tieke paęž‰taęž‰ mea aęž‰pa kutupa Polo Banabasi yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± mo kaomanu yeni pitolo lia haluekemaęž‰ hone wimikime.   
\p
\v 14 Kutu pimikipate Polo Banabasi yaapomaęž‰ opuaataęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ dau sinkipaęž‰ minalu pea mo wandaęž‰hali tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ anke hao pua wi alo alotaęž‰  
\v 15 Haliwekio. Ekipeke koto hau pitelemepe lepekeme. Diki make ikimaęž‰ handeke kenke hali yaapoe lepekeme. Do pitelemeeki manutaęž‰ paekie lepekeme. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ do hau minaęž‰paęž‰laminaęž‰yeke dikitaęž‰ Pi Seliapo mea aęž‰pa pupaęž‰me lepekeme. Do hau pao do ya kenke dawala ikali make tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ alemanu paeyao make wepia haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ deto halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la epoemenaęž‰yeke aęž‰pa pupaęž‰me lepekeme.  
\v 16 Ambaęž‰ haemeke haliwekitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ hau tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰yeke pinaęž‰ leekepate  
\v 17 pa ipikaęž‰ halaęž‰eki waluekemaęž‰ peneme yaeyekeme dupa. Epeke hau piaęž‰tiki pitolo hataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ oli ya nanemaęž‰ lako epenaęž‰ alo hataęž‰ bapinaęž‰ ikaęž‰ e alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ opaatiki pea kutupa nemaęž‰ make taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ haumaęž‰ make iki taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homatiki pitaęž‰laęž‰me lepekeme.  
\v 18 Koto pi lepekepate mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hande kaomanu lia haluekemaęž‰ taapemekepate paemekeme.   
\p
\v 19 Kutupa Aęž‰ndioko Aikoniomo Diu haliweki aęž‰paataęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali sutiaotaęž‰ Polo toopimaęž‰ liataęž‰ otaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰me laa lu yola daoni hamaęž‰ nane pemekeme.  
\v 20 Kutu pimikipate mo pi mimiki haliweki ipiki wieke alenaęž‰ mombaęž‰la haenaęž‰ Polotaęž‰ tiao mo daoni tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ paa peekeme. Kutupa da kelepeeketaęž‰ Banabasi yaapo mo Debi da nane pepekeme.   
\s1 Hande Sitia nane hayeke da Aęž‰ndioko nane paa pepekeeki  
\p
\v 21 Kutupa Polo Banabasi yaapomaęž‰ koto da paęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Pi Seliapo walakaęž‰naęž‰ disaipolo wandaęž‰hali wopu haenaęž‰ laataęž‰ oli hande Lisita Aikoniomo Aęž‰ndioko damanu paeyao nane laęž‰kaęž‰la puaataęž‰  
\v 22 Ketiso wandaęž‰hali honkopu haenaęž‰ alo hataęž‰ pi walolo alotaęž‰ Pi wotu miniki hao hapaęž‰pekealeo laataęž‰ Nikitaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki wotu meataęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambulumeke lepekeme.  
\v 23 Polo Banabasi yaapomaęž‰ mo siosi tapake handeteke haenaęž‰ tondiki haliweki tambaęž‰ mipi peaataęž‰ kutupa ne na neke yeni pitolo hataęž‰ mo hande Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaasaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali Kodaęž‰maęž‰ handeteke haenaęž‰ lepekeme.   
\p
\v 24 Kutupa Pisidia nane pua lombei pupa Paęž‰mbilia nane opolo pepekeme.  
\v 25 Kutupa Peka da paęž‰taęž‰ pi walakaęž‰naęž‰ Aęž‰talia da nane puniaepekeme.  
\v 26 Kutupa koto hao palai kawasonaęž‰ pita hande Aęž‰ndioko da paęž‰taęž‰ pepekeme. Koto dataęž‰ ambaęž‰ kone mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki minolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi walenaęž‰yeke tapaemeke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ pi wala paeyeke handa paa opolo epepekeme.   
\p
\v 27 Kutupa opolo aęž‰paataęž‰ siosi tapake wandaęž‰hali mombelenaęž‰ laataęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Diendaili wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ pi minaęž‰yeke potaęž‰ lombeekeeki make walepekeme.  
\v 28 Kutupa mo Ketiso wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± hao hatiki pimikime.   
\c 15  
\s1 Diutuseleme da paęž‰taęž‰ pi hotimikieki  
\p
\v 1 Kutupa mandane Diudia nane haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ hao holaęž‰paęž‰nini pea aęž‰pa Ketiso wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi walolo alotaęž‰ Mo hande Mosesimaęž‰ waleeke sekemesaisi hau na pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ deto halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ na milimikie laa lemekeme.  
\v 2 Koto lemeke ekinaęž‰ Polo Banabasi yaapomaęž‰ mo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± kaęž‰ndaęž‰piki pi tieke lepeketaęž‰ hande Aęž‰ndioko Ketiso tapake haliwekimaęž‰ Polo Banabasi yaapo make mandane haliwekimaęž‰ mo Diutuseleme haemeke aposolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ make mo handeteke haemeke tondiki haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ make hande walemeke pi hotulu penaęž‰yeke mimikime.   
\p
\v 3 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo siosi tapakemaęž‰ tapaemeketaęž‰ pua mo Pinisia nane make Sametia nane make pomu lopa mo Diendaili wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ puki laęž‰kaęž‰laemekeeki walolo hataęž‰ koto pimaęž‰ mo Ketiso wandaęž‰hali paeyaotaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaemekeme.  
\v 4 Kutupa Diutuseleme da paęž‰taęž‰ opolo pemeketaęž‰ mo aposolo haliweki make tondiki haliwekimaęž‰ make mo siosi wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ make taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ iki handaęž‰ mimikime. Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰ pieke ekimanu paeyao walepekepate  
\v 5 mandane Paęž‰tisi tapake Ketiso haliwekimaęž‰ tiao alotaęž‰ Mo wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ sekemesaisi hau pinaęž‰ laataęž‰ Mosesimaęž‰ waleeke Lo Pimanu make opinaęž‰ laataęž‰ anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me lemekeme.   
\p
\v 6 Mo hande aposolo haliweki make tondiki haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± mo hande lotaęž‰ pieke ekinaęž‰ mombelemekeme.  
\v 7 Pi wotu hotu haotaęž‰ Pidamaęž‰ tiao alotaęž‰ Ya kametitio. Ambaęž‰ kone iki ameĚ±leĚ± hano Kodaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± mea haenaęž‰ laataęž‰ Diendaili wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Pi Seliapo walonoyeke paęž‰laęž‰me. Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ pi opuakaęž‰naęž‰ hone tulaenaęž‰yeke paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 8 Kutupa wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ puki tukiki nane hando halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Diendaili wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hone tulaasemeeki aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me la walolo hataęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ make Holi Sipitidi haleekeme.  
\v 9 Kutu pieke ekimaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ niki Diu wandaęž‰hali make iki Diendaili wandaęž‰hali make taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pea na halomaęž‰eki waleekeme. Ikaęž‰ hone tulaemeke ekinaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke haumanu pa paeyaeyekeme.  
\v 10 Koto ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰eki handa kone ametaęž‰ pa ekipeke Kodaęž‰ la handuluekemaęž‰ hone witelemepe. Nikaęž‰ apaęž‰meimaęž‰ make nikanaęž‰maęž‰ kone make meaęž‰peke na yeke kaęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰eki kone pa ekipeke mo hande hone tulaaseme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homenaęž‰ alemepe.  
\v 11 Diaęž‰me laataęž‰ Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone tulaasomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Tekehali Yesu ipikaęž‰ pa aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ niki daęž‰taasaęž‰me. Diendaili wandaęž‰hali daęž‰taaso pitaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 12 Banabasi Polo yaapomaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰eki halaataęž‰ mo na hando haemeke ekimanu make wele pieke ekimanu make mo Diendaili wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pieke ekimanu walolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ mo mombelemeke haliwekimaęž‰ opitolo hataęž‰ pi na leke yopu pitimikime.  
\v 13 Pi lo paeyaepeketaęž‰ Diaęž‰mesimaęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ya kametitio. IĚ±maęž‰ alo pi opuaęž‰pe.  
\v 14 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo Diendaili wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ mandane ekimanu otaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali talopu mea haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ epeke hone witaęž‰laęž‰eki niki walaęž‰laęž‰me. Saimonomaęž‰ koto la kaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 15 Mo hande potopede haliwekimaęž‰ lemeke pi manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ mandake pimanu laęž‰laęž‰me. Hande Baibolo bukamaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰   
\q1
\v 16 Tekehalimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Doeki paeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ± paa aęž‰pataęž‰ Deipidinaęž‰ howa ulaęž‰ da IĚ±maęž‰ paa mea aęž‰pa aęž‰meiyalueke.  
\q1 Koto da taake paęž‰taęž‰ kone IĚ±maęž‰ paa epeao mea haenaęž‰ lolueke.   
\q1
\v 17 Kutupa mo mandane mandane wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ Tekehali weilimikie.  
\q1 Hande IĚ±maęž‰ wi lolo Diendaili wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ otaęž‰ yakaeki haenaęž‰ lolome leekeme.   
\q1
\v 18 Tekehalimaęž‰ ambaęž‰ kone dupiki pi la halaataęž‰ koto alaęž‰ handaęž‰e leekeme.   
\p
\v 19 Diaęž‰mesimaęž‰ pa alo alotaęž‰ Yaka honemaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰ mina haleme Diendaili wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki na halomanaęž‰ peaęž‰paęž‰peke alee.  
\v 20 Diaęž‰me. Wape maęž‰ndaęž‰ pea dupiki pi la halomanaęž‰ peaęž‰paęž‰peke alee. Mo toopi timaęž‰ wepia ulaęž‰ kodaęž‰manu paęž‰taęž‰ lia haleeke maęž‰naęž‰ mindiki napeke na yeke suseke hau na piki make waęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pa litaęž‰laęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ yeti na neke we make na napaęž‰peke laa lomanaęž‰ peaęž‰paęž‰peke alee.  
\v 21 Mosesimaęž‰ Lo Pi manutaęž‰ mo pi hotu haleme da paęž‰taęž‰manu hataęž‰taęž‰ Hoto Pilaęž‰ Nate paeyaonaęž‰ kone yataęž‰paęž‰tiki pu haemekeme. Kutupa make daoni paeyao paęž‰taęž‰manu ipikaęž‰ pimanu walaęž‰tiki pu halememe laa leekeme.   
\s1 Mo Diendaili Ketiso wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ wape tapaemekeeki  
\p
\v 22 Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ mo aposolo haliweki make mo tondiki haliweki make siosi wandaęž‰hali paeyao ameĚ±leĚ± ikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ mandane haliweki talopu mea haenaęž‰ laataęž‰ Polo Banabasi yaapo ameĚ±leĚ± hataęž‰taęž‰ mo Aęž‰ndioko da paęž‰taęž‰ tapaaluekemaęž‰ hone wimikime. Diudasi biki maęž‰ndaęž‰ Basabasi meataęž‰ Sailasi make talopu mea haenaęž‰ lemekeme. Mo Ketiso wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ koto hali yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ epeke hone u haemekeme.  
\v 23 Kutupa do wapetaęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ mea penaęž‰ lemekeme. Koto pase tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ do pi wiekeme.  
\q1 Nikitaęž‰ aposolo haliwekimaęž‰ mo siosinaęž‰ handeteke halomaęž‰ tondiki haliwekimaęž‰ tonkaęž‰naęž‰ ikaęž‰ kametonu hataęž‰ do wapemaęž‰ nikaęž‰ oli Aęž‰ndioko Sitia Silisia nane haleme Diendaili kametiti paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae alomaęž‰me.   
\b  
\p
\v 24 Nikaęž‰ da nane haliweki mandaneeki manumaęž‰ pi walolo hataęž‰ iki kaęž‰ndaęž‰ peaemeke ekitaęž‰ opumaęž‰me. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ dupa lapaęž‰peke pi na lomaęž‰pate pa ikaęž‰ konemaęž‰ iki kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaemekeme.  
\v 25 Koto ekinaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ mombaęž‰la hataęž‰ Mandane haliweki mumanaęž‰e laa koto haliweki nikaęž‰ epeke kame yaapo Banabasi Polo ameĚ±leĚ± iki paęž‰taęž‰ tapaomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ epelieke lomaęž‰me.   
\b  
\p
\v 26 Hande hali yaapomaęž‰taęž‰ Tekehali Yesu Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ hone wopu witolo hataęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ hau hone wopu na wiki homeke nono pea haepekeme.  
\v 27 Koto ekinaęž‰ Diudasi Sailasi yaapo iki paęž‰taęž‰ tapaasomaęž‰me. Kutupa ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ kakemaęž‰ hande pi kone lelipipikie lemekeme.   
\b  
\p
\v 28 Mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ make nikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ make iki paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na homaake pa do pimanu siki homeke aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ opuaęž‰pe alomaęž‰me.   
\b  
\p
\v 29 Toopi timaęž‰ wepia ulaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ lia halemeke hoteke ne alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ na neke we make na neke mo daęž‰kaęž‰pe miniki hataęž‰ homaasaęž‰eki na neke loke hoeyaasaęž‰ hau na piki kutupa koto haumanu na pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ halimikie alomaęž‰me. Aęž‰taloe laa wape pu paeyaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 30 Kutupa mo tapaemeke haliweki oni Aęž‰ndioko da nane puaataęž‰ Ketiso wandaęž‰hali aęž‰pa mombelenaęž‰ laakaęž‰naęž‰ hande pase halemekeme.  
\v 31 Kutupa yataęž‰pakaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ hande manaęž‰ lemekeeki opuaataęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homemekeme.  
\v 32 Kutupa Diudasi Sailasi yaapo potopede hali yaapo hataęž‰ kone pi wopu walolo hataęž‰taęž‰ honkopu haenaęž‰ lepekeme.  
\v 33 Kutupa koto paęž‰taęž‰ hosiki hao hatiki pipikitaęž‰ mo Ketiso haliwekimaęž‰ hande titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰ kone tapaemeke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ hataęž‰ paa tapaemekeme.  
\v 34 [Pate Sailasinaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ do paęž‰taęž‰ pa halueke hone wiekeme.]   
\p
\v 35 Kutu pimikipate Polo Banabasi yaapo Aęž‰ndioko da nane hao haotaęž‰ haliweki paeyao ameĚ±leĚ± hataęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ pi latiki peataęž‰ walaęž‰tiki pu haemekeme.   
\s1 Polo Banabasi yaapo kaęž‰taęž‰alu pea taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pipikieki  
\p
\v 36 Kutupa nate mandaneeki hao Polomaęž‰ Banabasi paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Panaęž‰e ambaęž‰ hande Tekehalinaęž‰ pi walopaęž‰ da ninaęž‰ wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ eki paęž‰laęž‰pe laa handopanaęž‰ panaęž‰e leekeme.  
\v 37 Kutupa Banabasimaęž‰ Dioni Maka hatuku poluekemaęž‰ hone wiekepate  
\v 38 Polomaęž‰taęž‰ hone na wiekeme. Hande Paęž‰mbilia da nane hataęž‰ pi walo poluekemaęž‰ hone na wiki ipiliki minaęž‰paęž‰laeyeke handa anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 39 Kutupa ipilikaęž‰ pi taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pea kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homepeke handa potaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ pea potaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ pea pepekeme. Banabasimaęž‰ Maka ameĚ±leĚ± pita palai kawasonaęž‰ Saipotasi nane pepekepate  
\v 40 Polomaęž‰ Sailasi meaataęž‰ Ketiso haliwekimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki minaęž‰yeke tapaemekeme.  
\v 41 Kutupa puataęž‰ Sitia Silisia yaapo nane siosi wandaęž‰hali honkopu haenaęž‰ alo hataęž‰ pomu haepekeme.   
\c 16  
\s1 Timoditaęž‰ Polo Sailasi ameĚ±leĚ± pemekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Kutupa mo Debi Lisita da yaapo nane opolo epepekeme. Ketiso hali homeke Timodi koto paęž‰taęž‰ hayekeme. Ipikaęž‰ inkikitaęž‰ Diu wandaęž‰maęž‰ kone pi miniki hayeke wandaęž‰naęž‰ eiyeke hayekepate ipikaęž‰ ateketaęž‰ Kitiki hali hayekeme.  
\v 2 Mo Lisita Aikoniomo da yaaponaęž‰ Ketiso wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Timodi ipikaęž‰ pi lao haemekeme.  
\v 3 Polomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ Timodi yaapo poluekemaęž‰ mo some meaataęž‰ sekemesaisi hau peaeyekeme. Mo da ninaęž‰ haemeke Diu haliwekimaęž‰ Timodinaęž‰ ateketaęž‰ Kitiki halie laa handemeke handa peaeyekeme.  
\v 4 Mo daoni paęž‰taęž‰manu pomu lopolo hataęž‰ hande Diutuseleme aposolo haliwekimaęž‰ make handeteke haemeke tondiki haliwekimaęž‰ make lemeke pi manutaęž‰ mo Ketiso wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hone winaęž‰yeke la halaęž‰tiki pimikime.  
\v 5 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo hande siosi tapake manumaęž‰ hande pi minaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ honkopu honkopu hao nate paeyao daeyaemekeme.   
\s1 Polomaęž‰ upamaęž‰ piki nono piekeeki  
\p
\v 6 Kutupa mo Pitikia Kaęž‰leisia nane yaapo lombei pupa pemekepate mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ mo Eisia nane pi na walenaęž‰ leekeme.  
\v 7 Kutupa Maisia nane teke paęž‰taęž‰ opolo epemekepate Bidinia nane poluekemaęž‰ pu handemekepate Yesu ipikaęž‰ Sipitidimaęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ piekeme.  
\v 8 Kutupa Maisia da nane nepoko nanemaęž‰ pakaęž‰lao puaataęž‰ lombei pupa puataęž‰ Dotoaęž‰si da nane holaęž‰paęž‰niaemekeme.  
\v 9 Timba upamaęž‰ piki nono pea Polomaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ handeekeme. Maęž‰sedonia hali homekemaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ honke alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Maęž‰sedonia nane niki tambaęž‰ mulu aęž‰paęž‰peke laa leeke some homeke handeekeme.  
\v 10 Kutupa hande upamaęž‰ piki nono pikieki handaataęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ hande Pi Seliapo koto wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ walomono leaęž‰me hone witolo hataęž‰ mo Maęž‰sedonia nane poluekemaęž‰ kuta kone potaęž‰ weimikime.   
\s1 Pilipai wandaęž‰ Lidiamaęž‰ hone laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰ mina wiekeeki  
\p
\v 11 Dotoaęž‰si da minaęž‰paęž‰laotaęž‰ palai kawasonaęž‰ pitaęž‰ mo Saęž‰moteisi da nane tikitikinaęž‰ opolo puaataęž‰ nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ Niaęž‰polisi da nane opolo pomaęž‰me.  
\v 12 Koto paęž‰taęž‰ hao minaęž‰paęž‰laotaęž‰ mo Maęž‰sedonia nane teke da Pilipai da nane opolo pomaęž‰me. Koto da paęž‰taęž‰ make Lomaęž‰ haliweki wopu haemekeme. Koto daoni paęž‰taęž‰ nate mandaneeki haotaęž‰  
\v 13 kutupa Hoto Pilaęž‰ Nate ninaęž‰ mo daoninaęž‰ potaęž‰ kake tieke paęž‰taęž‰ tunkulupa pua ikali teaęž‰ nane pomaęž‰me. Nikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ koto alenaęž‰taęž‰ yeni pu halaęž‰ alenaęž‰ hone wiaataęž‰ kutupa pitiniao koto paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa mombelemeke wandaęž‰weki paęž‰taęž‰ pi pi lomaęž‰me.  
\v 14 Wandaęž‰ homeketaęž‰ Lidiamaęž‰ mo Daetaeda daoni nane wandaęž‰ aęž‰pa wepiki alemanu hambo hatiki pinaęž‰ laataęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao yeni pu haotaęž‰ nikaęž‰ pi opiaęž‰me. Polomaęž‰ waleeke pi opinaęž‰yeke Tekehalimaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰naęž‰ puki laęž‰kaęž‰laeyekeme.  
\v 15 Kutupa ipikaęž‰ tapake ameĚ±leĚ± bapitaisi pea hataęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ honke alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ pi na tunkuliki Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ epeke halome hone wimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ya da paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa hao hapaęž‰peke leaęž‰me. Kutupa honke wopu leeke handa pomaęž‰me.   
\s1 Pilipai da dipula pitipikieki  
\p
\v 16 Hoto maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ hande yeni pu haeme alenaęž‰ pomaęž‰pate potaęž‰naęž‰ tiĚ±oĚ± wandiki maęž‰ndaęž‰ mandaęž‰hande pumaęž‰me. Mo wandikimaęž‰taęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ pulu paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu la halolo haenaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ teke haliwekimaęž‰ mani wopu mu haemekeme.  
\v 17 Kutupa Polo nikaęž‰ hoke nanemaęž‰ teli mea ipulu hataęž‰ wi laęž‰tiki pea alotaęž‰ Do haliwekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ oli manda halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ tieke ipikaęž‰ e pokaaseme haliweki hataęž‰ mo hande deto halaęž‰ potaęž‰ iki walelememe leaęž‰me.  
\v 18 Kutupa nate paeyao kutu piaęž‰tiki pu hayaęž‰pate Polomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la mo temoko paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ alomaęž‰ mo wandiki minaęž‰paęž‰lao opolu bao yopuma leaęž‰me. Kutupa koto kone opolu baeyaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 19 Kutu piaęž‰pate mo wandiki ipikaęž‰ teke haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ Nikaęž‰ hone piaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ mani miaęž‰tiki pumaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ametaęž‰ paeyaęž‰me laa hone wiaataęž‰ Polo Sailasi yaapo daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ minaataęž‰ makedi paęž‰taęž‰ yolaęž‰ mea pua you haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ pitaemekeme.  
\v 20 Kutupa mo pi yokaalu peao haemeke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku pua alotaęž‰ Do Diu haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ da teke hoeyaasepeme lemekeme.  
\v 21 Nikitaęž‰ Lomaęž‰ haliwekitaęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ walelepe hau manutaęž‰ opua peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me lemekeme.  
\v 22 Kutupa mo hande mombaęž‰la pitimiki wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ tonkaęž‰naęž‰ ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰ mineke pankemekeme. Kutupa mo pi yokaalu peao haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ dau leisi mea bao dopita manumaęž‰ yombua baenaęž‰yeke pi lemekeme.  
\v 23 Kutupa mo hali yaapotaęž‰ wopu yombua baotaęž‰ dipula da paęž‰taęž‰ mea lopao mo dipula handeteke hayeke hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wopu handeteke hapeke laa pi la halemekeme.  
\v 24 Koto pi opuaataęž‰ mo hali ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ oni dipula da otaęž‰ tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ mea lopao ipilikaęž‰ anke meataęž‰ tinaęž‰ talao katolao pitaeyekeme.   
\p
\v 25 Kutu piekepate butaęž‰hokinaęž‰ Polo Sailasi yaapomaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni peaęž‰tiki pea emeli laęž‰tiki pipikime. Kutupa mo dipula da paęž‰taęž‰ pitimiki haliwekimaęž‰ opitolo haenaęž‰  
\v 26 koto kone yu momeni tieke wotu piekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo dipula da pinkimanu laęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰maęž‰ pieketaęž‰ koto kone mo hande da potaęž‰manu paeyao lomba wieketaęž‰ hali paeyaonaęž‰ seni pumanu pa kone kaęž‰laęž‰pe pa lopeekeme.  
\v 27 Mo dipula handeteke hayeke halimaęž‰ tiaotaęž‰ mo dipula da potaęž‰manu lomba pa pa pu wiekeeki handolotaęž‰ dipula haliweki ambaęž‰ pindipa yopua pimikaęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kepete hokulu yolaęž‰ mea ipikaęž‰ kone aoluekemaęž‰ handaeyekepate  
\v 28 Polomaęž‰ anekehapu wi alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ kone na liaęž‰pe. Niki paeyaotaęž‰ do pambo pilumaęž‰taa leekeme.   
\p
\v 29 Kutupa lamepa mea epo laa mo halimaęž‰ dipula da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ anke hao hondaęž‰ pambaataęž‰ pututumaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ paalaęž‰ pieke handaataęž‰ Polo Sailasi yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ lopaęž‰niao hali yaapo hamaęž‰ nane hatuku pua alotaęž‰  
\v 30 Hali yaapoo. Deto halaęž‰eki muluekemaęž‰taęž‰ eki peonope leekeme.  
\v 31 Ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehali Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaapeke. Kutu pikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ deto halaęž‰eki milipikie. Neke make nakaęž‰ weki wandaęž‰maęž‰ make milimikie lepekeme.  
\v 32 Kutupa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ pitimiki wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make mo hande Tekehalinaęž‰ pi alemanu walepekeme.  
\v 33 Kutupa koto pitaęž‰ kone ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ hatuku mea pua ipilikaęž‰ yumbieke alenaęž‰ ikalimaęž‰ tandepeekeme. Kutupa koto kone ipikaęž‰ weki wandaęž‰ ameĚ±leĚ± apaęž‰tao bapitaisi pimikime.  
\v 34 Kutupa ipikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ mo hali yaapo hatuku aęž‰pa ipilikaęž‰ ne haleekeme. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ weki wandaęž‰ ameĚ±leĚ± hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi mimiki ekinaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ wotu homemekeme.   
\p
\v 35 Da kelepeeketaęž‰ mo hande pi yokaalu peao haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ polisi haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Dipula handeteke hayeke hali paęž‰taęž‰ do pi lolo pupe laataęž‰ Mo hali yaapotaęž‰ pa penaęž‰ tapae laa lolo pupe lemekeme.   
\p
\v 36 Koto leeke ekinaęž‰ mo dipula handeteke hayeke halimaęž‰ koto pitaęž‰ Polo paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo pi yokaalu peao haleme haliwekimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pi dupa laęž‰nealaęž‰me. Koto hali yaapotaęž‰ pa penaęž‰ tapae laęž‰nealaęž‰me leekeme. Koto laęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ipilikitaęž‰ do dipula da pao yopu pupe laa leekeme.  
\v 37 Koto leekepate Polomaęž‰ mo polisi haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Dikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ na pupaęž‰pate wandaęž‰hali handaęž‰ potopoto la haenaęž‰ kone diki yumbua baememe. Dikitaęž‰ Lomaęž‰ Kapomaninaęž‰ pamodi wia halopaęž‰ hali yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ kone pimikime. Kotoeki peataęž‰ dikitaęž‰ dipula da paęž‰taęž‰ pa mea lopaememe. Kutupa ametaęž‰ aęž‰mbaaso hataęž‰ diki pa tapaaluekemaęž‰ lemepe. Otaęž‰ diaęž‰me. Mo hande pi yokaalu peao haleme haliweki ikanaęž‰maęž‰ kone do paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰paataęž‰ diki mea aęž‰pa tapaenaęž‰ loaęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 38 Mo polisi haliwekimaęž‰ Polomaęž‰ leeke pitaęž‰ mo pi yokaalu peao haemeke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ lolo pemekeme. Kutupa mo haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ Polo Sailasi yaapomaęž‰ Lomaęž‰ Kapomaninaęž‰ pamodi wia halepe hali yaapo halepeme leekeeki opuaataęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homemekeme.  
\v 39 Koto ekinaęž‰ Polo Sailasi yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ pua alotaęž‰ Ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰ pumaęž‰eki aęž‰taęž‰e laa lemekeme. Koto laataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hali yaapo dipula da minaęž‰paęž‰lao hatuku mea pua ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do daoni minaęž‰paęž‰lao pupe laa honke lemekeme.  
\v 40 Polo Sailasi yaapomaęž‰ mo dipula da minaęž‰paęž‰laotaęž‰ Lidianaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ pepekeme. Ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Ketiso wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± koto paęž‰taęž‰ mombaęž‰la hataęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ saęž‰tiaasaęž‰ pimanu laataęž‰ mo da minaęž‰paęž‰lao pepekeme.   
\c 17  
\s1 Desalonaika da paęž‰taęž‰ haemekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Kutupa Aęž‰mbipolisi Aęž‰polonia da yaapo nane lombei pupa mo Diu haliwekinaęž‰ pi hotu haemeke da homeke hayeke paęž‰taęž‰ Desalonaika da nane opolo pemekeme.  
\v 2 Kutupa Polomaęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambaataęž‰ hande pu hayekeeki pitolo hataęž‰ kutupa Hoto Pilaęž‰ Nate teponaęž‰ mo Baibolo buka pinaęž‰ pi yokaalu alu pitolo hataęž‰  
\v 3 Ketiso tanda pitaęž‰laęž‰eki ambaęž‰la meaataęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ homa tiaalieke laa wotu waleekeme.  
\v 4 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do hande IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ waloaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ otaęž‰ Ketisoe leekeme. Kutupa mandaneeki manumaęž‰ hone laęž‰kaęž‰lao hataęž‰ Polo Sailasi yaapo ameĚ±leĚ± taęž‰maęž‰ni pea haemekeme. Kutupa Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone wopu u haemeke Kitiki wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ make mandane keileke wandaęž‰wekimaęž‰ make kutu pimikime.   
\p
\v 5 Kutu pimikipate mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰ honditi pitolo hataęž‰ hoke wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ ti teke yoko haemeke haliweki mandaneeki meaataęž‰ haliweki mombaęž‰lenaęž‰ laataęž‰ mo daoni wandaęž‰hali paeyao laęž‰tia tia peaataęž‰ Dieisoninaęž‰ da bepolaluekemaęž‰ pimikipate mo hali yaapotaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku poluekemaęž‰ pimikime.  
\v 6 Kutupa na handaęž‰ wieke handaataęž‰ Dieisoni make mandane Ketiso haliweki make yola pua mo daoninaęž‰ kaĚ±leĚ±sete haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ wala wi la alotaęž‰ Hande kenke paeyao laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ do paęž‰taęž‰ make ipulimime.  
\v 7 Kutupa do Dieisonimaęž‰ iki handaęž‰ miaęž‰me lemekeme. Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Sisamaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu yambolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kini hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ halaęž‰me. Ipikitaęž‰ Yesue lo halememe laa lemekeme.  
\v 8 Koto pi opuaataęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ make mo daoninaęž‰ kaĚ±leĚ±sete haliwekimaęž‰ make pitiniao na pitiki Eki aęž‰ndaęž‰ hau aęž‰paapaęž‰naęž‰ wotu handeteke hamanaęž‰e laa haemekeme.  
\v 9 Kutupa Dieisoni amedamaęž‰ mo kapomanimaęž‰ lo wieke tupaęž‰ mo kode hamboemenaęž‰ laa mani aneke halemeke handa da tapaemekeme.   
\s1 Betia da paęž‰taęž‰ haemekeeki  
\p
\v 10 Koto kone mo Ketiso haliwekimaęž‰ Polo Sailasi yaapo Betia da paęž‰taęž‰ timba kone tapaemekeme. Kutupa mo da paęž‰taęž‰ opolo puataęž‰ Diu haliwekinaęž‰ pi hotu haemeke da paęž‰taęž‰ pemekeme.  
\v 11 Mo da Diu haliwekimaęž‰ Desalonaika Diu haliwekimaęž‰ pimiki hau na piki pa epeke tupaęž‰ hataęž‰ homu pea mo hande pi opuaataęž‰ Otaęž‰ekipe la handuluekemaęž‰ mo Baibolo buka paęž‰taęž‰ yataęž‰pa nate paeyao weiyaęž‰tiki pimikime.  
\v 12 Koto ekinaęž‰ paeyaomaęž‰ pi mimikime. Kutupa mandane Kitiki wandaęž‰weki tiekemanu make mandane Kitiki haliweki wopu make pi mimikime.  
\v 13 Kutu pimikipate mo Desalonaika Diu haliwekimaęž‰ Polomaęž‰ mo Betia da paęž‰taęž‰ make Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi ale walaęž‰laęž‰me pi opuataęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ make aęž‰paataęž‰ pa wandaęž‰hali sutiaaso hataęž‰ mineke pankaęž‰ tiaemekeme.  
\v 14 Kutupa mo Ketiso haliwekimaęž‰ Polotaęž‰ oni dawala ikali nane tapaemekepate Sailasi Timodi yaapotaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ haepekeme.  
\v 15 Hande Polo hatuku pemeke haliwekitaęž‰ mo Aęž‰taęž‰ni da nane ipiki hatuku puaataęž‰ Polomaęž‰ Sailasi Timodi yaapo do paęž‰taęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± epenaęž‰ lolo pupe leeke pi opuaataęž‰ pa laęž‰kaęž‰la pemekeme.   
\s1 Aęž‰taęž‰ni da paęž‰taęž‰ haemekeeki  
\p
\v 16 Kutupa Polotaęž‰ Aęž‰taęž‰ni da paęž‰taęž‰ mo hali yaapo epenaęž‰ handeteke hataęž‰ mo daoni teke da toopi timaęž‰ wepia wimiki ale manumaęž‰ tumbaęž‰pa peekeeki handolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ wotu homeekeme.  
\v 17 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo pi hotu haemeke da paęž‰taęž‰ mo Diu haliweki Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone wopu wimiki haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± mo makedi paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± make nate paeyao pi yokaalu peaęž‰tiki pimikime.  
\v 18 Kutupa mandane Epikutiani Sitoiki sukulu tapake yaaponaęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ Polo mandaęž‰hande pea alotaęž‰ Do hande pi wopu alaęž‰ halimaęž‰ eki leliepe lemekeme. Mandaneeki manumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Da maęž‰ndaęž‰ nane kodaęž‰ manunaęž‰ hau walaęž‰laęž‰ hali yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me lemekeme. Polomaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ make mo hande wandaęž‰hali homa pa tiaalo piekeeki waleeke handa lemekeme.  
\v 19 Kutupa Polo handaęž‰ mea mo hande Aęž‰tiopeikusi da paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku pua alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ koto hande wale panake pi niki paęž‰taęž‰ pa la kie lemekeme.  
\v 20 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ na wale pimanu waleleme. Kutupa koto pi teke opuluekemaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰me lemekeme.  
\v 21 Mo Aęž‰taęž‰ni da haliwekimaęž‰ make kimisu aęž‰pa pitimiki haliwekimaęž‰ make koto paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ nate paeyao aletaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ hone na wiki panake waleeke pi ombu opuluekemaęž‰ hotu haemekeme.   
\p
\v 22 Koto ekinaęž‰ Polomaęž‰ mo Aęž‰tiopeikusi da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ tiao hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aęž‰taęž‰ni haliwekio. Ikaęž‰ temoko paęž‰taęž‰ hone wopu u haleme ekitaęž‰ handolome leekeme.  
\v 23 Ikaęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao hataęž‰ yeni pu haleme ale manutaęž‰ pulu hataęž‰ handoaęž‰pate pa ikaęž‰ oloda homekenaęž‰ mo wape paęž‰laęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ dupa handaęž‰ uaęž‰me. Na hando halaęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ ekie handoaęž‰me. Kutupa koto ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao hataęž‰ na hando haleme Tekehalinaęž‰ pi kone ame iki paęž‰taęž‰ walolome leekeme.  
\v 24 Do kenke ya yaapo tukikinaęž‰ halaęž‰ ekimanu paeyao make wepia haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ Kodaęž‰taęž‰ hepeni kenke yaapo Tekehali hataęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ aęž‰eteleme damanu paęž‰taęž‰ na hao halaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 25 Kutupa kenke haliwekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokaenaęž‰ na laęž‰laęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ kone anaęž‰naęž‰ halaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ kone haliweki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰maęž‰ peao pomu haenaęž‰ alaęž‰eki make pomo minaęž‰laęž‰eki make alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao make ku halaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 26 Hali homeke paęž‰taęž‰ kone ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaonaęž‰ tapakemanu kenke paeyaonaęž‰ mea haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me leekeme. Kutupa ikaęž‰ natemanu wiaotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kenke tombomanu wiaotaęž‰  
\v 27 Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ ipiki weimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ handaęž‰ winaęž‰yeke piekeme leekeme. Kutu piekepate niki paeyaotaęž‰ ipiki tekepaęž‰taęž‰ halomaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 28 Ikaęž‰ mandane emeli lemeke haliwekimaęž‰ lemeke tupaęž‰  
\q1 Ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰maęž‰ pea pomu hataęž‰ hao halomaęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ weki wandiki otaęž‰ hataęž‰ pitolomaęž‰me lemekeme leekeme.   
\p
\v 29 Kutupa nikitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weki wandiki hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰taęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ hone niminao kolo silipa toopimaęž‰ wepitaęž‰laęž‰ alemaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰me hone na umanaęž‰ peaęž‰paęž‰pekealeo.  
\v 30 Hone wopu na wimiki pitaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ pa pinaęž‰ leekepate ametaęž‰ kenke wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Ikaęž‰ hoke hau minaęž‰paęž‰lao hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la winaęž‰ lapaęž‰peke alaęž‰me.  
\v 31 Pa ekipeke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ nate ambaęž‰ wiaeyeke handa alaęž‰me. Koto natenaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ hali homekemaęž‰ kenke wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ pi yokaalu tikitikinaęž‰ pinaęž‰ lelieke leekeme. Kutu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ opua Otaęž‰ekie hone winaęž‰yeke mo hande halitaęž‰ homa peneme yao paa mea tiaeyekeme laa leekeme.   
\p
\v 32 Kutupa mo hande homa pa mea tiaeyekeeki opuaataęž‰ mandane haliwekimaęž‰ ki taemekepate mandane haliwekimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do alo ekinaęž‰taęž‰ hoto maęž‰ndaęž‰ nakaęž‰ pi opulumekee laa lemekeme.  
\v 33 Koto ekinaęž‰ Polo opulu bao peekepate  
\v 34 mandane haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ taĚ±laĚ±aĚ±taęž‰ pi mimikime. Mo Aęž‰tiopeikusi hali homeke Dionisiusi make wandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ Damatisi make mandane haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± pi mimikime.   
\c 18  
\s1 Kotindi da paęž‰taęž‰ haemekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Kutupa Aęž‰taęž‰ni da minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo Kotindi da nane puaataęž‰  
\v 2 Diu hali homeke Akuila mo Pondasi da nane hali kone pua handeekeme. Koto halitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weteke Pisila yaapo mo Ideli nane minaęž‰paęž‰lao panake aęž‰pa haepekeme. Mo Sisa Kolodiusimaęž‰ Diu wandaęž‰hali paeyaotaęž‰ Lomaęž‰ da minaęž‰paęž‰lao pupe leeke handa epepekeme. Polomaęž‰taęž‰ ipiliki handuluekemaęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ peekepate  
\v 3 mo tooli make Polo make homeke e poko haemeke handa Polotaęž‰ ipiliki ameĚ±leĚ± pelia hao hatiki peaataęž‰ palai damanu epeaaso tumbulu haemekeme.  
\v 4 Kutupa Hoto Pilaęž‰ Nate paeyaonaęž‰ mo pi hotu haemeke da paęž‰taęž‰ Diu haliweki make Kitiki haliweki make ikaęž‰ hone laęž‰kaęž‰laluekemaęž‰ pi yokaalu piaęž‰tiki pu hayekeme.   
\p
\v 5 Kutupa Sailasi Timodi yaapo Maęž‰sedonia nane hao opolo epepeke pitaęž‰taęž‰ Polomaęž‰ mo Diu haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ Ketisoe la waluekemaęž‰ hone wotu wia walaęž‰tiki pu hayekeme.  
\v 6 Kutu piekepate ipiki tolu luekemaęž‰ pi la la pimiki pitaęž‰ Polomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ dau tandela iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ± diaęž‰me. Ikaęž‰ younaęž‰ ikaęž‰ we mendiaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme. Ya ketete diaęž‰me leekeme. Ametaęž‰ Diendaili wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pulume leekeme.  
\v 7 Kutupa Diu haliweki minaęž‰paęž‰lao Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao yeni pu hayeke hali homeke Taitasi Diasedasinaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ peekeme. Mo halinaęž‰ dataęž‰ mo hande pi hotu haemeke da nepoko nane kone hayekeme.  
\v 8 Mo pi hotu haemeke da you hali Kitisipusimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weki wandaęž‰ ameĚ±leĚ± pi mimikime. Kutupa Kotindi wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ make Polomaęž‰ waleeke pi opua meaataęž‰ bapitaisi pimikime.   
\p
\v 9 Kutupa Tekehalimaęž‰ timba upamaęž‰ tupaęž‰ Polo paęž‰taęž‰ leekeme. Dupa. Paalaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ neke pa na pitiki ya pi walaęž‰tiki pu hapeke leekeme.  
\v 10 Pa ekipeke IĚ±taęž‰ neke yaapo halome. Kutupa neke luekemaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ na tiaalieke leekeme. Do da paęž‰taęž‰ ya wandaęž‰hali wotu halememe laa leekeme.  
\v 11 Koto ekinaęž‰ Polomaęž‰ ba pi homekenaęž‰ sumbaęž‰ yunki mindiki hataęž‰ haotaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi alemanu iki paęž‰taęž‰ walaęž‰tiki pu hayekeme.   
\p
\v 12 Kutu piekepate Kaęž‰liotaęž‰ mo Akaya nane kapomani tieke haenaęž‰ leeke pitaęž‰taęž‰ mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰ Polo luekemaęž‰ apaęž‰tao pi yokaalu puluekemaęž‰ mea pua alotaęž‰  
\v 13 Do halimaęž‰taęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ Lo Pimanu yambolo hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniaenaęž‰yeke ikaęž‰ hone laęž‰kaęž‰lao halaęž‰me lemekeme.   
\p
\v 14 Koto lemekepate Polomaęž‰ pi loluekemaęž‰ haenaęž‰ Kaęž‰liomaęž‰ mo Diu haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Diu haliwekio. Hoke hau ketete tieke piekenaęž‰ yolutaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi opulu puaęž‰pate  
\v 15 ikaęž‰ Lo Pi manunaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone epeaapaęž‰peke. Koto pi manunaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ na lalueke. Ki paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 16 Kutupa hama tolu liekeme.  
\v 17 Kutupa paeyaomaęž‰ mo hande pi hotu haemeke da handeteke hayeke hali Sosenisi daęž‰kaęž‰pe minaataęž‰ mo pi yokaalu pu haemeke da hamaęž‰ nane hataęž‰ yombua baemekepate Kaęž‰liomaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ na leekeme.   
\s1 Aęž‰ndioko da nane paa pemekeeki  
\p
\v 18 Polotaęž‰ nate mandane ekimanu koto paęž‰taęž‰ haotaęž‰ mo Ketiso wandaęž‰hali minaęž‰paęž‰lao hande Pisila Akuila tooli ameĚ±leĚ± palai kawasonaęž‰ pita Sitia nane pemekeme. Senkitia da nane hataęž‰ pi laęž‰ wiekeeki loluekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ itiki tunkuliekeme.  
\v 19 Kutupa Epesese opolo aęž‰paataęž‰ ipiliki koto paęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰ laataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone mo pi hotu haemeke da paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pamba pua Diu haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± pi yokaalu pimikime.  
\v 20 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ Hosiki hapeke aleo lemekepate Polomaęž‰ Diaęž‰me laakaęž‰naęž‰  
\v 21 mo haliweki minaęž‰paęž‰lao pulu hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ hone piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pa ipulueke leekeme. Kutupa palai kawasonaęž‰ pita Epesese da minaęž‰paęž‰lao peekeme.   
\p
\v 22 Sesatia da opolo aęž‰paataęž‰ mo siosi tapake handuluekemaęž‰ aęž‰meiya puataęž‰ oni Aęž‰ndioko da nane holaęž‰paęž‰niao peekeme.  
\v 23 Koto paęž‰taęž‰ hosiki hao hao peaataęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo Kaęž‰leisia Pitikia yaapo nane hone tulaasaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ honkopu haenaęž‰ titipu peaaso hataęž‰ pomu lopo hayekeme.   
\s1 Apolositaęž‰ Epesese Kotindi da yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ hayekeeki  
\p
\v 24 Diu hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ Apolositaęž‰ Aęž‰lekesaęž‰ndia da hali mo Epesese da paęž‰taęž‰ epeekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ Baibolo buka pi hone wotu wia pi wotu yoka laęž‰tiki pieke halie.  
\v 25 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ hau ambaęž‰ waleeke handa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ wele pieke hali hataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ pieke ekimanu tikitiki yao walo hayekepate Dionimaęž‰ bapitaisi peaeyekeeki paęž‰taęž‰ homeke hone wiekeme.  
\v 26 Mo pi hotu haemeke da paęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ takaęž‰lao hataęž‰ pi hondaęž‰ mea waleekepate Pisila Akuila toolimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi opuaataęž‰ ipiki hatuku mea pua Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hau wopu walepekeme.  
\v 27 Ipikitaęž‰ Akaya da nane poluekemaęž‰ hone pieke pitaęž‰ mo Ketiso haliwekimaęž‰ Aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ polenaęž‰e laa oli da nane haemeke Ketiso haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ pase wape pea alotaęž‰ Do hali handaęž‰ meaęž‰paęž‰peke lemekeme. Kutupa opolo puaataęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ pi mimiki wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ wotu petelo hayekeme.  
\v 28 Hande Baibolo buka pi walolo hataęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ otaęž‰ Ketisoe laa mo Diu haliwekitaęž‰ penemenaęž‰ hataęž‰ pimaęž‰ bepolao hayeke handaa piekeme.   
\c 19  
\s1 Polo Epesese da paęž‰taęž‰ hayekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Apolosi mo Kotindi da paęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰ Polotaęž‰ mo hande potopinisi tukikinaęž‰ yopu yopu pea Epesese da opolo epeekeme. Koto da paęž‰taęž‰ mandane disaipolo haliweki handeekeme.  
\v 2 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ambaęž‰taęž‰ pi minolo hataęž‰ Holi Sipitidi mimipe leekeme. Kutupa mo haliwekimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Diaęž‰me. Mo Holi Sipitidi alaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hoto homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ na opumaęž‰me lemekeme.  
\v 3 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Epinaęž‰ bapitaisi hau pimipe leekeme. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Dionimaęž‰ bapitaisi peaeyeke haunaęž‰ pumaęž‰me lemekeme.  
\v 4 Kutupa Polomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Dionimaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la mina witolo haenaęž‰ bapitaisi peao hayekepate wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ya hoki nane ipilie halinaęž‰ pi meaęž‰paęž‰peke laa laęž‰laęž‰me leekeme. Koto ekitaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 5 Koto pi opuataęž‰ Tekehali Yesunaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ bapitaisi pimikime.  
\v 6 Kutupa Polomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kiki yaapo ikaęž‰ younaęž‰ wieketaęž‰ mo Holi Sipitidi iki paęž‰taęž‰ epeekeme. Kutupa pi taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ kone laakaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pimanu lemekeme.  
\v 7 Mo haliweki paeyaotaęž‰ 12manu haemekeme.   
\p
\v 8 Kutupa mo pi hotu haemeke da paęž‰taęž‰ puataęž‰ sumbaęž‰ teponaęž‰ hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homeke pi yokaalu peaęž‰tiki pea honke alo hataęž‰ pi laęž‰tiki piekeme.  
\v 9 Kutu piekepate mandane haliwekimaęž‰ pi na miki ki hone witolo hataęž‰ mo hande Haunaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali pa pitinaęž‰ hoke pi lemeke pitaęž‰ Polotaęž‰ mo Ketiso haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± koto haliweki minaęž‰paęž‰lao puataęž‰ Taitaęž‰nusinaęž‰ mombolo haemeke da paęž‰taęž‰ nate paeyao pi yokaalu peaęž‰tiki piekeme.  
\v 10 Koto hau pitolo haenaęž‰ bapi yaapo yaapeekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo Eisia wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ Kitiki wandaęž‰hali make Diu wandaęž‰hali make Tekehalinaęž‰ pi alemanu opimikime.   
\s1 Sikipanaęž‰ eiyeketiti  
\p
\v 11 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Polo paęž‰taęž‰ wele peaaso hataęž‰ na hando haemeke wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu peaenaęž‰ laęž‰tiki piekeme.  
\v 12 Koto ekinaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Polonaęž‰ yonkeleke paęž‰taęž‰ taĚ±leeke dau munku tupaęž‰ tumbulieke ekimanu make hako leke howao yameeke daumanu make yeni haemeke wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ mea pemekepate yeni tandelatiki pea hoke temokomanu opulu batiki pimikime.  
\v 13 Kutupa mandane pomuolo hataęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ weleke paęž‰taęž‰ pitieke hoke temoko tolu haemeke Diu haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ bikimaęž‰ koto hau puluekemaęž‰ taapemekeme. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mandane hoke temokomanu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Polomaęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰ hali Yesunaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ neke alomaęž‰maęž‰ yopuma lemekeme.  
\v 14 Koto hautaęž‰ mo yeni peao hayeke you haliwekinaęž‰ you hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ Siba ipikaęž‰ eiyeke watake hataęž‰maęž‰ pimikipate  
\v 15 pa mo hoke temokomaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yesu handolome. Kutupa Polo make handolopate ikitaęž‰ epi ameda kaęž‰taęž‰pe leekeme.  
\v 16 Kutupa mo hoke temoko pitieke halimaęž‰ mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ pua ponkaalo hataęž‰ lu tumbua tumbua pea bepolayekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo haliwekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hoeyao pa loke hameke hataęž‰ mo da minaęž‰paęž‰lao pindipa pemekeme.  
\v 17 Koto piekeeki mo Epesese da Kitiki pitaęž‰ Diu wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ opuakaęž‰naęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homemekeme. Kutupa Tekehali Yesunaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ kende tia wiekeme.  
\v 18 Kutupa pi mimiki wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ aęž‰paataęž‰ ikaęž‰ pu haemeke ekimanu na aęž‰mbaake kelepemekeme.  
\v 19 Kutupa make temoko paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pu haemeke wandaęž‰hali mandaneeki manumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ bukamanu homeke alenaęž‰ mea aęž‰pa wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ handolo haenaęž‰ timaęž‰ kitimikime. Kutupa mo buka paeyaonaęž‰ mani make yataęž‰pa handemekepate pa mo kinamanu 50 daoseni anaęž‰ piekeme.  
\v 20 Koto ekinaęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ pi alemanu daeyao kende tia pomu haemekeme.   
\s1 Epesese da paęž‰taęž‰ pi tieke laa wi lemekeeki  
\p
\v 21 Kutupa hande pimiki ekimanu paeyeketaęž‰ Polomaęž‰ Diutuseleme da nane poluekemaęž‰ Maęž‰sedonia Akaya yaapo nanemaęž‰ lopaęž‰laęž‰ poluekemaęž‰ hone wia alotaęž‰ Kutupa pua Lomaęž‰ da nane make handolo puaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 22 Kutupa ipiki tambaęž‰ mu haepeke hali yaapo Timodi Etaęž‰situsi yaapo mo Maęž‰sedonia nane tapaotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ mo Eisia nane pa hayekeme.   
\p
\v 23 Kutupa koto dinaęž‰taęž‰ hande Ketiso haunaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ liekeeki tiaeyekeme.  
\v 24 Hali homeke Dimiditiasimaęž‰taęž‰ silipa alemanu wepu hayeke halimaęž‰ Atemisinaęž‰ silipa wepia wieke alemanu wepitolo hataęž‰ kutu pu haemeke mandane haliwekimaęž‰ make bisinisi wotu pu haenaęž‰ leekeme.  
\v 25 Koto ekinaęž‰ Dimiditiasimaęž‰ mo hande haliweki make mo hande mandake e poko haemeke mandane haliweki make mombaęž‰lao iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Haliwekio. Do pitolomaęž‰ bisinisi e paęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ mani ipulaęž‰eki mu halomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ handelememe leekeme.  
\v 26 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ do Polomaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰eki opua hando halememe leekeme. Do Epesese da homeke diaęž‰laęž‰pate mo Eisia nane paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ make wandaęž‰hali wopunaęž‰ puki laęž‰kaęž‰lao alotaęž‰ Kikimaęž‰ wepia ulaęž‰ kodaęž‰ sunutaęž‰ otaęž‰eki diaęž‰me lo halememe leekeme.  
\v 27 Kutupa nikaęž‰ bisinisinaęž‰ hoke biki wiaapaęž‰naęž‰ homeke diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate mo hande kodaęž‰wandaęž‰ Atemisinaęž‰ toopimaęž‰ aęž‰eyaęž‰laęž‰ yeni hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ da make pa aletaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ handilieke laataęž‰ kutupa ipikaęž‰ pu halaęž‰eki make hoeyaalieke. Mo hande Eisia wandaęž‰hali make do kenke honiki honiki paęž‰taęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ make do kodaęž‰wandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pu halemepate diaęž‰me dupiki hau pilieke leekeme.   
\p
\v 28 Koto pi opuaataęž‰ mineke tieke pankolo hataęž‰ wi la alotaęž‰ Epesese wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Atemisitaęž‰ tiekee laa wi laęž‰tiki pimikime.  
\v 29 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo daoni wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hone ti yokolo hataęž‰ Polonaęž‰ taęž‰maęž‰ni pea pomu haemeke Maęž‰sedonia yankeketiti Kaiasi Aęž‰tisakusi yaapo yolaęž‰ mea anke hao mo mombolo haemeke alenaęž‰ pemekeme.  
\v 30 Polomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ polueke hone wiekepate mo disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ pimikime.  
\v 31 Kutupa Polonaęž‰ yankeketiti mandaneeki manumaęž‰taęž‰ kaĚ±leĚ±sete haliweki hataęž‰ kone ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pi tapao alotaęž‰ Mo mombolo haleme alenaęž‰ na puaęž‰pe laa honke lemekeme.  
\v 32 Kutupa mo mombelemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hone ti yokolo hataęž‰ mandane haliwekimaęž‰ wi maęž‰ndaęž‰ laęž‰tiki mandane haliwekimaęž‰ wi maęž‰ndaęž‰ laęž‰tiki pimikime. Kutupa mandane wandaęž‰hali woputaęž‰ hone wotu na wiki pa mombelemekeme.  
\v 33 Mandane haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰ mea haenaęž‰ lemeke hali Aęž‰lekesaęž‰nda paęž‰taęž‰ ha la lemeke handa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi loluekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kiki tindipao wanke yaeyekepate  
\v 34 ipikitaęž‰ Diu halie laa handolo hataęž‰ paeyaomaęž‰ aowaęž‰ yaapo tupaęž‰ homeke pi ombu wi alo alotaęž‰ Epesese wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Atemisitaęž‰ tiekee laa wi lo haemekeme.   
\p
\v 35 Kutupa mo daoni kusikusi halimaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paeyao homu peaokaęž‰naęž‰ alotaęž‰ Epesese haliwekio. Hande ya nanemaęž‰ lopaęž‰niaeyeke toopi taęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Atemisi tiekenaęž‰ yeni hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ da Epesese daoni paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hali epimaęž‰ na opaęž‰laęž‰pe leekeme.  
\v 36 Koto ekimanu tunkula paapeke na yaęž‰leke handaataęž‰ ikitaęž‰ pa hau na piki yopu hapaęž‰peke aleo leekeme.  
\v 37 Do hatuku epeme haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ kodaęž‰wandaęž‰naęž‰ hau na hoeyaake ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hoke pi na lememe leekeme.  
\v 38 Koto ekinaęž‰ Dimiditiasi ipikaęž‰ e mandake pokeleme haliwekitaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ ketete ulaęž‰me hone wimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ pi yokaalu pu haleme damanu halaęž‰me. Kutupa mo pi yokaalu pitaęž‰laęž‰eki handeteke haleme haliweki make hao halememe. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pua lenaęž‰e leekeme.  
\v 39 Kutupa pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ make loluekemaęž‰ hone wimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo hande mombolo halomaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ aęž‰pa lapaęž‰peke leekeme.  
\v 40 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ ame pa hameke hone mateke pi laa wi lomeke handaataęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ samani peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 41 Kotoeki laakaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali tapaa tapaa piekeme.   
\c 20  
\s1 Mo Maęž‰sedonia Kitiki yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ pemekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Mo hande poiyaęž‰ poiyaęž‰ laęž‰ alualu pimikieki upa lopa haenaęž‰taęž‰ Polomaęž‰ hone tulaemeke wandaęž‰hali wi laęž‰ mepi pea iki paęž‰taęž‰ saęž‰tiaasaęž‰ pimanu laataęž‰ aęž‰taloe laa koto paęž‰taęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo Maęž‰sedonia nane peekeme.  
\v 2 Koto da paęž‰taęž‰manu pi waloendi pitolo hataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali honkopu ha tiatiki piekeme. Kutupa hao Kitiki kenke nane opolo puataęž‰  
\v 3 sumbaęž‰ tepo koto paęž‰taęž‰ hayekeme. Sitia nane poluekemaęž‰ tikitiki yaaso haenaęž‰ Diu haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki luekemaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombo haemekeeki opuaataęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la mo Maęž‰sedonia nanemaęž‰ lopaęž‰laęž‰ yapulueke hone wiekeme.  
\v 4 Mandane haliweki ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ pemekeme. Paitusinaęž‰ eiyeke mo Betia da hali Sopade make Aęž‰tisakusi Sekundusi yaapotaęž‰ Desalonaika da hali yaapo make mo Debi da hali Kaiasi make mo Eisia potopinisi hali tepotaęž‰ Timodi Tikikasi Totobimasi koto hali tepo make Polo ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ pemekeme.  
\v 5 Iki ambaęž‰la titinaęž‰ pua mo Todoaęž‰si da paęž‰taęž‰ niki pomono hando haemekeme.  
\v 6 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Na Pombei Yaake Palaowa Ne pamba paeyeketaęž‰ Pilipai da paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ palai kawasonaęž‰ pita pulu hamono nate yunki hataęž‰ paeyeketaęž‰ mo Todoaęž‰si da paęž‰taęž‰ opolo puataęž‰ mo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± mandake paęž‰taęž‰ hamono pula homeke yapeaęž‰me.   
\s1 Polomaęž‰ paeyaaso hataęž‰ Todoaęž‰si da handolo peekeeki  
\p
\v 7 Mo Sande natenaęž‰ nikitaęž‰ palaowa pindi pindi puluekemaęž‰ mombaęž‰la hamono Polomaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi waleaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ da kaęž‰laęž‰paaso polueke hone wiaataęž‰ timba butaęž‰hokinaęž‰ make pi ombu waleaęž‰me.  
\v 8 Kutupa nikanaęž‰maęž‰ mombolomaęž‰ da mandataęž‰ lamepa wopu teaęž‰me.  
\v 9 Kutupa wekihali homeke Yutaęž‰kusitaęž‰ windo lombaeyaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pitiaęž‰me. Kutupa Polomaęž‰ pi ombu alo pitinaęž‰ mo wekihali uĚ± tondaęž‰pao pita uĚ± peliaęž‰me. Kutupa uĚ± otaęž‰ peliaęž‰pate da yaapo ankulao oni kenkenaęž‰ lopeeke handa pua mea aęž‰meiyaemepate otaęž‰ homeaęž‰me.  
\v 10 Kutu pimipate Polomaęž‰ holaęž‰paęž‰niao kenkenaęž‰ hataęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao mo wekihali hopulaęž‰ mea alotaęž‰ Paalaęž‰ na hake hone na wiaęž‰pe. Ipikitaęž‰ pa do daęž‰ta pilaęž‰me leaęž‰me.  
\v 11 Kutupa Polotaęž‰ paa aęž‰meiya puataęž‰ palaowa pindi pindi pea naakaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± pi ombu alo alo pita da kelepeeke handa minaęž‰paęž‰lao peekeme.  
\v 12 Kutupa hande wekihali daęž‰ta tiao hayeke handa hone wopu bao hatuku pemekeme.   
\s1 Todoaęž‰si da minaęž‰paęž‰lao Mailitasi da paęž‰taęž‰ pemekeeki  
\p
\v 13 Kutu piaęž‰pate niki ambaęž‰la puataęž‰ mo palai kawaso tiekenaęž‰ pitataęž‰ Todoaęž‰si da minaęž‰paęž‰lao Polotaęž‰ Asosi da paęž‰taęž‰ mandaęž‰hande puluekemaęž‰ pomaęž‰me. Polomaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Potaęž‰naęž‰ pua mo Asosi da paęž‰taęž‰ opolo aęž‰pono pupe leeke handa pomaęž‰me.  
\v 14 Mo Asosi da paęž‰taęž‰ mandaęž‰hande pea Polo make kawasonaęž‰ aęž‰pa pitataęž‰ Mitilini da paęž‰taęž‰ puataęž‰  
\v 15 da maęž‰ndaęž‰ kelepeeketaęž‰ Seose hoki teke paęž‰taęž‰ opolo pomaęž‰me. Da maęž‰ndaęž‰ kelepeeketaęž‰ Saęž‰mosi paęž‰taęž‰ puataęž‰ kutupa da maęž‰ndaęž‰ kelepeeketaęž‰ Mailitasi opolo pomaęž‰me.  
\v 16 Polomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ mo Eisia nane haenaęž‰ nate paeyaamaęž‰naęž‰ Epesese da lombei pupa puataęž‰ mo hande Diutuseleme da paęž‰taęž‰ opolo polo paęž‰laęž‰ natetaęž‰ Pendikosi nate aĚ±iĚ± na paeyeke haenaęž‰ opolo puluekemaęž‰ hone wiaęž‰me.   
\s1 Tondiki haliweki minaęž‰paęž‰lao poluekemaęž‰ hataęž‰ leeke pimanu  
\p
\v 17 Kutupa Mailitasi da hao mo Epesese da nane pi tapaasotaęž‰ mo siosi wandaęž‰hali handeteke haemeke tondiki haliwekitaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ epenaęž‰yeke pi tapaeyaęž‰me.  
\v 18 Kutupa mo haliwekitaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ opolo epeme pitaęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Eisia nane panake aęž‰pa iki paęž‰taęž‰ haowaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ handememe leaęž‰me.  
\v 19 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ eĚ± alo hataęž‰ homu peaataęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ hau peaaso hano hande Diu haliwekimaęž‰ IĚ± luekemaęž‰ taapolo hataęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaemeeki manutaęž‰ handememe leaęž‰me.  
\v 20 Iki epeaalo piaęž‰eki iki na aęž‰mbaake walo haowaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ handememe leaęž‰me. Kutupa da maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ make mombaęž‰la pitimi tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ make walo haowaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ handememe leaęž‰me.  
\v 21 Kutupa Diu wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make Kitiki wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make ikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰ minaęž‰ wiaataęž‰ nikaęž‰ Tekehali Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ pi miniki haenaęž‰yeke walo haowaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ handememe leaęž‰me.  
\v 22 Kutupa ametaęž‰ IĚ± do handaęž‰pe leaęž‰me. Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ IĚ± hone yapaęž‰ peaaso haenaęž‰ Diutuseleme da nane pulume. Kutupa koto alenaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pulu paęž‰laęž‰ hau IĚ± mataęž‰laęž‰pate  
\v 23 mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ daoni paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ mo dipula pitaęž‰ tanda pulu paęž‰laęž‰eki IĚ± la ku halaęž‰me leaęž‰me.  
\v 24 Kutu paęž‰laęž‰pate ya lokenaęž‰ hau hone na witolome laa tombonaęž‰ opolo puaataęž‰ ya Tekehali Yesumaęž‰ waleaęž‰ hau ambaęž‰la paeyaalueke leaęž‰me. Hande Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pa hameke aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homo halaęž‰ Pi Seliapo la kitoloeki loaęž‰me leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 25 Kutupa ametaęž‰ opuaęž‰pe. Iki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ pominolo hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki waloendi pu haowaęž‰pate IĚ±maęž‰ handolome. Ya leke mineke paa na handilimikie leaęž‰me.  
\v 26 Koto ekinaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pi do alo handaęž‰pe leaęž‰me. IĚ±taęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰me yako pilume. Iki paeyaonaęž‰ we IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ diaęž‰me leaęž‰me.  
\v 27 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ na aęž‰mbaake Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hau paeyao iki paęž‰taęž‰ waloaęž‰me leaęž‰me.  
\v 28 Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ handeteke halo peleme haliweki mea haminaęž‰ leeke handa ikaęž‰ kone handeteke hao mo maęž‰naęž‰titi paeyao make handeteke hapaęž‰peke leaęž‰me. Tekehalimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Eiyekenaęž‰ wemaęž‰ kone mieke tapake wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ handeteke hapaęž‰peke leaęž‰me.  
\v 29 IĚ±maęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao poluaęž‰ natenaęž‰ kaĚ±ęž‰laĚ±ęž‰taęž‰ pu halaęž‰ tikene kika titimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰paataęž‰ do maęž‰naęž‰ titinaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ na homilimikie leaęž‰me.  
\v 30 Kutupa iki paęž‰taęž‰ kone mandane haliwekimaęž‰ tiaotaęž‰ mo Ketiso wandaęž‰hali yolaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ hoke pi alemanu lelimikie hone ulume leaęž‰me.  
\v 31 Koto ekinaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ handeteke hao hapaęž‰peke. Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ bapi teponaęž‰ u peliaęž‰laęž‰eki yolao da kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰laęž‰eki yolao iki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ eĚ± alo hataęž‰ pi walo haowaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 32 Kutupa ametaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ pa aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ pi ale paęž‰taęž‰ make iki halolome. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ iki daeyaapeke yao ipikaęž‰ talopu mea haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± ikaęž‰ anke teke mulu pelemeeki anaęž‰naęž‰ kiaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me leaęž‰me.  
\v 33 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ silipa kolo dau leke na polopaotaęž‰  
\v 34 ya do kiki yaapomaęž‰ e pokaa IĚ± ameĚ±leĚ± haeme haliweki nikaęž‰ meaęž‰peke yeke ekimanu mu haowaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ iki handememe leaęž‰me.  
\v 35 Koto puaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ e wopu pokolo hataęž‰ honkopu na hake hali tambaęž‰ mumanaęž‰yeke waloaęž‰me leaęž‰me. Tekehali Yesumaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ pi hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke dupae. Aletaęž‰ aletaęž‰ halolo hataęž‰ otaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaasaęž‰ekie. Minolo hataęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ wopu diaęž‰me laęž‰laęž‰me leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 36 Koto pi laakaęž‰naęž‰ tumiki yotuao iki paeyao ameĚ±leĚ± homeke paęž‰taęž‰ pitaęž‰ yeni piaęž‰me.  
\v 37 Kutupa paeyaomaęž‰ eĚ± alo hataęž‰ Polo hopulu mea nunu pimime.  
\v 38 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ya leke mineke paa na handilimikie leeke handaa aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ wotu homememe. Kutupa mo palai kawaso paęž‰taęž‰ ipiki hatuku pememe.   
\c 21  
\s1 Polotaęž‰ Diutuseleme da nane peekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taloe la iki minaęž‰paęž‰lao pomaęž‰me. Palai kawasonaęž‰ pitataęž‰ tikitikinaęž‰ tunkula pua Kosi da paęž‰taęž‰ pomaęž‰me. Kutupa da maęž‰ndaęž‰ kelepeeketaęž‰ Lodesi da paęž‰taęž‰ opolo puataęž‰ pa mo Padata da paęž‰taęž‰ pomaęž‰me.  
\v 2 Koto da paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ Pinisia nane polu piaęž‰ palai kawaso maęž‰ndaęž‰ handaęž‰ wiaataęž‰ koto kawasonaęž‰ pita pomaęž‰me.  
\v 3 Koto pulu hataęž‰taęž‰ Saipotasi hoki handomaęž‰pate koto hoki nepoko nane pua mo Sitia nane pomaęž‰me. Taiya da paęž‰taęž‰ opolo puataęž‰ kenkenaęž‰ holaęž‰pa pomaęž‰me. Koto Taiya da paęž‰taęž‰ mo kawasonaęž‰ mea wia pemeke alemanu londolo wimime.  
\v 4 Koto paęž‰taęž‰ pua mandane disaipolo wandaęž‰hali handaęž‰ wiaataęž‰ pula homeke iki ameĚ±leĚ± pelia haomaęž‰me. Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone u tiaaso haenaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Polo paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Diutuseleme da nane na puaęž‰peke aleo laa lememe.  
\v 5 Koto lemepate nikitaęž‰ koto da paęž‰taęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± haomaęž‰ di paeyeketaęž‰ iki minaęž‰paęž‰lao pomaęž‰me. Koto haliweki paeyaomaęž‰ ikaęž‰ weki wandaęž‰ paeyao ameĚ±leĚ± make daoni nane niki hatuku tapaalo epememe. Kutupa niki paeyaomaęž‰ koto dawala ikali teaęž‰naęž‰ tumiki yotuao pitaęž‰ yeni pumaęž‰me.  
\v 6 Niki paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taloe la alu alu peaataęž‰ nikitaęž‰ mo palai kawasonaęž‰ pitulu pomono ikitaęž‰ da laęž‰kaęž‰la pememe.   
\p
\v 7 Nikitaęž‰ Taiya da minaęž‰paęž‰lao kawasonaęž‰ pita mo Tolemese da paęž‰taęž‰ opolo pomaęž‰me. Koto paęž‰taęž‰ haeme Ketiso wandaęž‰hali kiki minaęž‰ alu alu pea hoto homeke iki ameĚ±leĚ± polumaęž‰me.  
\v 8 Da kaęž‰laęž‰paotaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo Sesatia da nane opolo puataęž‰ kutupa hande pi walo hayaęž‰ hali Pilipinaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambomaęž‰me. Mo Diutuseleme da nane ambaęž‰ hande maĚ±leke limi 7 dikoni haliweki kone homeketaęž‰ ipikie.  
\v 9 Kutupa ipikaęž‰ wandiki tonkoputaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi laęž‰ u haemeke potopede wandikitonu haemekeme.  
\v 10 Nate mandaneeki koto paęž‰taęž‰ hamono potopede hali homeke Akipasi Diudia nane hao epeaęž‰me.  
\v 11 Kutupa niki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pataęž‰ Polonaęž‰ baęž‰taęž‰ido hako meaataęž‰ anke kiki ipikaęž‰ kone tonkao alotaęž‰ Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ do alaęž‰me leaęž‰me. Mo Diutuseleme da nane Diu haliwekimaęž‰ do baęž‰taęž‰ido hako teke hali mea tonkao mo Diendaili haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ ipiki mea hatuku pelimikie alaęž‰me leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 12 Kotoeki opuaataęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ haeme wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± nikanaęž‰maęž‰ Polo paęž‰taęž‰ Diutuseleme da nane na polenaęž‰e laa honke lomaęž‰me.  
\v 13 Kutupa Polomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikitaęž‰ do eĚ± eĚ± aleme ekimaęž‰ ya puki hoeyaaluekemaęž‰ alemepe leaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ Tekehali Yesunaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ mo Diutuseleme da nane dipula pituluekemaęž‰ homeke na loaęž‰me. Otaęž‰ homuluekemaęž‰ kone tikitiki yao halome leaęž‰me.  
\v 14 Kutupa ipikaęž‰ hone laęž‰kaęž‰laapeke na yeke handa nikanaęž‰maęž‰ kiao alotaęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki pinaęž‰e lomaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 15 Kutupataęž‰ nikaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ hombo pea wia oli Diutuseleme da nane pomaęž‰me.  
\v 16 Kutupa mandane Sesatia Ketiso wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ niki ameĚ±leĚ± puataęž‰ mo Saipotasi hali Menasonitaęž‰ titinaęž‰ pi mieke hali ipikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ hamonoyeke niki hatuku pememe.   
\s1 Polomaęž‰ Diaęž‰mesi handolo peekeeki  
\p
\v 17 Diutuseleme da nane pomaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ Ketiso wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ niki handaęž‰ mimime.  
\v 18 Kutupa da kaęž‰laęž‰paotaęž‰ mo handeteke haemeke tondiki haliweki paeyao pitinaęž‰ Polo ameĚ±leĚ± nikitaęž‰ Diaęž‰mesi handolo pomaęž‰me.  
\v 19 Kutupa Polomaęž‰ keiyae pi laa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ pi walaęž‰ tia pomieke pitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo Diendaili wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pieke ekimanu homeke homeke lo la halaęž‰tiki piaęž‰me.  
\v 20 Kutupa mo haliwekimaęž‰ kotoeki opuaataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi laememe. Kutupa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kameo. Hande Diu haliweki paeyaomaęž‰ pi mimiki ekitaęž‰ handeleme. Paeyaomaęž‰ hande Lo Pimanu opuluekemaęž‰ hone wotu witelemepate  
\v 21 mandane haliwekimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ lemekeeki dupa. Hande hali Polomaęž‰ mo Diendaili wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± haleme Diu haliweki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Mosesimaęž‰ waleekeeki minaęž‰paęž‰lao ikaęž‰ wekisunu sekemesaisi hau na piki Diu haliwekimaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰eki na peaęž‰paęž‰peke laa walo halaęž‰mee alememe lememe.  
\v 22 Koto ekinaęž‰ eki pumanaęž‰pe. Mo haliwekimaęž‰ neke epeleeki otaęž‰ opilimikie lememe.  
\v 23 Koto ekinaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ lolo polomaęž‰eki peaęž‰peke lememe.  
\v 24 Tonkopu haliwekimaęž‰ nindi pea do halememe. Do haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± hataęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ loke epeao kutupa ikaęž‰ you itiki makole minaęž‰yeke ikaęž‰ yenki halawapeke lememe. Koto ekinaęž‰ paeyaomaęž‰ nakaęž‰ hande Lo Pimanu opiteleeki handolo hataęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ leme pimanu na opilimikie lememe.  
\v 25 Kutu paęž‰laęž‰pate hande pi mimiki Diendaili wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ wape tapaaso dupiki pi lomaęž‰me. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ toopi timaęž‰ wepia ulaęž‰ alemanu paęž‰taęž‰ lia halaęž‰eki na neke we make na neke daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ mina homaasaęž‰eki make na neke kutupa loke hoeyaasaęž‰eki make na pinaęž‰e lomaęž‰me lememe.  
\v 26 Kutupa Polomaęž‰ mo hande haliweki hatuku puataęž‰ da kaęž‰laęž‰paotaęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± ipikaęž‰ loke epeao mo tembolo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambaataęž‰ pua hande loke epeaasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ natemanu la ulu ekimaęž‰ make mo haliweki paeyaonaęž‰ yenki halawaaluekemaęž‰ pemekeme.   
\s1 Tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ Polo daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ minimikieki  
\p
\v 27 Hande nate watake hataęž‰ paeluekemaęž‰ haenaęž‰ mo Eisia nane hao epemeke Diu haliwekimaęž‰ Polo mo hande tembolo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hayekeeki handaataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao sutiao Polo daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ mina hataęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\v 28 Isulai haliwekio. Aęž‰pa niki paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰pe lemekeme. Nikaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make mo hande Lo Pimanu paęž‰taęž‰ make do da paęž‰taęž‰ make wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ hoke hone winaęž‰yeke laęž‰tia pominaęž‰laęž‰ hali doe lemekeme. Kutupa make do tembolo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ Kitiki haliweki hatuku aęž‰paataęž‰ do pi ulaęž‰ da ambaęž‰ hoeyaeyaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me laa lemekeme.  
\v 29 Ambaęž‰taęž‰ Polo mo hande Epesese da hali Totobimasi yaapo daoni nane pomipikieki hando hao ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ Polomaęž‰ koto hali tembolo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku mea pulu piaęž‰me hone wimikime.   
\p
\v 30 Kutupa mo daoni wandaęž‰hali paeyao tiao anke hao pua homeke paęž‰taęž‰ mombaęž‰la hataęž‰ Polo daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ mina mo tembolo da hamaęž‰ nane yolaęž‰ mea pua kutupa kuta kone mo potaęž‰manu hambemekeme.  
\v 31 Kutupa Polo otaęž‰ lia homaaluekemaęž‰ taapolo haenaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande Lomaęž‰ ami haliwekinaęž‰ tumiki hali paęž‰taęž‰ pua alotaęž‰ Diutuseleme da wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ mombaęž‰la hataęž‰ wi laa pa pi takaęž‰lake la alu alu pitelememe pua leekeme.  
\v 32 Koto pi opuataęž‰ mo tumiki halimaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± koto kone ipikaęž‰ ami mandane haliweki ikaęž‰ opisa haliweki tonkaęž‰naęž‰ oni wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ anke hao hatuku peekeme. Kutupa wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo ami tumiki hali ipikaęž‰ ami haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± epemekeeki handaataęž‰ Polo litolo haemeke ekitaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰laemekeme.  
\v 33 Kutupa mo hande aęž‰ndaęž‰ tumiki halimaęž‰ aęž‰pa Polo minataęž‰ seni pu yaapomaęž‰ hotape leekeme. Kutupa Polotaęž‰ hane halipe eki hau piaęž‰pe laa lotaęž‰ piekeme.  
\v 34 Mo mombelemeke haliweki mandane ekimaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ wi laęž‰tiki pa mandaneeki manumaęž‰ pi taęž‰taęž‰ wi laęž‰tiki kutupa wi laęž‰tiki pimiki ekimaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tumiki halimaęž‰ opuaęž‰peke na yeke handaataęž‰ Polotaęž‰ mo ami haliwekinaęž‰ halaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku pupe leekeme.  
\v 35 Kutupa mo wataęž‰pe lieke alenaęž‰ opolo peekepate pa mo mombela mineke pambemeke haliwekimaęž‰ pasaęž‰tei puaęž‰tiki pemeke handaataęž‰ mo ami haliwekimaęž‰ Polo kikimaęž‰ minaęž‰liao opaęž‰liaemekeme.  
\v 36 Pate mo haliwekimaęž‰ teliaęž‰ mea pulu hataęž‰ wi alo alotaęž‰ Homenaęž‰ lie laa laęž‰tiki pimikime.   
\s1 Polomaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ kone ipikaęž‰ pi leekeeki  
\p
\v 37 Polomaęž‰taęž‰ mo ami haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ halaęž‰ da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ ipiki hatuku opolo puluekemaęž‰ haenaęž‰ mo aęž‰ndaęž‰ tumiki hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neke paęž‰taęž‰ pi siki lonope leekeme.  
\v 38 Kutupa mo somemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kitiki pitaęž‰ neketaęž‰ opelepe leekeme. Neketaęž‰ mo hande Idiepi hali diaęž‰yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe laataęž‰ Neketaęž‰ kapomani mea lopaaluekemaęž‰ mo 4 daoseni pi uleke yambolo haemeke haliweki sutiao mo hapu hayeke alenaęž‰ hatuku peeke hali diaęž‰yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe leekeme.  
\v 39 Polomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Diu halie. Mo Silisia nane Tasaęž‰si teke da tiekenaęž‰ da hali hao epoaęž‰me leekeme. Wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi loluekemaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ honke alome leekeme.  
\v 40 Kutupa mo halimaęž‰ Aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me lolenaęž‰e leeke handa Polomaęž‰taęž‰ mo wataęž‰pe manda hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kikimaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi paape laakaęž‰naęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi pi na leke haenaęž‰ Polomaęž‰ mo Hibulu pi laa iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰   
\c 22  
\p
\v 1 Kame apaęž‰titio. Iki paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ame do alo pi opuaęž‰pe leekeme.  
\v 2 Kutupa iki paęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Hibulu pi laa leekeeki opuakaęž‰naęž‰ pi pi na leke pa haemekeme. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰   
\p
\v 3 IĚ±taęž‰ Diu hali mo hande Silisia nane halaęž‰ da Tasaęž‰si da paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± mendiekepate do daoni tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ daeya polome. Kutupa Kamalielenaęž‰ sukulu da pita nikaęž‰ apaęž‰ amedanaęž‰ Lo haumanu sukulu wotu peakaęž‰naęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ ame hone wotu witeleme tupaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ make hone u halome.  
\v 4 Kutupa do hande Hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ambaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ wotu litolo hataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ minataęž‰ dipula da paęž‰taęž‰ mea lopao haowaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 5 Mo yeni peao haleme you haliwekinaęž‰ you halimaęž‰ make mo kaĚ±leĚ±sete haliwekimaęž‰ make handememe leekeme. Mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ Damasikasi hameke titinaęž‰ pasemanu meakaęž‰naęž‰ oli da nane Ketiso wandaęž‰hali muluekemaęž‰ poaęž‰me leekeme. Mo wandaęž‰hali mea tonkao Diutuseleme da nane hatuku aęž‰pa panisi peaaluekemaęž‰ puaęž‰me leekeme.   
\s1 Polomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰ miniekeeki  
\p
\v 6 Potaęž‰naęž‰ puakaęž‰naęž‰ mo Damasikasi da nane opolo poluekemaęž‰ pulu hano nate you tikekenaęž‰ haenaęž‰ oli ya nanemaęž‰ epeaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± tiekemaęž‰ IĚ± hapisaęž‰ pea to hopaęž‰liaeyaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 7 IĚ±taęž‰ kenkenaęž‰ hondaęž‰pa lopa wiono pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰makemaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ dupa laęž‰niaeyaęž‰me. Solo. Solo. Ekipeke IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ litelepe laa laęž‰niaeyaęž‰me.  
\v 8 Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Neketaęž‰ epikaęž‰taęž‰pe laa laęž‰liaowaęž‰pate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Naęž‰saęž‰tete hali Yesue. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ liteleke puaęž‰me laa laęž‰niaeyaęž‰me.  
\v 9 Kutupa IĚ± ameĚ±leĚ± haeme haliwekimaęž‰ hande paĚ±aĚ± piaęž‰eki handemepate oli ya nane pi laęž‰niaeyaęž‰ halinaęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰maketaęž‰ na opimime leekeme.  
\v 10 Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Eki peonope loaęž‰me. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tiao. Mo Damasikasi da paęž‰taęž‰ pua pitikaęž‰naęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰pa nakaęž‰ pulu peleeki la kilieke laa laęž‰niaeyaęž‰me.  
\v 11 Mo hande paĚ±aĚ± wotu pieke handa IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ handaęž‰peke na yeke hano mo IĚ± ameĚ±leĚ± haeme haliwekimaęž‰ yaka kiki mina mo Damasikasi da paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± hatuku pememe.  
\v 12 Kutupa hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ Aęž‰naęž‰naisitaęž‰ hande Lo Pimanu wotu opu hayeke hali make koto paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke Diu haliweki paeyaomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi lao hatiki pimiki hali IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ epoaęž‰me.  
\v 13 Kutupa teke paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ya kame Soloo. Ametaęž‰ nakaęž‰ leke ki laa handaęž‰peke laa leaęž‰me. Kutupa koto kone yaka leke ki leeke handa ipiki handoaęž‰me.  
\v 14 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nikaęž‰ apaęž‰meinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ neketaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki handoelenaęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ Tikitikinaęž‰ halaęž‰ hali handolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kakemaęž‰ laęž‰niaeyaęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make opuelenaęž‰yeke neke maĚ±leke lilaęž‰me.  
\v 15 Koto ekinaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ handeeki make opieki make wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ la halaęž‰tiki pilipikie.  
\v 16 Kutupa ametaęž‰ ekipeke hando halepe. Tiao pua bapitaisi hau pea ipikaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ wi alo hataęž‰ nakaęž‰ hoke hau pi ekimanu tandaęž‰penaęž‰ lapeke leaęž‰me leekeme.   
\s1 Polomaęž‰ Diendaili wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi laenaęž‰ wi leekeeki  
\p
\v 17 Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰ Diutuseleme da nane paa aęž‰pa hataęž‰ mo tembolo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pitolo hataęž‰ upamaęž‰ leke  
\v 18 Tekehali handoaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ya la halawaasaęž‰eki do wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ na opilimikie. Koto ekinaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± tiao do Diutuseleme da minaęž‰paęž‰lao puaęž‰peke laa leaęž‰me.  
\v 19 Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Mo pi hotu haleme damanu paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ pi mimi wandaęž‰hali mea yombuaęž‰tiki pea dipula mea lopatiki puaęž‰eki mo haliwekimaęž‰ handememe.  
\v 20 Kutupa nakaęž‰ la halawaeyaęž‰ hali Sidipeninaęž‰ we lopaeme pitaęž‰ IĚ± make koto paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ make aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me lipe laa ipiki limi haliwekinaęž‰ daumanu miniki haowaęž‰me loaęž‰me.  
\v 21 Koto loaęž‰pate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Pue. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ papate kone pa mo Diendaili wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ neke tapaalueke leaęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 22 Hande wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Polonaęž‰ pi ambaęž‰ opimikipate mo koto leekeeki opuaataęž‰ takaęž‰lake pi la alu alu pea alotaęž‰ Do hali lumanaęž‰e. Apaęž‰e. Ipikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ homaenaęž‰ lapeke aleo leekeme.  
\v 23 Kutupa pi takaęž‰lake pi la alu alu pitolo haenaęž‰ ikaęž‰ daumanu wankea wankea pitolo haenaęž‰ dokolo apolo lopaliaaso haenaęž‰  
\v 24 mo aęž‰ndaęž‰ tumiki halimaęž‰ Polotaęž‰ mo baliki da paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku mea epenaęž‰ laakaęž‰naęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ koto takaęž‰lake pi la alu alu pimiki ekinaęž‰ teke weiluekemaęž‰ Polo yombinaęž‰ leekeme.  
\v 25 Kutu piekepate pumaęž‰ Polo tonkaemeke pitaęž‰ Polomaęž‰ ipiki teke paęž‰taęž‰ hayeke ami opisa hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Lomaęž‰ da pamodi mea wia halaęž‰ halitaęž‰ pi yokaalu na piki yumbolo hautaęž‰ anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰pe laa leekeme.   
\p
\v 26 Koto pi opuaataęž‰ mo opisa halimaęž‰ hande aęž‰ndaęž‰ tumiki hali paęž‰taęž‰ pua alotaęž‰ Eki puluekemaęž‰ pitelee laa do halitaęž‰ Lomaęž‰ pamodi wia halaęž‰ halie leekeme.  
\v 27 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo aęž‰ndaęž‰ tumiki halimaęž‰ Polo paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ la kie. Neketaęž‰ Lomaęž‰ pamodi wia halaęž‰maęž‰ leaęž‰ halipe leekeme. Kutupa Polomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aowe leekeme.  
\v 28 Mo aęž‰ndaęž‰ tumiki halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka pamodi wia halo ekitaęž‰ mani tiekemaęž‰ hamboaęž‰me laa leekepate Polomaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Kutu paęž‰laęž‰pate IĚ± mendiaęž‰ alenaęž‰ kone pamodi mea puaęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 29 Hande Polonaęž‰ pu hayeke ekinaęž‰ teke weilu pimiki haliwekimaęž‰ koto leekeeki opuaataęž‰ kuta kone yolaęž‰ pamba tikitiki puaęž‰tiki pua haemekeme. Kutupa mo aęž‰ndaęž‰ tumiki hali make Polotaęž‰ hande Lomaęž‰ pamodi wia halaęž‰ hali mea tonkao puaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me laa paalaęž‰maęž‰ homeekeme.   
\s1 Polotaęž‰ kaĚ±leĚ±sete haliwekinaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ hayekeeki  
\p
\v 30 Kutupa da kelepeeketaęž‰ mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰ Polo baęž‰saęž‰ pimiki ekinaęž‰ otaęž‰ teke lotaęž‰ pu handuluekemaęž‰ mo aęž‰ndaęž‰ tumiki halimaęž‰ Polonaęž‰ tonkaemekeeki kaęž‰laęž‰pakaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo Diunaęž‰ yeni peao haemeke you haliweki make ikaęž‰ kaĚ±leĚ±sete haliweki paeyao make mombelenaęž‰ laataęž‰ Polotaęž‰ mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku mea aęž‰pa haenaęž‰ leekeme.   
\c 23  
\p
\v 1 Kutupa Polomaęž‰ mo kaĚ±leĚ±sete haliweki wotu handake witolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kametitio. Hokeeki na piki Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ hatiki pea ame make hataęž‰ puaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 2 Kutupa mo yeni peao haemeke you haliwekinaęž‰ you hali Aęž‰naęž‰naisimaęž‰ Polo teke paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ Polonaęž‰ kake daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ linaęž‰e leekeme.  
\v 3 Kutupa Polomaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ neke lieke. Neketaęž‰ yayapiki hau pu halaęž‰ halie leekeme. Mo hande Lo Pimanu manaęž‰ leeke ekinaęž‰ pi yokaalu puluekemaęž‰ koto handeteke pilipateto hande Lo Pimanu na opiki nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± pa linaęž‰ leme leekeme.   
\p
\v 4 Hande ipiki teke paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yeni peao haleme you haliwekinaęž‰ you hali paęž‰taęž‰ hoke pi pa lelipikipe lemekeme.  
\v 5 Kutupa Polomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kametitio. Ipikitaęž‰ yeni peao haleme you haliwekinaęž‰ you halie hone na uaęž‰me leekeme. Hande wape pea ulaęž‰eki doe. Nakaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ you hali paęž‰taęž‰ hoke pi na lapeke laęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 6 Kutu piekepate Polomaęž‰ mo hande kaĚ±leĚ±sete haliweki handaataęž‰ mo Saęž‰dusi Paęž‰tisi yaapo tapake haliweki aęž‰pa pitaęž‰ pelememe hone wia iki paęž‰taęž‰ pi anekemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kametitio. IĚ±taęž‰ Paęž‰tisi hali hataęž‰ Paęž‰tisi tapake weki mendiaęž‰me laataęž‰ Do IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pi yokaalu piteleme ekitaęž‰ hande IĚ± polo tupaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali mea tiaalo paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ pitelememe laa leekeme.  
\v 7 Koto pitaęž‰ Polomaęž‰ leeke handa mo Saęž‰dusi Paęž‰tisi yaapo tapake haliwekimaęž‰ ape ape laa kaęž‰taęž‰ alu alu pea taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pea haemekeme.  
\v 8 Mo hande Saęž‰dusi tapake haliwekimaęž‰ lo haemeke ekimanu dupa Homemeke wandaęž‰hali paa na mea tialieke laa mo enisolo tapaketaęž‰ na hao hataęž‰ pelememe laa make mo temokomanu make na pitaęž‰ pelememe laa lo haemekepate mo Paęž‰tisi tapake haliwekimaęž‰ koto pi paeyao opu haemekeme.  
\v 9 Kutupa ape ape alo hataęž‰ mandane Paęž‰tisi tapake Wape pea walaęž‰tiki pu haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ tiao alotaęž‰ Do halitaęž‰ eki aęž‰ndaęž‰ ketete make na handaęž‰ witolomaęž‰me. Enisolomaęž‰ o temokomaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ la piaęž‰pe niki mataęž‰laęž‰me lemekeme.  
\v 10 Kutupa mo hande ape ape daeyao lemeke handa mo aęž‰ndaęž‰ tumiki halimaęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ Polo mea pa lusinki paamaęž‰naęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aęž‰ndeli miniki haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ Polo pendilao mea mo ami haliwekinaęž‰ halaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku penaęž‰yeke pi laa tapaeyekeme.   
\p
\v 11 Kutupa nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ timba Tekehalimaęž‰ Polo teke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Honkopu hapeke. Do Diutuseleme da paęž‰taęž‰ yaka pi la halawaeye tupaęž‰ mo Lomaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ make pi la halawaalenaęž‰e leekeme.   
\s1 Polo luekemaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombemekeeki  
\p
\v 12 Kutupa da kelepeeketaęž‰ Diu haliwekimaęž‰ tome tome pamba nindi pea alotaęž‰ Ne ikali aĚ±iĚ± na neke hataęž‰ Polo ambaęž‰la lumanaęž‰e lemekeme.  
\v 13 Kutupa mo 45 tupaęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ nindi pea koto lemekeme.  
\v 14 Kutupa mo yeni peao haemeke teke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ make mo tondiki haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ make pua alotaęž‰ Nikaęž‰ kone otaęž‰ nindi tieke pea Ne ikali aĚ±iĚ± na neke hataęž‰ Polo ambaęž‰la lumanaęž‰e lomaęž‰me lemekeme.  
\v 15 Koto ekinaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo kaĚ±leĚ±sete haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± hataęž‰ mo aęž‰ndaęž‰ tumiki hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi tapaapaęž‰peke dupa. Hande Polotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi yokaalu otaęž‰ tikitikinaęž‰ pumanaęž‰yeke hatuku aęž‰paęž‰peke laa tapaapaęž‰peke lemekeme. Kutupa Polotaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na opolo pa ipulu haenaęž‰ kone ambaęž‰ lulumeke lemekeme.   
\p
\v 16 Polo ipikaęž‰ belikinaęž‰ eiyekemaęž‰ hande haliwekimaęž‰ yuwia pituluekemaęž‰ lemekeeki opua puataęž‰ mo ami haliwekinaęž‰ halaęž‰ da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pamba Polo paęž‰taęž‰ pua la haleekeme.  
\v 17 Kutupa Polomaęž‰ opisa hali homeke epenaęž‰ wi laęž‰ mea alotaęž‰ Do wekihalitaęž‰ mo aęž‰ndaęž‰ tumiki hali paęž‰taęž‰ la halenaęž‰yeke hatuku puaęž‰peke leekeme.  
\v 18 Koto ekinaęž‰ hatuku mea pua mo aęž‰ndaęž‰ tumiki hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hande dipula pilaęž‰ hali Polomaęž‰ IĚ± wi la alotaęž‰ Do wekihalimaęž‰ mo aęž‰ndaęž‰ tumiki hali paęž‰taęž‰ pua la halenaęž‰yeke hatuku puaęž‰peke leaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 19 Mo aęž‰ndaęž‰ tumiki halimaęž‰ hande wekihalinaęž‰ kiki mina hosiki mo pate leke hatuku pua tome tome la lotaęž‰ pea alotaęž‰ Eki pi la kuluekemaęž‰ lepe leekeme.  
\v 20 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰ tome tome pamba mo Polonaęž‰ pi yokaalu tikitikinaęž‰ puluekemaęž‰ belia neke paęž‰taęž‰ laa mo kaĚ±leĚ±sete haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku epoelenaęž‰ honke lelimikie lememe leekeme.  
\v 21 Koto lelemepate nakanaęž‰maęž‰ na opuaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke mo 45 tupaęž‰ haleme haliwekimaęž‰ nindi pea ne ikali aĚ±iĚ± na neke koto Polotaęž‰ titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la lumeke laa potaęž‰naęž‰ yuwia pitaęž‰ tikitiki yao nakaęž‰ lolo peleeki opuluekemaęž‰ handeteke pitaęž‰ pelememe laa leekeme.  
\v 22 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo aęž‰ndaęž‰ tumiki halimaęž‰ hande wekihali Pu la alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pua IĚ±maęž‰ la hala puaęž‰me pi na lapeke leekeme.   
\s1 Polotaęž‰ mo kapomani teke hali Pilikisi paęž‰taęž‰ tapaeyekeeki  
\p
\v 23 Koto laakaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tumiki halimaęž‰ opisa hali yaapo epenaęž‰ wi laęž‰ mea alotaęž‰ Ame timba 9 okoloko tupaęž‰ mo ami haliweki 200 make hosi maęž‰naęž‰ hokinaęž‰ pitu haleme ami haliweki 70 make dolo miniki haliweki 200 make Sesatia da nane penaęž‰yeke ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ tikitiki yao haenaęž‰ lapaęž‰peke.  
\v 24 Kutupa Polo pitulu paęž‰laęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰manu mea haenaęž‰ laataęž‰ mo kapomani you hali Pilikisi paęž‰taęž‰ yopu handeteke hatia hatuku puaęž‰peke leekeme.  
\v 25 Koto laataęž‰ mo ami you halimaęž‰ tameiyaęž‰ homeke dupa wape piekeme.   
\q1
\v 26 Kolodiusi Laisiasimaęž‰ nikaęž‰ kapomani you hali Pilikisi neke paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae alome.  
\v 27 Do halitaęž‰ Diu haliwekimaęž‰ daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ mina hataęž‰ otaęž‰ luekemaęž‰ taapolo haenaęž‰ yaka ami haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± IĚ±maęž‰ opolo pua peteloaęž‰me. Ipikitaęž‰ Lomaęž‰ pamodi mea wia halaęž‰ hali yeke handa puaęž‰me.   
\b  
\p
\v 28 Ikaęž‰ baęž‰saęž‰ pimi pi teke weiluekemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kaĚ±leĚ±sete haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku poaęž‰pate  
\v 29 mo baęž‰saęž‰ pimi pitaęž‰ pa ikaęž‰ Lo Pi manunaęž‰ pimime. Koto ekinaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ dipula mea pitapeke o homenaęž‰ lapeke ekitaęž‰ anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me handaęž‰ uaęž‰me.  
\v 30 Kutupa haliwekimaęž‰ Polo luekemaęž‰ tome tome pambemekeeki maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ la kieke handaa neke paęž‰taęž‰ koto kone tapaasome. Kutupa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ baęž‰saęž‰ piteleme haliwekimaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ baęž‰saęž‰ pinaęž‰ loaęž‰me loaęž‰me laa wape piekeme.   
\p
\v 31 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo ami haliwekimaęž‰ koto ikaęž‰ you halinaęž‰ manaęž‰ pi opuataęž‰ Polo meaataęž‰ timba kone mo Aęž‰ndipatisi da paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku pemekeme.  
\v 32 Kutupa da kelepeeketaęž‰ mo hosi maęž‰naęž‰ hokinaęž‰ pitu haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ Polo hatuku mea tapaalo mo ami haliwekitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ halaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la epemekeme.  
\v 33 Kutupa Sesatia da nane opolo puataęž‰ mo kapomani you hali paęž‰taęž‰ mo pase halaakaęž‰naęž‰ Polo make hatuku pua haenaęž‰ lemekeme.  
\v 34 Kutupa mo kapomani you halimaęž‰ hande pase yataęž‰pakaęž‰naęž‰ Polo paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pea alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ hando potopinisi halipe leekeme. Kutupa Polotaęž‰ Silisia nane halie leekeeki opua  
\v 35 ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neke paęž‰taęž‰ baęž‰saęž‰ pimiki haliweki opolo epemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakaęž‰ pi opulueke leekeme. Kutupa mo Hetodinaęž‰ da tieke paęž‰taęž‰ mea pita kade haliwekimaęž‰ handeteke haenaęž‰yeke leekeme.   
\c 24  
\s1 Diu haliwekimaęž‰ Polo samani pimikieki  
\p
\v 1 Kutupa nate yunki hataęž‰ paeyeketaęž‰ mo yeni peao haemeke you haliwekinaęž‰ you hali Aęž‰naęž‰naisi make mandane handeteke haemeke tondiki haliweki make pi lalo pieke hali homeke Tetalusi make opolo epemekeme. Kutupa ikaęž‰ samani pimiki pi Polo paęž‰taęž‰ mo kapomani you hali paęž‰taęž‰ laakaęž‰naęž‰  
\v 2 kutupa Polo aęž‰pa haenaęž‰ mo Tetalusimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ baęž‰saęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰  
\p Epeke you hali Pilikisio. Neketaęž‰ niki handeteke hataęž‰ hone wopu wiki hali hale ekinaęž‰ nikitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ kone aęž‰ndaęž‰ pelia hao halomaęž‰me. Kutupa halomaęž‰pate nakanaęž‰maęž‰ make nikaęž‰ kenke paęž‰taęž‰ halomaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali epeaaluekemaęž‰ tikitiki hau peaasaęž‰ ekimanu ambaęž‰ peaaleme.  
\v 3 Koto pele ekinaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ do kenke paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ hoto paeyao neke paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ keiyae pi lo halomaęž‰me.  
\v 4 Koto pele ekinaęž‰ nakaęž‰ nate paeyaapaęž‰naęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ pi hokulu na leke nikaęž‰ lolo polomaęž‰ pi sikitaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ epeke hone witolo hataęž‰ opuelenaęž‰yeke neke honke alo loaęž‰me.  
\v 5 Do hande halimaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali hao hoeyaenaęž‰ dupi dupi laa sutiao halaęž‰ hali halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ handomaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ do kenke paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ Diu haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ sembaęž‰lalo paęž‰laęž‰ pi laęž‰tiki pomu halaęž‰me. Ipikitaęž‰ mo Naęž‰saęž‰tini tapake wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ you hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ halaęž‰me.  
\v 6 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ hande tembolo da hoeyaaluekemaęž‰ taapeekepate daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ minumaęž‰me.  
\p [Nikaęž‰ Lo Pi manumaęž‰ alaęž‰ tupaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hali paęž‰taęž‰ puluekemaęž‰ pumaęž‰pate  
\v 7 mo aęž‰ndaęž‰ tumiki hali Laisiasimaęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambolo aęž‰paataęž‰ nikaęž‰ kiki yolaęž‰ mepi bao honkopu hao do hali paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ mea hatuku peaęž‰me.  
\v 8 Koto hau pea Laisiasimaęž‰taęž‰ do hali paęž‰taęž‰ samani pimi haliwekitaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa haenaęž‰ dupeaęž‰peke laa leaęž‰me.]  
\p Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ do hali paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ do hali paęž‰taęž‰ samani pumaęž‰ pitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ lelie pi nakanaęž‰maęž‰ kone opilipikie laa leekeme.  
\v 9 Mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰ make Polo samani pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Koto hande leaęž‰ ekimanu paeyaotaęž‰ otaęž‰ leaęž‰eki nikanaęž‰maęž‰ make handolomaęž‰me laa lemekeme.   
\s1 Polomaęž‰ Pilikisi paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi leekeeki  
\p
\v 10 Polomaęž‰ pi lenaęž‰yeke mo kapomani you halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ you mea aęž‰meiyaeyekeme. Kutu pieketaęž‰ Polomaęž‰ handataęž‰ pi alo alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ bapi elekeeleke do kenke paęž‰taęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ pi yokaalu peao halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ hone ulume. Koto ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ make ya pu halo ekimanu neke paęž‰taęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolome.  
\v 11 Ambaęž‰taęž‰ da kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰laęž‰eki 12 tupaęž‰ koto natenaęž‰ kone oli Diutuseleme da paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao yeni puluekemaęž‰ poaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ nakaęž‰ kone weiya handaęž‰ wiaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 12 Mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo tembolo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ ameĚ±leĚ± ape alo hano maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± na aęž‰pa handeaęž‰me. Mo pi hotu haleme da paęž‰taęž‰manu make mo daoni tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ make aletaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ make IĚ±maęž‰ wandaęž‰hali sutia tia pitolo hano hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± na aęž‰pa handeaęž‰me.  
\v 13 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate do IĚ± aęž‰pa samani peleme pimanu make IĚ±maęž‰ otaęž‰ polo ekimanu do haliwekimaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ la kiaęž‰paęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 14 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ do lolo polo pitaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi lolueke. Mo haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ yayapiki hau aleme Hau kone IĚ±maęž‰ teliaęž‰ mea pulume. Kutu puluekemaęž‰ yaka apaęž‰mei amedanaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao yeni pu halome. Kutupa make mo Mosesimaęž‰ wape pea ulaęž‰ Lo Pimanu paeyao make mo potopede haliwekimaęž‰ wape pea ulaęž‰ buka manunaęž‰ pi paeyao make IĚ±maęž‰ opu halome.  
\v 15 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ pulu paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao hataęž‰ handeteke hao halo tupaęž‰ do haliwekimaęž‰ make Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ koto tupaęž‰ halememe. Dupae. Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaotaęž‰ epeke wandaęž‰hali make hoke wandaęž‰hali make homa lapaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mea tiaalieke.  
\v 16 Kutu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ nate paeyao Kodaęž‰naęž‰ leke minekenaęž‰ hataęž‰ make wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ leke minekenaęž‰ hataęž‰ make yaka pu halo hau paęž‰taęž‰ hokeeki maęž‰ndaęž‰ taapaęž‰paapaęž‰naęž‰ hone wotu wia hao halome.   
\p
\v 17 Diutuseleme da nane mandane bapi manunaęž‰ IĚ± na poaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ numaneke aęž‰ndaęž‰ poaęž‰pitaęž‰taęž‰ yaka wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ mani mea pua halaotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ haluekemaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ make lia haloaęž‰me.  
\v 18 Mo tembolo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ koto hau pitolo hataęž‰taęž‰ mo hali wamo pitolo pu halaęž‰ hau pu paeyao hano kone mo haliwekimaęž‰ IĚ± aęž‰pa handememe. Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ haliweki wopu IĚ± ameĚ±leĚ± mandake paęž‰taęž‰ na aęž‰pa haememe. Haliwekimaęž‰ poiyaęž‰ poiyaęž‰ na aęž‰pa lememe.  
\v 19 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate mo Eisia potopinisi nane hao epeleme Diu haliweki mandane ekimanu koto paęž‰taęž‰ haememe. Koto haliweki ikanaęž‰maęž‰ kone IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ hone wimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa ikaęž‰ samani piteleme pi lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ epelieke.  
\v 20 Do haleme haliwekimaęž‰ make IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ kaĚ±leĚ±sete haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ yaka pi loaęž‰ pitaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ pu hoeyao hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ handaęž‰ wimi ekitaęž‰ lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ epelieke.  
\v 21 Koto haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ tiao hataęž‰taęž‰ pi homeke homeke wi laa dupa loaęž‰me. Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ lapaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali mea tiaalo paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ kutu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ hone tulao halo ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ame ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± pi yokaalunaęž‰ mea hasememe laa leekeme.   
\p
\v 22 Koto leeketaęž‰ Pilikisimaęž‰taęž‰ mo Hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki dupae laa maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ la haleeke handaataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Pi anaęž‰ma. Paape laa leekeme. Mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo aęž‰ndaęž‰ tumiki hali Laisiasi opolo epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi tikitiki yao lalueke leekeme.  
\v 23 Koto laataęž‰ mo Polo handeteke hayeke ami opisa paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Polo handeteke hataęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ dipula pilaęž‰ hali tupaęž‰ na handeteke hake ipikaęž‰ yankeke titimaęž‰ otaęž‰ meaęž‰peke alemanu mea epemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ na peaęž‰peke laa leekeme.   
\s1 Polomaęž‰ Pilikisi Datusila yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ pi leekeeki  
\p
\v 24 Hoto mandane ekimanu haotaęž‰ Pilikisi ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ Datusila yaapo epepekeme. Datusilataęž‰ Diu tapake wandaęž‰e. Pilikisimaęž‰taęž‰ Polo aęž‰pa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pi lenaęž‰yeke epoe laa laęž‰moneaeyekeme. Polomaęž‰taęž‰ Yesu Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaasaęž‰ pi teke la halolo hataęž‰taęž‰  
\v 25 tikitiki hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki hone tulaasaęž‰ pi teke la halolo kone anaęž‰naęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ make Kodaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ pi yokaalu pulu paęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ make kutupiki pi leekepate Pilikisimaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ametaęž‰ pue laa Nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ waleke wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ epoelenaęž‰ paa wi loluekemaęž‰ ametaęž‰ pue leekeme.  
\v 26 Pilikisimaęž‰ hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ make dupa wiekeme. Polomaęž‰ mani maęž‰ndaęž‰ kinaęž‰e hone wiekeme. Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ Polo epenaęž‰ wi laęž‰tiki pea Polo yaapo pi laęž‰tiki pipikime.   
\p
\v 27 Kutupa hao bapi yaapo yapeeketaęž‰ Pilikisimaęž‰ kapomani you hali hayaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ pa Posiasi Pesitasimaęž‰ miekeme. Kutu pieketaęž‰ Pilikisimaęž‰taęž‰ mo Diu haliweki taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaaluekemaęž‰ Polotaęž‰ dipula pa pitaęž‰ pelia haenaęž‰ laa peekeme.   
\c 25  
\s1 Polomaęž‰taęž‰ Sisamaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi yokaalu peaenaęž‰ honke leekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Pesitasi mo potopinisi nane opolo aęž‰paataęž‰ hoto tepo hao mo Sesatia da minaęž‰paęž‰lao oli Diutuseleme da nane peekeme.  
\v 2 Koto da paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke yeni peao haemeke you haliwekimaęž‰ make mo Diu you haliwekimaęž‰ make ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Polo samani pimiki pitaęž‰ Pesitasi paęž‰taęž‰ la halemekeme. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Pesitasi paęž‰taęž‰ honke alo alotaęž‰  
\v 3 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ epeke hone wiomono Polotaęž‰ do Diutuseleme nane epenaęž‰ lae lemekeme. Koto lemeke pitaęž‰ Polotaęž‰ potaęž‰naęž‰ ipulu haenaęž‰ luekemaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombaęž‰ wia lemekeme.  
\v 4 Pesitasimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Polotaęž‰ Sesatia nane dipula pa pilaęž‰me. Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ hosiki hao koto da nane paa laęž‰kaęž‰la polueke. Mo halimaęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ pu hoeyaalaęž‰eki wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰  
\v 5 kotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ you haliwekimaęž‰ IĚ± ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ Sesatia da paęž‰taęž‰ pua mo hali paęž‰taęž‰ samani piki pi loaęž‰minaęž‰e laa leekeme.   
\p
\v 6 Koto pi laataęž‰ Pesitasi ipikitaęž‰ hoto ketepo hataęž‰ o noĚ±iĚ± hataęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± pelia hao Sesatia da paęž‰taęž‰ peekeme. Pua da kelepeeketaęž‰ mo pi yokaalu pu haemeke da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pua pitataęž‰ Polo hatuku ipupe laa leekeme.  
\v 7 Kutupa Polo opolo aęž‰pa haenaęž‰taęž‰ mo Diutuseleme da hao epemeke Diu haliwekimaęž‰ Polo dupao hataęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do halimaęž‰taęž‰ hoke hoke ane mone haumanu wopu pu halaęž‰ halimaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me lemekepate mo otaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰eki tekemanu na laęž‰ yokemekeme.  
\v 8 Koto lemekepate Polomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Lo Pimanu paęž‰taęž‰ make mo tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ pi wilimi ekimanu paęž‰taęž‰ make mo Lomaęž‰ kapomani hali Sisa paęž‰taęž‰ make hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ na polome laa leekeme.   
\p
\v 9 Pesitasimaęž‰ mo Diu haliweki taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰ tiaaluekemaęž‰ Polo paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do hande samani piteleme pitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ nakaęž‰ pi yokaalutaęž‰ oli Diutuseleme da nane peaano poluekemaęž‰ hone witelepe laa lotaęž‰ piekeme.  
\v 10 Koto leeke Polomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Sisamaęž‰ pi yokaalu peao halaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ do halotaęž‰ laataęž‰ do da paęž‰taęž‰ kone peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Do Diu haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ na poloeki make nakaęž‰ kone handeleme.  
\v 11 IĚ±maęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki otaęž‰ yambaęž‰laęž‰ meaęž‰peke yenkitaęž‰ homolo poloeki meaęž‰peke yeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ± na pindipa polueke. Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate pa yayapikieki laa IĚ± samani pitolo lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± mea halaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Sisamaęž‰ kone yaka pi yokaalu peaenaęž‰ honke alome laa leekeme.   
\p
\v 12 Koto leeketaęž‰ Pesitasimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ potaęž‰ epeaaseme haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± pi pi ambaęž‰la laa Polomaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Sisamaęž‰ nakaęž‰ pi yokaalu peaenaęž‰ honke le ekinaęž‰ kotaęž‰ Sisa paęž‰taęž‰ pelipikie laa leekeme.   
\s1 Akatipa paęž‰taęž‰ Polomaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu la haleekeeki  
\p
\v 13 Mandane pulamanu hao mo kini hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ Akatipataęž‰ Benisi yaapo Pesitasi paęž‰taęž‰ kiki haluekemaęž‰ mo Sesatia da paęž‰taęž‰ epepekeme.  
\v 14 Koto paęž‰taęž‰ hoto mandane ekimanu aęž‰pa haenaęž‰taęž‰ Pesitasimaęž‰ Polomaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu kini hali paęž‰taęž‰ la halolo alotaęž‰ Do paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ hali homeketaęž‰ Pilikisimaęž‰ dipula mea pitao peekeme.  
\v 15 IĚ±taęž‰ Diutuseleme da nane poaęž‰ pitaęž‰taęž‰ mo yeni peao haleme teke haliweki make tondiki haliweki make paeyao Diu haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ samani peaataęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ honke alo alotaęž‰ Do halitaęž‰ hoke hau paęž‰laęž‰ halie lae la honke lememe.  
\v 16 Koto lemepate IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Lomaęž‰ haliweki nikaęž‰ hautaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ pa hameke kone kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Haliwekimaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hokeeki piaęž‰me laa samani pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo ipiki samani pilimi haliwekinaęž‰ leke minekenaęž‰ hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰eki alo hataęž‰ mo haliwekinaęž‰eki hombo peaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 17 Mo haliwekitaęž‰ do paęž‰taęž‰ epemeketaęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ handaęž‰ pelia na hake da kelepeaęž‰eke kone mo pi yokaalu pu halomaęž‰ da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pua pitaęž‰ mo hali hatuku epenaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 18 Mo ipiki samani pimi haliwekimaęž‰ tiao hataęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ samani piteleme pimanu lemepate pa IĚ±maęž‰ hone uaęž‰ tupaęž‰ otaęž‰ hoke hau paęž‰laęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ na lememe.  
\v 19 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki samani pitolo leme ekitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ yeni pu haleme haunaęž‰ make pa ambaęž‰ homeeke hali Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ make samani pitolo lememe. Koto hali Yesutaęž‰ Polomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ koto hali ame paa tiao halaęž‰me leaęž‰me.  
\v 20 Kutu piki haumanu handaęž‰ wiaęž‰peke potaęž‰ weiluekemaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ pomomaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ Polo paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ koto hande neke samani pitolo leme pinaęž‰ pi yokaalu peaano mo Diutuseleme da paęž‰taęž‰ poluekemaęž‰ hone witelepe la lotaęž‰ puaęž‰pate  
\v 21 Polomaęž‰ Sisamaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi yokaalu peaenaęž‰ honke laataęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ dipula da paęž‰taęž‰ handeteke haenaęž‰ Sisamaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi tikitiki yao laowaenaęž‰ honke leaęž‰me. Koto leeke handa IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ dipula pa pitinaęž‰ laa Sisa paęž‰taęž‰ tapaalueke laa loaęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 22 Akatipamaęž‰ Pesitasi paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do halinaęž‰ pi IĚ±maęž‰ kone opuluekemaęž‰ hone witolome leekeme. Pesitasimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Belia opuelenaęž‰e leekeme.   
\p
\v 23 Koto laa da kaęž‰laęž‰paasotaęž‰ Akatipa Benisi yaapo au au wotu laa aęž‰pataęž‰ mo mombolo haeme da paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo ami aęž‰ndaęž‰ tumiki haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± make mo daoni paęž‰taęž‰ haeme you haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± make paeyaotaęž‰ hondaęž‰ pamba epememe. Pesitasimaęž‰ pi leeke handa Polo hatuku epenaęž‰ lememe.  
\v 24 Kutupa aęž‰pa haenaęž‰ Pesitasimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kini hali Akatipao. Do hao yapeleme wandaęž‰hali iki paeyao make do halaęž‰ hali ikaęž‰ handelememe. Do paęž‰taęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ make Diutuseleme da paęž‰taęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ make koto Diu wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ koto hali samani pimime. Mo haliwekimaęž‰ pi tanda pu alu alu pea alotaęž‰ Do halitaęž‰ homenaęž‰e alememe.  
\v 25 Koto alemepate do halimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ homolo paęž‰laęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ na handaęž‰ witolome. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ kone Sisamaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi yokaalu peaenaęž‰ honke leaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ Sisa paęž‰taęž‰ tapaalueke hone uaęž‰me.  
\v 26 Kutu puaęž‰pate pa do halimaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ Sisa paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ teke pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ wape pea tapaaluekemaęž‰ IĚ± hone na witolome. Koto ekinaęž‰ Kini hali Akatipao. Neke paęž‰taęž‰ make do haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ make iki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ do hali koto epenaęž‰ alo handaęž‰e. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ lelie pi opuataęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ wape pulu polo pi hone ulueke.  
\v 27 IĚ±maęž‰ dipula pilaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ tapaaso hataęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ samani pimi pi teke tonkaęž‰naęž‰ wape anaęž‰naęž‰ pea na tapaowaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me hone witolome laa leekeme.   
\c 26  
\s1 Polomaęž‰ Akatipanaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ hataęž‰ pi leekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Akatipamaęž‰ Polo paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ kone pi lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Lae leaęž‰me. Kutupa Polomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kiki tindipao pi alo alotaęž‰   
\p
\v 2 Kini Akatipao. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ kone mo hande Diu haliwekimaęž‰ IĚ± baęž‰saęž‰ pimi ekimanu yaka pi alo ekinaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 3 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande Diu haliwekinaęž‰ peleme ekimanu make ikaęž‰ pi yokaalu pu haleme haunaęž‰ ekimanu handolo hataęž‰ yaka pi yopu opu pitaęž‰peke leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 4 Yaka wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ weki hataęž‰ puaęž‰eki make Diutuseleme da paęž‰taęž‰ haowaęž‰eki make Diu wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ handememe leaęž‰me.  
\v 5 IĚ±taęž‰ hande Paęž‰tisi tapake haowaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ ambaęž‰ kone handataęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me leaęž‰me.  
\v 6 Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ apaęž‰ ameda paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰ wiekeeki paęž‰taęž‰ hone ulumaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ame IĚ± baęž‰saęž‰ pitelememe leaęž‰me.  
\v 7 Koto pi laęž‰ wiekeeki muluekemaęž‰ nikaęž‰ tapake 12 wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao yeni pu halememe leaęž‰me. Kini halio. Koto pi laęž‰ wieke ekinaęž‰ hone ulu ekinaęž‰ mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰ IĚ± baęž‰saęž‰ pitelememe.  
\v 8 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paa mea tiaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me laa ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ekipeke koto hone na witelemepe leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 9 Mo hande Naęž‰saęž‰tete hali Yesunaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu saęž‰saęž‰ puluekemaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ wotu puluekemaęž‰ hone wopu wiaataęž‰  
\v 10 Diutuseleme da paęž‰taęž‰ kutu puaęž‰me. Mo yeni peao haleme you haliwekimaęž‰ peaęž‰peke lemeke handaataęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ yakopiki wandaęž‰hali woputaęž‰ dipula homeke na pitaake otaęž‰ litolo haenaęž‰ make IĚ±maęž‰ make kiki mea aęž‰meiyaowaęž‰me leaęž‰me.  
\v 11 Kutupa mo wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ pi hotu haleme da paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ panisi wotu peatiki peaataęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ hoke pi lenaęž‰yeke la handetiki puaęž‰me. Kutupa mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ mineke wotu pankolo hataęž‰ mandane damanu paęž‰taęž‰ kone tolu liaęž‰tiki puaęž‰me.   
\s1 Polomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰ miniekeeki laęž‰laęž‰eki  
\p
\v 12 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo yeni peao haleme teke haliwekimaęž‰ IĚ± tapaemeke handa IĚ±taęž‰ Damasikasi da nane poaęž‰pate  
\v 13 Ya tiekeo. Nate you tikekenaęž‰ haenaęž‰ potaęž‰naęž‰ pulu hamono oli ya nanemaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± tieke nate tupaęž‰ diaęž‰me mo IĚ± ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ pomaęž‰ haliweki hande paĚ±aĚ± tiekemaęž‰ niki dopuaeyaęž‰eki handoaęž‰me leaęž‰me.  
\v 14 Kutupa niki paeyao kenkenaęž‰ hondaęž‰pa lopa wiomono IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ Hibulu pimaęž‰ kone pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ leaęž‰eki opuaęž‰me dupae. Solo. Solo. Ekipeke IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ litelepe leaęž‰me. Kanake etimaęž‰ awaęž‰laęž‰eki kiaase ekinaęž‰ tanda koto minele handaęž‰e leaęž‰me.  
\v 15 Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Neketaęž‰ epikaęž‰taęž‰pe loaęž‰me. Kutupa Tekehalimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Yesue. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ liteleme.  
\v 16 Kutu pitelepate neke tiao hapeke laataęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ ya e pokaalenaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ya kone neke paęž‰taęž‰ peneme yaowaęž‰me leaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰ puaęž‰ hau nakanaęž‰maęž‰ handa la haloelenaęž‰ make IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ peneme yaalo polo ekinaęž‰ la haloelenaęž‰ make neke halenaęž‰ alome leaęž‰me leaęž‰me.  
\v 17 Kutupa mo Diu Diendaili yaapo tapake haliwekimaęž‰ neke na minaęž‰ laataęž‰ mo Diendaili wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ neke tapaasome leaęž‰me leaęž‰me.  
\v 18 Ikaęž‰ leke kilaowalenaęž‰ yeke neke tapaasome leaęž‰me. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ timbaęž‰ lo pambaęž‰laęž‰eki laęž‰kaęž‰la minaęž‰paęž‰lao paĚ±aĚ±naęž‰ epoemenaęž‰yeke puaęž‰me. Hande Sadaninaęž‰ wele paęž‰laęž‰eki laęž‰kaęž‰la minaęž‰paęž‰lao Kodaęž‰naęž‰eki haminaęž‰yeke puaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu Kodaęž‰maęž‰ pa tombuao halaęž‰eki muemenaęž‰yeke puaęž‰me. Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ yaka pi minaęž‰leke handa talopu mea haenaęž‰ lolo wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa haminaęž‰yeke puaęž‰me leaęž‰me.   
\s1 Polomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokeekeeki laęž‰laęž‰eki  
\p
\v 19 Koto ekinaęž‰ Kini Akatipao. IĚ±maęž‰ oli ya nanemaęž‰ peneme yao laęž‰niaeyaęž‰eki opuataęž‰ pi na tunkuliki otaęž‰ puaęž‰me.  
\v 20 Mo Damasikasi da wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰la wala kutupa Diutuseleme da paęž‰taęž‰ make mo Diudia nane paeyao make kutupa Diendaili wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make iki paeyaomaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰lolo hataęž‰ hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la witolo epeke haumanu pinaęž‰yeke pi waloendi pu haowaęž‰me.  
\v 21 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰ mo tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ mina luekemaęž‰ taapemepate  
\v 22 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± pa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki mu hataęž‰ ame make do paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ hali tieke paęž‰taęž‰manu make hosiki halisunu paęž‰taęž‰ make la halaęž‰tiki pitolome. Hande Mosesimaęž‰ make mo potopede haliwekimaęž‰ make pulu paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu lemeke tupaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ make do la halo halome.  
\v 23 Dupa. Ketisotaęž‰ titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la tanda paęž‰laęž‰eki meaataęž‰ kutupa titinaęž‰ homa paa tiaalo paęž‰laęž‰ hali hataęž‰ mo Diu wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make mo Diendaili wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make paĚ±aĚ± pitaęž‰laęž‰eki walaęž‰tiki pilieke leleme pi kone IĚ±maęž‰ make alome leekeme.   
\p
\v 24 Kutupa Polomaęž‰ koto pi alo haenaęž‰ Pesitasimaęž‰ pi anekemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Polo neketaęž‰ keaase leaęž‰me. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ hau paeyao pitele ekimaęž‰ neke koto mea keaasaęž‰ handaęž‰e leaęž‰pate  
\v 25 Polomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hali keilekeo. IĚ±taęž‰ siakaęž‰hali diaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome.  
\v 26 Kini hali Akatipamaęž‰ do haumanu handeleke handa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pa pi alo hataęž‰ yaka honemaęž‰taęž‰ koto hau paeyao handaęž‰laęž‰me. Pa ekipeke mo hau manutaęž‰ aęž‰mbao na piki peneme yao piaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 27 Kini hali Akatipao. Hande potopede haliwekimaęž‰ wape pelemeeki manutaęž‰ opitele laa nakaęž‰ opua pitele hautaęž‰ handolome laa leekeme.  
\v 28 Kutupa Akatipamaęž‰ Polo paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ paa koto kone Ketiso hali hanoyeke alepe laa leekeme.  
\v 29 Koto leeke Polomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ame dope o wetepenaęž‰pe o Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ ya hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ neke make do pita yapaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao make do IĚ±maęž‰ walolo pi opuataęž‰ IĚ± tupaęž‰ haminaęž‰yeke loaęž‰pate pa do seni pu manumaęž‰ IĚ± tonkao halo tupaęž‰ na loaęž‰me leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 30 Kutupa mo hande kini hali tiaotaęž‰ mo kapomani you hali make Benisi make mo iki ameĚ±leĚ± pitimiki wandaęž‰hali make tiao minaęž‰paęž‰lao puaataęž‰  
\v 31 ikaęž‰ kone pi la alu alu pitolo alotaęž‰ Do halitaęž‰ dipula pitinaęž‰ homaapeketaęž‰ anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me. Eki aęž‰ndaęž‰ na piaęž‰me laa lemekeme.  
\v 32 Kutupa Akatipamaęž‰ Pesitasi paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do halimaęž‰taęž‰ Sisa paęž‰taęž‰ wi na leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ da nane pa puaęž‰peke yolo piaęž‰me laa leekeme.   
\c 27  
\s1 Polotaęž‰ palai kawasonaęž‰ pita Lomaęž‰ nane peekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Kutupa Ideli nane palai kawaso tiekenaęž‰ pomanaęž‰e laa hone wimiki pitaęž‰ Polo mandane dipula haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± ami opisa hali homeke Diuliusi paęž‰taęž‰ halaakaęž‰naęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Okasitani tapake hali hataęž‰ handeteke haenaęž‰yeke pimime.  
\v 2 Kutupa Aęž‰datamitiomo da nane hao epeeke palai kawaso Eisia damanu paęž‰taęž‰ poluekemaęž‰ haenaęž‰ mo hande Maęž‰sedonia nane Desalonaika hali Aęž‰tisakusi ameĚ±leĚ± mo kawasonaęž‰ pua pita pomaęž‰me.  
\v 3 Da kelepeeke handa mo Saidoni da opolo pomaęž‰me. Kutupa Diuliusimaęž‰ Polo paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yankeke titimaęž‰ handeteke haenaęž‰yeke handolo penaęž‰ leaęž‰me.  
\v 4 Kutupa koto paęž‰taęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao dawala tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pua po tilipumanu wenoko nanemaęž‰ epeeke handa mo Saipotasi nanemaęž‰ oto paęž‰taęž‰ yapomaęž‰me.  
\v 5 Kutupa mo Silisia Paęž‰mbilia kenke yaapo nane dawalanaęž‰ tunkula puataęž‰ mo Laisia nanemaęž‰ halaęž‰ da Maita da paęž‰taęž‰ opolo pomaęž‰me.  
\v 6 Koto da paęž‰taęž‰ mo opisa halimaęž‰ palai kawaso homeke Aęž‰lekesaęž‰ndia da nane hao Ideli nane poluekemaęž‰ haenaęž‰ handaęž‰ wiaataęž‰ niki koto palai kawasonaęž‰ pitaeyaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 7 Nate mandaneeki manunaęž‰taęž‰ yopusiki puaęž‰tiki pea kaęž‰ndaęž‰ taapunaęž‰ mo Sinaidasi da paęž‰taęž‰ opolo pomaęž‰me. Kutupa mo po tilipu nikaęž‰ wenoko nanemaęž‰ ipulu hataęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ pieke handa mo Kotiti hoki oto paęž‰taęž‰ mo Saęž‰lomono da teke paęž‰taęž‰ pomaęž‰me.  
\v 8 Kutupa mo dawala teaęž‰ nane kaęž‰ndaęž‰ taapunaęž‰ pulu hataęž‰ mo hande Lasea teke paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ da Pe Heipeni da paęž‰taęž‰ opolo pomaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 9 Natelekemanu ambaęž‰ paeyeke handa mo hande Diu wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ nemanu na neke pa hao haemeke nate make paeyeke handa niki ekiaęž‰ndaęž‰ peaamaęž‰naęž‰ laa da puaęž‰peke na yeaęž‰me. Polomaęž‰ pi alo alotaęž‰  
\v 10 Haliwekio. Ya hone witolo ekitaęž‰ doe leaęž‰me. Ame do dinaęž‰ pomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ hoeyapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me leaęž‰me. Do palai kawaso alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ homeke na loaęž‰me. Haliweki make alupeaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me leaęž‰me.  
\v 11 Koto leekepate mo opisa halimaęž‰ Polomaęž‰ leaęž‰ pi na opiki mo palai kawaso teke halinaęž‰ pi pitaęž‰ mo teke handeteke hayeke hali yaaponaęž‰ pi homeke opiaęž‰me.  
\v 12 Kutupa koto paęž‰taęž‰ kosaęž‰ ki epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ hapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me laa haliweki paeyaomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Dawala tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pua mo Kotiti nane sisima u hayeke alenaęž‰ Pinikisi da paęž‰taęž‰ opolo polumaęž‰pe mataęž‰laęž‰me laa lememe. Koto paęž‰taęž‰ hamono kosaęž‰ ki epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ anaęž‰ pilieke laa lememe.   
\s1 Mo dawalanaęž‰ po tilipu epeekeeki  
\p
\v 13 Kutupa po hosiki ipulu haenaęž‰ Ametaęž‰ puaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me hone wia mo aęž‰nka yolaęž‰ mea aęž‰meiyao mo Kotiti nepoko nanemaęž‰ pomaęž‰me.  
\v 14 Pomaęž‰pate po tieke kenke nanemaęž‰ epeeketaęž‰  
\v 15 otaęž‰ ambulaeyeke handa mo hande kawasotaęž‰ wenoko nanemaęž‰ puaęž‰peke na yalo hataęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la niki tu mea baeyaęž‰me.  
\v 16 Kutupa puoopu hao mo Kouda hosiki nepoko nanemaęž‰ puataęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ kone mo kawasosiki mea kawaso tieke manda  
\v 17 mea aęž‰meiyao mo palai kawaso tieke setepe pea mea tonkaluekemaęž‰ pimime. Kutupa mo Setisi kenke nane puaamaęž‰naęž‰ palaimanu leisi mea wiaataęž‰ pa pomaęž‰ tinaęž‰ lememe.  
\v 18 Kutupa mo kawaso tieketaęž‰ lekeleke wotu leeke handa da kelepeeketaęž‰ kako alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ ikali paęž‰taęž‰ mu ba ba pimime.  
\v 19 Da maęž‰ndaęž‰ kelepeeketaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kikimaęž‰ kone mo hande palaimanu make mo palai endu hayaęž‰ pumanu make mea baememe.  
\v 20 Kutupa mo hande nate hombulankaęž‰manu hoto elekeeleke na teeke handa po tieke paa ipulu haenaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ nikitaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me laa hone umaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 21 Kutupa nate paeyao ne na nemeke handa Polomaęž‰taęž‰ tiao iki paęž‰taęž‰ pua alotaęž‰ Haliwekio. IĚ±maęž‰ hande loaęž‰ pi opuaęž‰paęž‰peke aleo. Kotiti nane na minaęž‰paęž‰laemekaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ do alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰tieke na hao weleke we pumaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ na pulu pumaęž‰me leaęž‰me.  
\v 22 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ do alome. Honkopu hape leaęž‰me. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ homeke hautaęž‰ na pilieke. Do kawaso homeke hoelieke leaęž‰me.  
\v 23 Ame do timba kone ya pandaęž‰puniao hataęž‰ taęž‰maęž‰ni pea halo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ enisolo homeke IĚ± teke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa hataęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\v 24 Poloo otaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰peke. Neketaęž‰ Sisa teke paęž‰taęž‰ pua halipikie leaęž‰me leaęž‰me. Kutupa opie. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ neke ameĚ±leĚ± pulimi haliweki paeyao pa kilieke leaęž‰me.  
\v 25 Koto ekinaęž‰ haliwekio. Honkopu hape. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi miniki hataęž‰ hande IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ leaęž‰ haumanu otaęž‰ pilieke hone ulume leaęž‰me.  
\v 26 Kutu piliepate nikitaęž‰ hoki maęž‰ndaęž‰ nane pua talumeke leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 27 Natemanu 14 paeyeketaęž‰ mo po tilipu ipulu haenaęž‰ timbataęž‰ mo Meditoteiniani dawala ikali tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pulu hamono butaęž‰hokinaęž‰ mo palai kawaso handeteke haeme haliwekimaęž‰ Ametaęž‰ kenke teke paęž‰taęž‰ pulumaęž‰me hone wimikime.  
\v 28 Koto ekinaęž‰ pu mea lopaęž‰niao 20 paęž‰domi yataęž‰pa handaataęž‰ hosiki mo pateleke pua paa mea lopaęž‰niao 15 paęž‰domi yataęž‰pa handemekeme.  
\v 29 Kutupa mo toopi paęž‰taęž‰ puaamaęž‰naęž‰ mo palai kawaso hoki nane aęž‰nka tonkopu mea lopaotaęž‰ da kelepenaęž‰yeke yeni pimikime.  
\v 30 Mo palai kawaso handeteke haeme haliwekitaęž‰ mo palai kawaso minaęž‰paęž‰lao pindipa poluekemaęž‰ mo hande kawasosiki mea ikali manda lopanialuekemaęž‰ pimime. Mo palai kawaso mineke nane paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰nka mandane ekimanu mea lopaaluekemaęž‰ makeaaso hataęž‰ pimipate  
\v 31 Polomaęž‰ mo opisa hali ipikaęž‰ ami haliweki tonkaęž‰naęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do palai kawaso handeteke haleme haliweki do paęž‰taęž‰ na pitimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me leaęž‰me.  
\v 32 Koto leaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ mo ami haliwekimaęž‰ hande konau pumanu tunkula hande kawasosiki paa lopenaęž‰ lememe.   
\p
\v 33 Da kaęž‰laęž‰puluekemaęž‰ haenaęž‰ Polomaęž‰ paeyaomaęž‰ nesiki nenaęž‰yeke honke wotu alo alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ nesiki na neke hone elekeeleke witolo haminaęž‰ nate 14 paeyaęž‰me leaęž‰me.  
\v 34 Koto ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ do honke alo pitaęž‰ Ne nape pi ta alo handaęž‰pe leaęž‰me. Honkopu hamenaęž‰ nape leaęž‰me. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ itiki homeke kone na alupilieke leaęž‰me.  
\v 35 Koto laakaęž‰naęž‰ Polomaęž‰ palaowa mea haliweki paeyao ameĚ±leĚ± hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae pi laataęž‰ mo palaowa pindipa neaęž‰me.  
\v 36 Kutupa paeyaomaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homa ikaęž‰ kone ne nememe.  
\v 37 Mo hande kawaso tiekenaęž‰ 276 haliweki pitumaęž‰me.  
\v 38 Kutupa ne anaęž‰naęž‰ naakaęž‰naęž‰ mo kawaso yapaęž‰ pu liaenaęž‰yeke mo widi palaowanaęž‰ kiliki pusemanu dawala tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ mea lopaememe.   
\s1 Mo hande palai kawaso yambaęž‰laęž‰ alu alu piekeeki  
\p
\v 39 Kutupa da kelepeaęž‰ pitaęž‰taęž‰ kenke handaataęž‰ Hando paęž‰taęž‰pe lemepate ankolo pu wiekeeki homeke handaataęž‰ Do kawasotaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ talamanaęž‰e lememe.  
\v 40 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo hande aęž‰nka pumanu kaęž‰laęž‰pa lopaęž‰niao oni dawala tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ ulu penaęž‰ laataęž‰ mo kawaso laęž‰kaęž‰lao hayaęž‰ alemanu tonkaeyaęž‰ pumanu make kaęž‰laęž‰paataęž‰ mo kawaso mineke nane palai homeke mea endiao pomaęž‰ titolo haenaęž‰ mo kenke paęž‰taęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± penaęž‰yeke pimime.  
\v 41 Kutu pimipate mo kawasotaęž‰ ikali hou paęž‰taęž‰ taĚ±laĚ± haenaęž‰ mo kawaso mineke nane otaęž‰ pankaęž‰ pelia hataęž‰ takaęž‰laęž‰pa pulu haenaęž‰ hande mendeke nanetaęž‰ mo dawala ikali homaęž‰ aęž‰pa mea lonke lonke laaso hataęž‰ hande kawaso mendeke nane yambaęž‰latiki piaęž‰me.  
\v 42 Kutupa mo ami haliwekimaęž‰ mo dipula haliweki paeyao ikali paęž‰taęž‰ kiki mokaęž‰la pindipa puaamaęž‰naęž‰ lumanaęž‰e hone wimikipate  
\v 43 pa ikaęž‰ opisa halimaęž‰ Polo tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ mo haliweki hone wimieki tunkula saęž‰saęž‰ piaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi la alotaęž‰ Kiki mokaęž‰lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ haliweki ambaęž‰la dawala paęž‰taęž‰ ponkaniao kenke nane puaęž‰paęž‰peke leaęž‰me.  
\v 44 Kutupa mandane haliwekitaęž‰ tisunu make kawaso yambaęž‰laęž‰laęž‰eki sasakesunu make mea mina puaęž‰paęž‰peke leaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ niki paeyaotaęž‰ mo kenke nane pua anaęž‰naęž‰ opolo pomaęž‰me.   
\c 28  
\s1 Molota paęž‰taęž‰ hayekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Kutupa kenke nane epeke opolo pua hataęž‰ koto hokinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Molota lemeeki opumaęž‰me.  
\v 2 Koto paęž‰taęž‰ haeme haliwekimaęž‰ niki petololo hataęž‰ ti kita kiki kimime. Lako ipulu hataęž‰ kosaęž‰ pieke handa pimime.  
\v 3 Polomaęž‰ tisunu mu tonko pea tinaęž‰ wiaęž‰pate titipu pieke handa hoke ketomaęž‰ aęž‰pa ipikaęž‰ kikinaęž‰ hapuliaęž‰me.  
\v 4 Mo da haliwekimaęž‰ hande keto ipikaęž‰ kikinaęž‰ hapuliaęž‰eki handaataęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone ane mone pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do halimaęž‰taęž‰ ketete pea hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ litolo paęž‰laęž‰me lememe. Dawala paęž‰taęž‰ na homeaęž‰pate pa ipikaęž‰ ketetenaęž‰ homilieke lememe.  
\v 5 Koto lemepate Polomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kiki tande tande laa mo keto ti paęž‰taęž‰ lopaeyaęž‰me. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ ekiaęž‰ndaęž‰ na piaęž‰me.  
\v 6 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ Polo pombei yao tako pea lopenaęž‰ patemaęž‰ handomaęž‰ handomaęž‰ pimipate ekiaęž‰ndaęž‰ na pieke handa ikaęž‰ hone laęž‰kaęž‰la alotaęž‰ Do halitaęž‰ kodaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me lememe.   
\p
\v 7 Koto alenaęž‰ tekepaęž‰taęž‰ mo hokinaęž‰ haeme wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hamoko tumiki hali Pubiliusitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ emanu pokeaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ niki handaęž‰ mea nate teponaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ niki handeteke hayaęž‰me.  
\v 8 Ipikaęž‰ ateketaęž‰ ki yeni tiputu hatu yamaasaęž‰ yeni make hao homaęž‰pa wiaęž‰me. Kutupa Polomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ da pandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pua Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pea ipikaęž‰ kiki yaapo mo halinaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ wia yeni tandelaeyaęž‰me.  
\v 9 Kutu pieke handa mo hokinaęž‰ yeni haeme wandaęž‰hali paeyao epemepate ikaęž‰ yeni make tandelenaęž‰ leaęž‰me.  
\v 10 Niki paęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ wopu kiaataęž‰ kutupa palai kawaso maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ paa poluekemaęž‰ hamono nikaęž‰ mea puaęž‰peke yeaęž‰ alemanu kimime.   
\s1 Mo Molota hao Lomaęž‰ nane pemekeeki  
\p
\v 11 Sumbaęž‰ tepo yapeeke handa mo Aęž‰lekesaęž‰ndia da hao epeaęž‰ palai kawaso homekenaęž‰ pomaęž‰me. Mo kawaso bikitaęž‰ Temoko Mandaęž‰e. Mo kosaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ hande hoki paęž‰taęž‰ hando hayaęž‰me.  
\v 12 Kutupa pua mo Sitakusi daoni paęž‰taęž‰ opolo pua nate tepo koto paęž‰taęž‰ haowaęž‰me.  
\v 13 Koto paęž‰taęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao puoopu hao mo Lidiumi daoni paęž‰taęž‰ opolo pomaęž‰me. Da kelepeaęž‰ pitaęž‰taęž‰ mo dawala nane po ipulu haenaęž‰yeke nate yaapo puataęž‰ mo Puteoli daoni paęž‰taęž‰ opolo pomaęž‰me.  
\v 14 Koto paęž‰taęž‰ mandane Ketiso tapake wandaęž‰hali handaęž‰ umaęž‰pate pula homekenaęž‰ niki ameĚ±leĚ± hamanaęž‰e laa honke lememe. Koto ekinaęž‰ puataęž‰ Lomaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ opolo pomaęž‰me.  
\v 15 Kutupa mo Lomaęž‰ Ketiso kame titimaęž‰ niki ipulumaęž‰me pi opuataęž‰ mo Apiusinaęž‰ makedi paęž‰taęž‰ make mo Kimisu Hali Polu Halaęž‰ Da Tepo paęž‰taęž‰ make niki mandaęž‰hande pulu epememe. Kutupa Polomaęž‰ iki handaataęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae pi laataęž‰ honkopu hayaęž‰me.   
\s1 Lomaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hayekeeki  
\p
\v 16 Kutupa mo Lomaęž‰ daoni paęž‰taęž‰ opolo pomaęž‰pate pa Polotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone honumake haenaęž‰ mo ami hali homekemaęž‰ ipiki handeteke haenaęž‰ lememe.  
\v 17 Kutupa nate tepo paeyeketaęž‰ Polomaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ haeme tondiki Diu haliweki wi laęž‰ mepi peaataęž‰ kutupa mombaęž‰la haenaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kametitio. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make nikaęž‰ apaęž‰mei manunaęž‰ peleme ekimanu paęž‰taęž‰ make ekiaęž‰ndaęž‰ na puaęž‰pate mo Diutuseleme haliwekimaęž‰ IĚ± meaataęž‰ Lomaęž‰ haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ halememe.  
\v 18 Kutupa ya hau weiya lotaęž‰ pimipate IĚ± homaalo piaęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ na handaęž‰ u haotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ da tapaaluekemaęž‰ hone wimime.  
\v 19 Kutu pimipate mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰ Na tapaapeke lemeke handa yaka wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ samani puluekemaęž‰ hone na uaęž‰pate Sisa paęž‰taęž‰ kone wi loluekemaęž‰ puaęž‰me.  
\v 20 Koto ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki wi la handolo pi loluekemaęž‰ loaęž‰me. Isulai wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hone wilimi ekinaęž‰ do seni pumaęž‰ IĚ± tonkaeyaęž‰me leaęž‰me.  
\v 21 Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Diudia nanemaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ wape pea ipulaęž‰ pasemanu na mumaęž‰me. Kutupa do ane epeaęž‰ kame homekemaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ hoke pi make neke paęž‰taęž‰ na laęž‰laęž‰me lememe.  
\v 22 Kutu paęž‰laęž‰pate mo kenke paeyao nane do hande tapake paęž‰taęž‰ la la pu halemeeki opolomaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ nakaęž‰ hone witele ekimanu opuluekemaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰me lememe.   
\p
\v 23 Kutupa nate wiataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hayaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ haliweki wopu pua mombelememe. Kutupa Polomaęž‰ mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ pimanu walo hayaęž‰eki da kaęž‰laęž‰paaso la pua timbaęž‰ laeyaęž‰me. Yesunaęž‰ pi opua minaęž‰yeke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ hande Mosesinaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ Lo Pimanu make mo potopede haliwekinaęž‰ wape pelemeeki paęž‰taęž‰ make laa waleaęž‰me.  
\v 24 Mandane haliwekimaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ leaęž‰ pi opimipate mandaneeki manumaęž‰ na opimime.  
\v 25 Koto ekinaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone hone taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ wia pi taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ alo hataęž‰ poluekemaęž‰ haenaęž‰ Polomaęž‰ pi homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ dupa leaęž‰me. Mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ hande potopede hali Aisaya paęž‰taęž‰ la halolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ atekemanu paęž‰taęž‰ do leeke pitaęž‰ otaęž‰ alo piaęž‰me.  
\v 26 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ leeke ekitaęž‰ dupa  
\q1 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ opitolo opitolo halo pelemepate ikaęž‰ hone paęž‰taęž‰ na wilimikie.  
\q1 Kutaa make handolo handolo halo pelemepate ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ na handilimikie.   
\q1
\v 27 Pa ekipeke. Do wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hone manutaęž‰ timbaęž‰ lo make ikaęž‰ katakemanu poko make ikaęž‰ lekemanu handupu paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\q1 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\q1 Kutu piki haumanu na piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ ikaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ epeke hando make ikaęž‰ katakemaęž‰ epeke opu make ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ epeke hone wia hataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la epolo pimikaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki wamo pulu puaęž‰me laa laęž‰laęž‰me leekeme leaęž‰me.   
\b  
\p
\v 28 Kutupa Polomaęž‰ lo paeyaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ daęž‰taasaęž‰ pitaęž‰ mo Diendaili wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ tapaasaęž‰maęž‰ opilimikie laa leaęž‰me.  
\v 29 [Koto pi leaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao pulu hataęž‰ pi la alu alu pulu pimime.]   
\p
\v 30 Kutupa koto paęž‰taęž‰ bapi yaapo Polomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hambo hayaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ hao hataęž‰ ipiki handolo epemeke wandaęž‰hali paeyao handaęž‰ meaataęž‰  
\v 31 maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ na pitolo haenaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ honkopu haaso hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ make mo Tekehali Yesu Ketisonaęž‰eki make pi walaęž‰tiki pu hayekeme.   